-- 16/09/2024

SELECT * FROM FINANCE_GRADE_CONSOLIDADA WHERE DATAPGT = '20240913' and Z2_CTRID IS NULL
UPDATE FINANCE_GRADE_CONSOLIDADA SET DATAPGT = '20240917' WHERE DATAPGT = '20240913' and Z2_CTRID IS NULL

-- 03/09/2024
Conferencia VA VE Moove Julho/2024

-- PowerBK
SELECT EVENTO,DESCREVENTO,SUM(VALOR) FROM FOLHA WHERE EMPRESA = '16'
AND COMPETAM = '202407'
GROUP BY EVENTO,DESCREVENTO
ORDER BY EVENTO,DESCREVENTO

-- DataP10

SELECT Z2_TIPO,SUM(Z2_VALOR) FROM SZ2010 WHERE Z2_CODEMP = '16' AND SUBSTRING(Z2_DATAPGT,1,6) = '202407' AND Z2_STATUS = 'S' GROUP BY Z2_TIPO ORDER BY Z2_TIPO

SELECT D1_COD,D1_XXDESCP,D1_CC,D1_TOTAL FROM SD1160 WHERE D1_COD = '31201045' AND SUBSTRING(D1_DTDIGIT,1,6) = '202407'
UNION ALL
SELECT D1_COD,D1_XXDESCP,D1_CC,D1_TOTAL FROM SD1160 WHERE D1_COD = '31201046' AND SUBSTRING(D1_DTDIGIT,1,6) = '202407'
UNION ALL
SELECT D1_COD,D1_XXDESCP,D1_CC,D1_TOTAL FROM SD1160 WHERE D1_COD = '31201047' AND SUBSTRING(D1_DTDIGIT,1,6) = '202407'


SELECT * FROM SD1160 WHERE D1_XXDESCP LIKE '%VT$'
SELECT * INTO SD1160OLD  FROM SD1160
UPDATE SD1160 SET D1_COD = '31201047' WHERE D1_COD = '31201045'
UPDATE SD1160 SET D1_COD = '31201045' WHERE D1_COD = '31201046'

-- 13/08/2024 - ACERTO Z5_CC BHG
SELECT * FROM SZ5150 WHERE Z5_CC LIKE  'Er:%'
UPDATE SZ5150 SET Z5_CC = '000001010' WHERE Z5_CC LIKE  'Er:%'


SELECT * FROM SZ5010 WHERE Z5_CC LIKE  'Er:%'
UPDATE SZ5010 SET Z5_CC = '142000605' WHERE Z5_CC LIKE  'Er:%'

UPDATE SZ5010 SET Z5_CC = '142000605' WHERE Z5_CC = 'Er:000614'
UPDATE SZ5010 SET Z5_CC = '142000579' WHERE Z5_CC = 'Er:000613'
UPDATE SZ5010 SET Z5_CC = '142000513' WHERE Z5_CC = 'Er:000612'

SELECT  'CSB',CSB_CCANT ,COUNT(*) FROM CSB010 WHERE CSB_CCANT  = '044000618' GROUP BY CSB_CCANT  UNION ALL
SELECT  'HWA',HWA_CCUSTO,COUNT(*) FROM HWA010 WHERE HWA_CCUSTO = '044000618' GROUP BY HWA_CCUSTO

-- 12/06/24 - Relao de Centros de Custo

SELECT '01-BK' AS EMPRESA,CTT_CUSTO AS CCUSTO,CTT_DESC01 AS DESCRICAO FROM CTT010 WHERE D_E_L_E_T_ = ' ' --ORDER BY CTT_CUSTO
UNION ALL
SELECT '02-MMDK' AS EMPRESA,CTT_CUSTO AS CCUSTO,CTT_DESC01 AS DESCRICAO FROM CTT020 WHERE D_E_L_E_T_ = ' ' 
UNION ALL
SELECT '12-CORRETORA' AS EMPRESA,CTT_CUSTO AS CCUSTO,CTT_DESC01 AS DESCRICAO FROM CTT120 WHERE D_E_L_E_T_ = ' ' 
UNION ALL
SELECT '14-BALSA' AS EMPRESA,CTT_CUSTO AS CCUSTO,CTT_DESC01 AS DESCRICAO FROM CTT140 WHERE D_E_L_E_T_ = ' ' 
UNION ALL
SELECT '15-BHG' AS EMPRESA,CTT_CUSTO AS CCUSTO,CTT_DESC01 AS DESCRICAO FROM CTT150 WHERE D_E_L_E_T_ = ' ' 
UNION ALL
SELECT '16-MOOVE' AS EMPRESA,CTT_CUSTO AS CCUSTO,CTT_DESC01 AS DESCRICAO FROM CTT160 WHERE D_E_L_E_T_ = ' ' 
UNION ALL
SELECT '17-DMAF' AS EMPRESA,CTT_CUSTO AS CCUSTO,CTT_DESC01 AS DESCRICAO FROM CTT170 WHERE D_E_L_E_T_ = ' ' 
UNION ALL
SELECT '18-BK VIA' AS EMPRESA,CTT_CUSTO AS CCUSTO,CTT_DESC01 AS DESCRICAO FROM CTT180 WHERE D_E_L_E_T_ = ' ' 
UNION ALL
SELECT '19-BK SOLUOES' AS EMPRESA,CTT_CUSTO AS CCUSTO,CTT_DESC01 AS DESCRICAO FROM CTT190 WHERE D_E_L_E_T_ = ' ' 

ORDER BY EMPRESA,CTT_CUSTO

-- 04/06/24 - Acerto descrio de produtos da CNB
SELECT CNB_CONTRA,CNB_PRODUT,CNB_DESCRI,B1_COD,B1_DESC FROM CNB010
--UPDATE CNB010 SET CNB_DESCRI = B1_DESC FROM CNB010
LEFT JOIN SB1010 ON CNB_PRODUT = B1_COD AND SB1010.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''
WHERE CNB010.D_E_L_E_T_='' 
AND B1_DESC <> CNB_DESCRI

==============================================================
-- 24/04/2024 Relao de produtos em uso desde 01/01/2021

WITH PRD  AS (

SELECT D1_COD COD,MAX(D1_DTDIGIT) AS DATA, B1_DESC,'ENTRADA' AS TIPO ,B1_XXSGRP,ZI_DESC,BM_GRUPO,BM_DESC
FROM SD1010 SD1 
LEFT JOIN SB1010 SB1 ON D1_COD = B1_COD AND SB1.D_E_L_E_T_ = ' '
LEFT JOIN SZI010 SZI ON ZI_COD = B1_XXSGRP AND SZI.D_E_L_E_T_ = ' '
LEFT JOIN SBM010 SBM ON BM_GRUPO = B1_GRUPO AND SBM.D_E_L_E_T_ = ' '
WHERE  SD1.D_E_L_E_T_ = ' ' AND B1_MSBLQL = '2' AND B1_COD NOT LIKE '%-%'
GROUP BY D1_COD, B1_DESC ,B1_XXSGRP,ZI_DESC,BM_GRUPO,BM_DESC
UNION ALL

SELECT D2_COD COD ,MAX(D2_EMISSAO) AS DATA , B1_DESC,'SAIDA' AS TIPO ,B1_XXSGRP,ZI_DESC,BM_GRUPO,BM_DESC
FROM SD2010 SD2 
LEFT JOIN SB1010 SB1 ON D2_COD = B1_COD AND SB1.D_E_L_E_T_ = ' '
LEFT JOIN SZI010 SZI ON ZI_COD = B1_XXSGRP AND SZI.D_E_L_E_T_ = ' '
LEFT JOIN SBM010 SBM ON BM_GRUPO = B1_GRUPO AND SBM.D_E_L_E_T_ = ' '
WHERE  SD2.D_E_L_E_T_ = ' '  AND B1_MSBLQL = '2' AND B1_COD NOT LIKE '%-%'
GROUP BY D2_COD, B1_DESC ,B1_XXSGRP,ZI_DESC,BM_GRUPO,BM_DESC
)

SELECT '="'+COD+'"', SUBSTRING(DATA,7,2)+'/'+SUBSTRING(DATA,5,2)+'/'+SUBSTRING(DATA,1,4) , B1_DESC,TIPO ,B1_XXSGRP,ZI_DESC,'="'+BM_GRUPO+'"',BM_DESC
FROM PRD
--WHERE DATA <= '20211231'
ORDER BY DATA,COD, B1_DESC

-- 04/04/2024 Gravar o campo E2_XTIPOPG

SELECT 
 	 E2_XTIPOPG
	 ,F1_XTIPOPG
	 FROM SE2010 SE2 
	 LEFT JOIN SF1010 SF1 ON
	 	SE2.E2_FILIAL      = SF1.F1_FILIAL
	 	AND SE2.E2_NUM     = SF1.F1_DOC 
	 	AND SE2.E2_PREFIXO = SF1.F1_SERIE
	 	AND SE2.E2_FORNECE = SF1.F1_FORNECE
	 	AND SE2.E2_LOJA    = SF1.F1_LOJA
	 	AND SF1.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''
	 WHERE SE2.D_E_L_E_T_ = '' AND E2_XTIPOPG = ' ' AND F1_XTIPOPG <> ' '

	 UPDATE SE2010 SET E2_XTIPOPG = SF1.F1_XTIPOPG
	 	 FROM SE2010 SE2 
	 LEFT JOIN SF1010 SF1 ON
	 	SE2.E2_FILIAL      = SF1.F1_FILIAL
	 	AND SE2.E2_NUM     = SF1.F1_DOC 
	 	AND SE2.E2_PREFIXO = SF1.F1_SERIE
	 	AND SE2.E2_FORNECE = SF1.F1_FORNECE
	 	AND SE2.E2_LOJA    = SF1.F1_LOJA
	 	AND SF1.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''
	 WHERE SE2.D_E_L_E_T_ = '' AND E2_XTIPOPG = ' ' AND F1_XTIPOPG <> ' '

	 UPDATE SE2020 SET E2_XTIPOPG = SF1.F1_XTIPOPG
	 	 FROM SE2020 SE2 
	 LEFT JOIN SF1020 SF1 ON
	 	SE2.E2_FILIAL      = SF1.F1_FILIAL
	 	AND SE2.E2_NUM     = SF1.F1_DOC 
	 	AND SE2.E2_PREFIXO = SF1.F1_SERIE
	 	AND SE2.E2_FORNECE = SF1.F1_FORNECE
	 	AND SE2.E2_LOJA    = SF1.F1_LOJA
	 	AND SF1.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''
	 WHERE SE2.D_E_L_E_T_ = '' AND E2_XTIPOPG = ' ' AND F1_XTIPOPG <> ' '

	UPDATE SE2120 SET E2_XTIPOPG = SF1.F1_XTIPOPG
	 FROM SE2120 SE2 
	 LEFT JOIN SF1120 SF1 ON
	 	SE2.E2_FILIAL      = SF1.F1_FILIAL
	 	AND SE2.E2_NUM     = SF1.F1_DOC 
	 	AND SE2.E2_PREFIXO = SF1.F1_SERIE
	 	AND SE2.E2_FORNECE = SF1.F1_FORNECE
	 	AND SE2.E2_LOJA    = SF1.F1_LOJA
	 	AND SF1.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''
	 WHERE SE2.D_E_L_E_T_ = '' AND E2_XTIPOPG = ' ' AND F1_XTIPOPG <> ' '

	UPDATE SE2140 SET E2_XTIPOPG = SF1.F1_XTIPOPG
	 FROM SE2140 SE2 
	 LEFT JOIN SF1140 SF1 ON
	 	SE2.E2_FILIAL      = SF1.F1_FILIAL
	 	AND SE2.E2_NUM     = SF1.F1_DOC 
	 	AND SE2.E2_PREFIXO = SF1.F1_SERIE
	 	AND SE2.E2_FORNECE = SF1.F1_FORNECE
	 	AND SE2.E2_LOJA    = SF1.F1_LOJA
	 	AND SF1.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''
	 WHERE SE2.D_E_L_E_T_ = '' AND E2_XTIPOPG = ' ' AND F1_XTIPOPG <> ' '

-- 29/02/2024 - Copiar os eventos da empresa 14 para a 18

SELECT [NumEmpr]
      ,[CodTab]
      ,[CodEve]
      ,[DesEve]
      ,[usu_microsigac]
      ,[usu_microsigad]
      ,[usu_mesatr]
      ,[usu_profve]
      ,[usu_encben]
	  --INTO EVENTOS14
  FROM [BKIntegraRubi].[dbo].[FINANCE_EVENTOS_INTEGRA_CONTABIL] WHERE [NumEmpr] = 18

  UPDATE EVENTOS14 SET NumEmpr = 18 FROM EVENTOS14

  SELECT * FROM EVENTOS14

  INSERT INTO [FINANCE_EVENTOS_INTEGRA_CONTABIL] SELECT * FROM EVENTOS14

-- 19/02/2024 - Ajuste SX2 da empresa 19

UPDATE SX2190 SET SX2190.X2_ARQUIVO = SX2180.X2_ARQUIVO FROM SX2180
inner join SX2190 ON SX2190.X2_CHAVE = SX2180.X2_CHAVE
WHERE SUBSTRING(SX2180.X2_ARQUIVO,4,3) = '010'

--SZ2
SELECT * FROM SZ2010 WHERE (Z2_DATAPGT = '20240212' OR Z2_DATAPGT = '20240213' OR Z2_DATAPGT = '20240210' OR Z2_DATAPGT = '20240211')
UPDATE SZ2010 SET Z2_DATAPGT = '20240214' WHERE (Z2_DATAPGT = '20240212' OR Z2_DATAPGT = '20240213' OR Z2_DATAPGT = '20240210' OR Z2_DATAPGT = '20240211')

--SE2

-- 28/12/23  - IRRF retido na Fonte - bk_senior

-- IRRF Lanado: 1.472.597,20
-- Query        -1.471.875.30



WITH FOLHA AS (
SELECT
SUBSTRING(REPLACE(STR(bk_senior.bk_senior.R046VER.NumEmp,2),' ','0'),1,2) COLLATE Latin1_General_BIN AS EMPRESA,
   (CASE WHEN bk_senior.bk_senior.R046VER.NumEmp = 14 AND 
			SUBSTRING(BKIntegraRubi.dbo.CUSTOSIGA.ccSiga,1,3) IN ('000','Er:') THEN '302000508'
         WHEN bk_senior.bk_senior.R046VER.NumEmp = 15 AND 
	        SUBSTRING(BKIntegraRubi.dbo.CUSTOSIGA.ccSiga,1,3) IN ('000','Er:') THEN '305000554'
         WHEN bk_senior.bk_senior.R046VER.NumEmp = 16 AND 
	        SUBSTRING(BKIntegraRubi.dbo.CUSTOSIGA.ccSiga,1,3) IN ('000','Er:') THEN '386000609'
	  ELSE SUBSTRING(BKIntegraRubi.dbo.CUSTOSIGA.ccSiga,1,9) END) COLLATE Latin1_General_BIN AS CONTRATO,
SUBSTRING(CONVERT(VARCHAR,PerRef,112),1,6) COLLATE Latin1_General_BIN AS COMPETAM,
bk_senior.bk_senior.R046VER.CodEve AS EVENTO,
UPPER(bk_senior.bk_senior.R008EVC.DesEve) COLLATE Latin1_General_BIN AS DESCREVENTO,
bk_senior.bk_senior.R008EVC.TipEve AS TIPOEVENTO,
(CASE WHEN bk_senior.bk_senior.R008EVC.TipEve = 3
		   THEN -bk_senior.bk_senior.R046VER.ValEve 
      ELSE bk_senior.bk_senior.R046VER.ValEve END) AS VALOR
FROM bk_senior.bk_senior.R046VER 
INNER JOIN bk_senior.bk_senior.R044cal  
           ON  bk_senior.bk_senior.R046VER.NumEmp = bk_senior.bk_senior.R044cal.NumEmp
           AND bk_senior.bk_senior.R046VER.CodCal= bk_senior.bk_senior.R044cal.Codcal
INNER JOIN BKIntegraRubi.dbo.CUSTOSIGA 
		ON bk_senior.bk_senior.R046VER.NumEmp= BKIntegraRubi.dbo.CUSTOSIGA.NumEmp
		AND bk_senior.bk_senior.R046VER.NumCad = BKIntegraRubi.dbo.CUSTOSIGA.Numcad
		AND bk_senior.bk_senior.R046VER.TipCol = BKIntegraRubi.dbo.CUSTOSIGA.TipCol
		AND bk_senior.bk_senior.R044cal.Codcal = BKIntegraRubi.dbo.CUSTOSIGA.Codcal
INNER JOIN bk_senior.bk_senior.R008EVC 
		ON bk_senior.bk_senior.R046VER.TabEve = bk_senior.bk_senior.R008EVC.CodTab
		AND bk_senior.bk_senior.R046VER.CodEve = bk_senior.bk_senior.R008EVC.CodEve
LEFT JOIN bk_senior.bk_senior.R034FUN 
	ON 	bk_senior.bk_senior.R046VER.NumEmp = bk_senior.bk_senior.R034FUN.numemp
	AND bk_senior.bk_senior.R046VER.NumCad = bk_senior.bk_senior.R034FUN.numcad
	AND bk_senior.bk_senior.R046VER.TipCol = bk_senior.bk_senior.R034FUN.tipcol
LEFT JOIN bk_senior.bk_senior.R024CAR 
	ON 	bk_senior.bk_senior.R034FUN.codcar = bk_senior.bk_senior.R024CAR.CodCar
	AND	bk_senior.bk_senior.R024CAR.EstCar = 1
WHERE 
Tipcal IN(11) AND Sitcal = 'T'
AND bk_senior.bk_senior.R046VER.NumEmp = '01'
AND SUBSTRING(CONVERT(VARCHAR,PerRef,112),1,6) COLLATE Latin1_General_BIN = '202310'
AND UPPER(bk_senior.bk_senior.R008EVC.DesEve) COLLATE Latin1_General_BIN LIKE '%IRRF%'
--AND (bk_senior.bk_senior.R046VER.CodEve = 304 OR bk_senior.bk_senior.R046VER.CodEve = 308)
), FOLHA2 AS (
SELECT EMPRESA,CONTRATO,COMPETAM,EVENTO,DESCREVENTO,TIPOEVENTO,SUM(VALOR) AS VALOR FROM FOLHA
GROUP BY EMPRESA,CONTRATO,COMPETAM,EVENTO,DESCREVENTO,TIPOEVENTO
)
SELECT CONTRATO,SUM(VALOR) FROM FOLHA2 
GROUP BY CONTRATO
ORDER BY CONTRATO

--SELECT SUM(VALOR) FROM FOLHA2

UPDATE SE2160 SET E2_HIST = 'Depto Pessoal - EXAME MEDICO' WHERE E2_XXTIPBK = 'EXM' AND E2_HIST = 'Depto Pessoal'
UPDATE SE2160 SET E2_HIST = 'Depto Pessoal - REEMBOLSO' WHERE E2_XXTIPBK = 'REE' AND E2_HIST = 'Depto Pessoal'
UPDATE SE2160 SET E2_HIST = 'Depto Pessoal - DIARIA DE CAMPO' WHERE E2_XXTIPBK = 'DCH' AND E2_HIST = 'Depto Pessoal'
UPDATE SE2160 SET E2_HIST = 'Depto Pessoal - GRATIFICACAO' WHERE E2_XXTIPBK = 'GRA' AND E2_HIST = 'Depto Pessoal'
UPDATE SE2160 SET E2_HIST = 'Depto Pessoal - HORAS EXTRAS' WHERE E2_XXTIPBK = 'HEX' AND E2_HIST = 'Depto Pessoal'
UPDATE SE2160 SET E2_HIST = 'Depto Pessoal - DIN' WHERE E2_XXTIPBK = 'DIN' AND E2_HIST = 'Depto Pessoal'

UPDATE SE2160 SET E2_HIST = 'Despesas de Viagem - SOLICITACAO' WHERE E2_XXTIPBK = 'SOL' AND E2_HIST = 'Despesas de Viagem'
UPDATE SE2160 SET E2_HIST = 'Despesas de Viagem - HOSPEDAGEM' WHERE E2_XXTIPBK = 'HOS' AND E2_HIST = 'Despesas de Viagem'

WHERE B1_DESC LIKE '%BALSA NOVA%'
UPDATE SB1180 SET B1_DESC = REPLACE(B1_DESC,'BALSA NOVA','BK VIA') WHERE B1_DESC LIKE '%BALSA NOVA%'

-- 23/11/23  Preencher C9_XXMOT COM CNA_XXMOT
SELECT C9_PEDIDO,C5_NUM,C5_MDCONTR,C5_MDPLANI,C5_XXREV,CNA_NUMERO,CNA_CONTRA,CNA_REVISA,CNA_XXMOT,C9_XXMOT 
--UPDATE SC9010 SET C9_XXMOT = CNA_XXMOT 
FROM SC9010 SC9
INNER JOIN SC5010 SC5 ON C5_NUM = C9_PEDIDO AND SC5.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''
INNER JOIN CNA010 CNA ON CNA_CONTRA = C5_MDCONTR AND CNA_NUMERO = C5_MDPLANI AND CNA_REVISA = C5_XXREV AND CNA.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''
WHERE  SC9.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''
--AND C5_EMISSAO = '20231122'

UPDATE SC9020 SET C9_XXMOT = CNA_XXMOT 
FROM SC9020 SC9
INNER JOIN SC5020 SC5 ON C5_NUM = C9_PEDIDO AND SC5.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''
INNER JOIN CNA020 CNA ON CNA_CONTRA = C5_MDCONTR AND CNA_NUMERO = C5_MDPLANI AND CNA_REVISA = C5_XXREV AND CNA.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''
WHERE  SC9.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''

UPDATE SC9140 SET C9_XXMOT = CNA_XXMOT 
FROM SC9140 SC9
INNER JOIN SC5140 SC5 ON C5_NUM = C9_PEDIDO AND SC5.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''
INNER JOIN CNA140 CNA ON CNA_CONTRA = C5_MDCONTR AND CNA_NUMERO = C5_MDPLANI AND CNA_REVISA = C5_XXREV AND CNA.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''
WHERE  SC9.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''

-- 29/11/23  Preencher C9_XXMUN COM CNA_XXMUN
SELECT C9_PEDIDO,C5_NUM,C5_MDCONTR,C5_MDPLANI,C5_XXREV,CNA_NUMERO,CNA_CONTRA,CNA_REVISA,CNA_XXMUN,C9_XXMUN
--UPDATE SC9010 SET C9_XXMUN = CNA_XXMUN
FROM SC9010 SC9
INNER JOIN SC5010 SC5 ON C5_NUM = C9_PEDIDO AND SC5.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''
INNER JOIN CNA010 CNA ON CNA_CONTRA = C5_MDCONTR AND CNA_NUMERO = C5_MDPLANI AND CNA_REVISA = C5_XXREV AND CNA.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''
WHERE  SC9.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''
--AND C5_EMISSAO = '20231122'

UPDATE SC9020 SET C9_XXMUN = CNA_XXMUN
FROM SC9020 SC9
INNER JOIN SC5020 SC5 ON C5_NUM = C9_PEDIDO AND SC5.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''
INNER JOIN CNA020 CNA ON CNA_CONTRA = C5_MDCONTR AND CNA_NUMERO = C5_MDPLANI AND CNA_REVISA = C5_XXREV AND CNA.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''
WHERE  SC9.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''

UPDATE SC9140 SET C9_XXMUN = CNA_XXMUN
FROM SC9140 SC9
INNER JOIN SC5140 SC5 ON C5_NUM = C9_PEDIDO AND SC5.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''
INNER JOIN CNA140 CNA ON CNA_CONTRA = C5_MDCONTR AND CNA_NUMERO = C5_MDPLANI AND CNA_REVISA = C5_XXREV AND CNA.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''
WHERE  SC9.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''

UPDATE SE2140 SET E2_VENCREA = '20231117' WHERE E2_VENCREA = '20231120' AND (E2_TIPO = 'TX' or E2_TIPO = 'INS')

SELECT MAX(D1_ITEM),D1_SERIE,D1_DOC,D1_FORNECE,D1_DTDIGIT,SUM(D1_TOTAL) 
FROM SD1010 
WHERE D1_COD ='21301004' AND D_E_L_E_T_ = '' AND D1_DTDIGIT > '2019'
GROUP BY D1_SERIE,D1_DOC,D1_DTDIGIT,D1_FORNECE
ORDER BY D1_DTDIGIT,D1_SERIE,D1_DOC,D1_FORNECE


SELECT MAX(D1_ITEM),D1_SERIE,D1_DOC,D1_FORNECE,D1_DTDIGIT,SUM(D1_TOTAL),D_E_L_E_T_ 
FROM SD1010 
WHERE D1_COD ='21301004'  AND D1_DTDIGIT > '2019'
GROUP BY D1_SERIE,D1_DOC,D1_DTDIGIT,D_E_L_E_T_,D1_FORNECE
ORDER BY D1_DTDIGIT,D1_SERIE,D1_DOC,D_E_L_E_T_,D1_FORNECE

--06/11/23 - REMOVER CUMULATIVO 
SELECT D2_DOC,D2_TES,D2_EMISSAO,D2_BASIMP5,D2_VALIMP5,D2_ALQIMP5,ROUND(D2_BASIMP5 * 7.6 /100,2) AS IMP5,
                  D2_BASIMP6,D2_VALIMP6,D2_ALQIMP6,ROUND(D2_BASIMP6 * 1.65 /100,2) AS IMP6

FROM SD2010 WHERE D2_TES = '506' AND D_E_L_E_T_ = '' AND D2_DOC IN ('000010715','000011093','000011365') AND D2_SERIE = '001'

UPDATE SD2010 SET D2_ALQIMP5 = 7.6,D2_ALQIMP6 = 1.65,D2_VALIMP5 = ROUND(D2_BASIMP5 * 7.6 /100,2),D2_VALIMP6 = ROUND(D2_BASIMP6 * 1.65 /100,2) 
FROM SD2010 WHERE D2_TES = '506' AND D_E_L_E_T_ = '' AND D2_DOC IN ('000010715','000011093','000011365') AND D2_SERIE = '001'

SELECT F2_DOC,F2_EMISSAO,F2_VALIMP5,F2_VALIMP6 FROM SF2010 
WHERE F2_SERIE = '001' AND F2_DOC IN ('000010715','000011093','000011365') 
AND D_E_L_E_T_ =''

UPDATE SF2010 SET F2_VALIMP5 = ROUND(F2_BASIMP5 * 7.6 /100,2),F2_VALIMP6 = ROUND(F2_BASIMP6 * 1.65 /100,2) 
WHERE F2_SERIE = '001' AND F2_DOC IN ('000010715','000011093','000011365') 
AND D_E_L_E_T_ =''

SELECT * FROM SF4010 WHERE F4_CODIGO IN ('506','510')

WHERE SUBSTRING(B1_CONTA,1,1) = '1' AND SB1010.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''
ORDER BY CT1_CONTA

SELECT Z5_CC,CTT.CTT_DESC01,Z5_EVENTO,SUM(Z5_VALOR) FROM SZ5010 SZ5
LEFT JOIN CTT010 CTT ON CTT_CUSTO = Z5_CC AND CTT.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''
WHERE Z5_EVDESCR LIKE '%FGTS%'
AND Z5_ANOMES = '202309'
AND SZ5.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''
GROUP BY Z5_CC,CTT.CTT_DESC01,Z5_EVENTO
ORDER BY CTT.CTT_DESC01,Z5_CC,Z5_EVENTO
--SELECT 1159634.51 - 1159949.03

LEFT JOIN CTT010 CTT ON CTT_CUSTO = Z5_CC AND CTT.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''
WHERE Z5_EVDESCR LIKE '%FGTS%'
AND Z5_ANOMES = '202309'
AND SZ5.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''
--GROUP BY Z5_CC,CTT.CTT_DESC01,Z5_EVENTO
ORDER BY CTT.CTT_DESC01,Z5_CC,Z5_EVENTO

LEFT JOIN SED010 ON ED_CODIGO = SA1.A1_NATUREZ
WHERE A1_COD IN ('000161','000368','000190','000302','000359','000049','000380','000032','000290','000040','000309')
AND SA1.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''
ORDER BY A1_NATUREZ


SELECT * FROM SED010 WHERE ED_CODIGO = '0000000044' OR ED_PERCIRF = 4.8
SELECT * FROM SED010 WHERE ED_CODIGO = '0000000045' OR ED_PERCIRF = 4.8
SELECT * FROM SED010 WHERE ED_CODIGO = '0000000046' OR ED_PERCIRF = 4.8
SELECT * FROM SED010 WHERE ED_CODIGO = '0000000047' OR ED_PERCIRF = 4.8
SELECT * FROM SED010 WHERE ED_CODIGO = '0000000048' OR ED_PERCIRF = 4.8

UPDATE SA1010 SET A1_NATUREZ = '0000000089' WHERE A1_COD = '000032'
UPDATE SA1010 SET A1_NATUREZ = '0000000089' WHERE A1_COD IN ('000040','000190','000368')
UPDATE SA1010 SET A1_NATUREZ = '0000000001' WHERE A1_COD IN ('000049','000302')
UPDATE SA1010 SET A1_NATUREZ = '0000000089' WHERE A1_COD IN ('000309','000380','000290','000359')

AND CNA_XXNAT <> ' ' AND D_E_L_E_T_ = ''

==============================================================

-- 14/10/2023|08:15:22|01|000000-Administrador|6|SIGAFIN|FINA750|P12|
--set statistics io,time on

WITH RESUMO AS ( 
 SELECT 
	  '01' AS EMPRESA
	 ,'BK' AS NOMEEMP
	 ,E2_TIPO
	 ,E2_PREFIXO
	 ,E2_NUM
	 ,E2_PARCELA
	 ,F1_DOC
	 ,E2_FORNECE
	 ,E2_PORTADO
	 ,E2_LOJA
	 ,E2_HIST
	 ,E2_USERLGI
	 ,E2_BAIXA
	 ,E2_VENCREA
	 ,E2_VALOR
	 ,A2_NOME
	 ,A2_TIPO
	 ,A2_CGC
	 ,(CASE WHEN E2_SALDO = E2_VALOR 
	 		THEN E2_VALOR + E2_ACRESC - E2_DECRESC
	 		ELSE E2_SALDO END) AS SALDO
	 ,F1_XTIPOPG
	 ,(CASE WHEN (F1_XTIPOPG IS NULL) AND (Z2_BANCO IS NULL) THEN E2_TIPO+' '+E2_PORTADO
			WHEN F1_XTIPOPG IS NULL AND (E2_PORTADO IS NOT NULL) THEN 'LF '+E2_PORTADO
			ELSE F1_XTIPOPG END) AS FORMPGT
	 ,F1_XNUMPA
	 ,F1_XBANCO
	 ,F1_XAGENC
	 ,F1_XNUMCON
	 ,F1_XXTPPIX
	 ,F1_XXCHPIX 
	 ,F1_USERLGI
	 ,F1_XXUSER
  ,CONVERT(VARCHAR(800),CONVERT(Binary(800),D1_XXHIST)) AS D1_XXHIST 
  ,Z2_BANCO

	 FROM SE2010 SE2 
	 LEFT JOIN SF1010 SF1 ON
	 	SE2.E2_FILIAL      = SF1.F1_FILIAL
	 	AND SE2.E2_NUM     = SF1.F1_DOC 
	 	AND SE2.E2_PREFIXO = SF1.F1_SERIE
	 	AND SE2.E2_FORNECE = SF1.F1_FORNECE
	 	AND SE2.E2_LOJA    = SF1.F1_LOJA
	 	AND SF1.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''
	 LEFT JOIN SA2010  SA2 ON
	 	SA2.A2_FILIAL      = '  '
	 	AND SE2.E2_FORNECE = SA2.A2_COD
	 	AND SE2.E2_LOJA    = SA2.A2_LOJA
	 	AND SA2.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''
 LEFT JOIN SD1010 SD1 ON SD1.D_E_L_E_T_=''
   AND D1_FILIAL  = '01' 
   AND D1_DOC     = F1_DOC
   AND D1_SERIE   = F1_SERIE
   AND D1_FORNECE = F1_FORNECE
   AND D1_LOJA    = F1_LOJA
   AND SD1.R_E_C_N_O_ = 
   	(SELECT TOP 1 R_E_C_N_O_ FROM SD1010 SD1T 
   	  WHERE SD1T.D_E_L_E_T_     = '' 
   	        AND SD1T.D1_FILIAL  = '01' 
   			AND SD1T.D1_DOC     = F1_DOC
   			AND SD1T.D1_SERIE   = F1_SERIE
   			AND SD1T.D1_FORNECE = F1_FORNECE
   			AND SD1T.D1_LOJA    = F1_LOJA
		 ORDER BY D1_ITEM)

 LEFT JOIN SZ2010 SZ2 ON SZ2.D_E_L_E_T_=''
	 		AND SZ2.Z2_CODEMP  = '01' 
	 		AND SE2.E2_PREFIXO = SZ2.Z2_E2PRF
	 		AND SE2.E2_NUM     = SZ2.Z2_E2NUM 
	 		AND SE2.E2_PARCELA = SZ2.Z2_E2PARC
	 		AND SE2.E2_TIPO    = SZ2.Z2_E2TIPO
	 		AND SE2.E2_FORNECE = SZ2.Z2_E2FORN
	 		AND SE2.E2_LOJA    = SZ2.Z2_E2LOJA
	 		AND SZ2.Z2_STATUS  = 'S'
		    AND SZ2.R_E_C_N_O_ = 
   	(SELECT TOP 1 R_E_C_N_O_ FROM SZ2010 SZ2T 
   	  WHERE SZ2T.D_E_L_E_T_     = '' 
	 		AND SZ2.Z2_CODEMP  = '01' 
	 		AND SE2.E2_PREFIXO = SZ2T.Z2_E2PRF
	 		AND SE2.E2_NUM     = SZ2T.Z2_E2NUM 
	 		AND SE2.E2_PARCELA = SZ2T.Z2_E2PARC
	 		AND SE2.E2_TIPO    = SZ2T.Z2_E2TIPO
	 		AND SE2.E2_FORNECE = SZ2T.Z2_E2FORN
	 		AND SE2.E2_LOJA    = SZ2T.Z2_E2LOJA
	 		AND SZ2T.Z2_STATUS  = 'S'
		 ORDER BY SZ2T.R_E_C_N_O_)

	 WHERE SE2.D_E_L_E_T_ = '' 
  AND E2_VENCREA = '20231016' 
)
SELECT 
  * 
  
  ,ISNULL(D1_XXHIST,E2_HIST) AS HIST
  FROM RESUMO 
 ORDER BY
    EMPRESA,FORMPGT


==============================================================
--Tabelas do SIGCT que devem ter a mesma configurao de Compartilhamento

-- https://tdn.totvs.com/display/public/PROT/GCT0010+-+Compartilhamento+Tabelas+SIGAGCT


CN1 - Tipo contrato
CNL - Tipo planilha
CN8 - Caues
CN9 - Contrato
CNA - Planilha
CNB - Itens planilha
CNC - Fornecedor x contrato
CNF - Cronograma financeiro
CNG - Histrico do Contrato
CNH - Vinc. Multas vs. Contrato
CNI - Notas Fiscais de Cauo
CNK - Documentos Contratuais
CNM - Avaliao Contrato x Fornecedor
CNN - Amarrao Usurio x Contrato
CNS - Cronograma Fsico
CNT - Caues Retidas
CNU - Contratos x Vendedores
CNV - Cabealho Cronograma Contbil
CNW - Parcelas Cronograma Contbil
CNX - Adiantamentos de Contrato
CNY - Baixas Reteno
CNZ - Rateio itens do contrato
CPD - Filial x contrato
CXI - Partes Envolvidas do Contrato
CXK - Cabealho do Reajuste
CXL - Itens do Reajuste Automtico
CXM - Agrupadores Estoque por Planilha
CXO - Mltiplas Naturezas
CXP - Distrib de Naturezas em CC

Tabelas Medio

CND - Cabealho Medio de Contratos
CNE - Itens da Medio de Contratos
CXN - Planilha Med. de Contratos
CNQ - Amarrao Med x Descontos
CNR - Amarrao Medio x Multas
CZY - Medio x Adiantamento
CXJ - Amar Ped x Med x Pla x Part

SELECT * FROM SX2010 WHERE X2_CHAVE IN ('CN1','CNL','CN8','CN9','CNA','CNB','CNC','CNF','CNG','CNH','CNI','CNK','CNM','CNN','CNS','CNT','CNU','CNV','CNW','CNX','CNY','CNZ','CPD','CXI','CXK','CXL','CXM','CXO','CXP','CND','CNE','CXN','CNQ','CNR','CZY','CXJ')

SELECT X2_MODO,X2_MODOUN,X2_MODOEMP FROM SX2010 WHERE X2_CHAVE = 'CZY'
UPDATE SX2010 SET X2_MODO = 'E',X2_MODOUN= 'E',X2_MODOEMP= 'E' FROM SX2010 WHERE X2_CHAVE = 'CZY'

UPDATE SX2040 SET X2_MODO = 'E',X2_MODOUN= 'E',X2_MODOEMP= 'E' WHERE X2_CHAVE = 'CZY'
UPDATE SX2060 SET X2_MODO = 'E',X2_MODOUN= 'E',X2_MODOEMP= 'E' WHERE X2_CHAVE = 'CZY'
UPDATE SX2070 SET X2_MODO = 'E',X2_MODOUN= 'E',X2_MODOEMP= 'E' WHERE X2_CHAVE = 'CZY'
UPDATE SX2080 SET X2_MODO = 'E',X2_MODOUN= 'E',X2_MODOEMP= 'E' WHERE X2_CHAVE = 'CZY'
UPDATE SX2090 SET X2_MODO = 'E',X2_MODOUN= 'E',X2_MODOEMP= 'E' WHERE X2_CHAVE = 'CZY'
UPDATE SX2100 SET X2_MODO = 'E',X2_MODOUN= 'E',X2_MODOEMP= 'E' WHERE X2_CHAVE = 'CZY'
UPDATE SX2110 SET X2_MODO = 'E',X2_MODOUN= 'E',X2_MODOEMP= 'E' WHERE X2_CHAVE = 'CZY'
UPDATE SX2120 SET X2_MODO = 'E',X2_MODOUN= 'E',X2_MODOEMP= 'E' WHERE X2_CHAVE = 'CZY'

UPDATE SX2150 SET X2_MODO = 'E',X2_MODOUN= 'E',X2_MODOEMP= 'E' WHERE X2_CHAVE = 'CZY'

-- 03/10/2023 Base do INSS Patronal 
SELECT 
	BKIntegraRubi.dbo.CUSTOSIGA.ccSiga,
	bk_senior.bk_senior.R046VER.CodEve AS CodEve,
	bk_senior.bk_senior.R008EVC.DesEve,
	COUNT(bk_senior.bk_senior.R046VER.CodEve) AS nCont,
	SUM(bk_senior.bk_senior.R046VER.ValEve) as valevent,
	bk_senior.bk_senior.R008EVC.TipEve,
	bk_senior.bk_senior.R008INC.IncInm,
	bk_senior.bk_senior.R008INC.IncInd,
	bk_senior.bk_senior.R008INC.IncIna
FROM bk_senior.bk_senior.R046VER 
	INNER JOIN bk_senior.bk_senior.R044cal ON 
		bk_senior.bk_senior.R046VER.NumEmp= bk_senior.bk_senior.R044cal.NumEmp
		AND bk_senior.bk_senior.R046VER.CodCal= bk_senior.bk_senior.R044cal.Codcal
	INNER JOIN BKIntegraRubi.dbo.CUSTOSIGA ON 
		bk_senior.bk_senior.R046VER.NumEmp= BKIntegraRubi.dbo.CUSTOSIGA.NumEmp
		AND bk_senior.bk_senior.R046VER.NumCad = BKIntegraRubi.dbo.CUSTOSIGA.Numcad
		AND bk_senior.bk_senior.R046VER.TipCol = BKIntegraRubi.dbo.CUSTOSIGA.TipCol
		AND bk_senior.bk_senior.R044cal.Codcal = BKIntegraRubi.dbo.CUSTOSIGA.Codcal
	INNER JOIN bk_senior.bk_senior.R008EVC ON 
		bk_senior.bk_senior.R046VER.TabEve = bk_senior.bk_senior.R008EVC.CodTab
		AND bk_senior.bk_senior.R046VER.CodEve = bk_senior.bk_senior.R008EVC.CodEve
	INNER JOIN bk_senior.bk_senior.R008INC ON 
		bk_senior.bk_senior.R046VER.TabEve = bk_senior.bk_senior.R008INC.CodTab
		AND bk_senior.bk_senior.R046VER.CodEve = bk_senior.bk_senior.R008INC.CodEve
 WHERE 
	bk_senior.bk_senior.R046VER.NumEmp='01' 
	AND (bk_senior.bk_senior.R008INC.IncInm = '+' OR bk_senior.bk_senior.R008INC.IncInd = '+' OR bk_senior.bk_senior.R008INC.incina = '+')
	AND Tipcal In(11) And Sitcal = 'T' 
	AND PerRef ='20230701'
	AND BKIntegraRubi.dbo.CUSTOSIGA.ccSiga = '333000521'

 GROUP BY 
	BKIntegraRubi.dbo.CUSTOSIGA.ccSiga,
	bk_senior.bk_senior.R046VER.CodEve,
	bk_senior.bk_senior.R008EVC.DesEve,
	bk_senior.bk_senior.R008EVC.TipEve,
	bk_senior.bk_senior.R008INC.IncInm,
	bk_senior.bk_senior.R008INC.IncInd,
	bk_senior.bk_senior.R008INC.IncIna
 ORDER BY 
	BKIntegraRubi.dbo.CUSTOSIGA.ccSiga,
	bk_senior.bk_senior.R046VER.CodEve,
	bk_senior.bk_senior.R008EVC.DesEve,
	bk_senior.bk_senior.R008EVC.TipEve,
	bk_senior.bk_senior.R008INC.IncInm,
	bk_senior.bk_senior.R008INC.IncInd,
	bk_senior.bk_senior.R008INC.IncIna

 --select * from bk_senior.bk_senior.R008EVC WHERE CodEve in (1,126,222,935,28) order by CodEve
 --select IncInm,IncInd,IncIna,* from bk_senior.bk_senior.R008INC

--select 6789.65+2669.83+2992.05+978.17
--select 13429.70 * .2


-- Total por CC
SELECT 
	BKIntegraRubi.dbo.CUSTOSIGA.ccSiga,
	SUM(bk_senior.bk_senior.R046VER.ValEve) as valevent
FROM bk_senior.bk_senior.R046VER 
	INNER JOIN bk_senior.bk_senior.R044cal ON 
		bk_senior.bk_senior.R046VER.NumEmp= bk_senior.bk_senior.R044cal.NumEmp
		AND bk_senior.bk_senior.R046VER.CodCal= bk_senior.bk_senior.R044cal.Codcal
	INNER JOIN BKIntegraRubi.dbo.CUSTOSIGA ON 
		bk_senior.bk_senior.R046VER.NumEmp= BKIntegraRubi.dbo.CUSTOSIGA.NumEmp
		AND bk_senior.bk_senior.R046VER.NumCad = BKIntegraRubi.dbo.CUSTOSIGA.Numcad
		AND bk_senior.bk_senior.R046VER.TipCol = BKIntegraRubi.dbo.CUSTOSIGA.TipCol
		AND bk_senior.bk_senior.R044cal.Codcal = BKIntegraRubi.dbo.CUSTOSIGA.Codcal
	INNER JOIN bk_senior.bk_senior.R008EVC ON 
		bk_senior.bk_senior.R046VER.TabEve = bk_senior.bk_senior.R008EVC.CodTab
		AND bk_senior.bk_senior.R046VER.CodEve = bk_senior.bk_senior.R008EVC.CodEve
	INNER JOIN bk_senior.bk_senior.R008INC ON 
		bk_senior.bk_senior.R046VER.TabEve = bk_senior.bk_senior.R008INC.CodTab
		AND bk_senior.bk_senior.R046VER.CodEve = bk_senior.bk_senior.R008INC.CodEve
 WHERE 
	bk_senior.bk_senior.R046VER.NumEmp='01' 
	AND (bk_senior.bk_senior.R008INC.IncInm = '+' OR bk_senior.bk_senior.R008INC.IncInd = '+' OR bk_senior.bk_senior.R008INC.incina = '+')
	AND Tipcal In(11) And Sitcal = 'T' 
	AND MONTH(PerRef) = 5 AND YEAR(PerRef) = 2023

 GROUP BY 
	BKIntegraRubi.dbo.CUSTOSIGA.ccSiga
 ORDER BY 
	BKIntegraRubi.dbo.CUSTOSIGA.ccSiga

-- Total
SELECT 
	SUM(bk_senior.bk_senior.R046VER.ValEve) as valevent
FROM bk_senior.bk_senior.R046VER 
	INNER JOIN bk_senior.bk_senior.R044cal ON 
		bk_senior.bk_senior.R046VER.NumEmp= bk_senior.bk_senior.R044cal.NumEmp
		AND bk_senior.bk_senior.R046VER.CodCal= bk_senior.bk_senior.R044cal.Codcal
	INNER JOIN BKIntegraRubi.dbo.CUSTOSIGA ON 
		bk_senior.bk_senior.R046VER.NumEmp= BKIntegraRubi.dbo.CUSTOSIGA.NumEmp
		AND bk_senior.bk_senior.R046VER.NumCad = BKIntegraRubi.dbo.CUSTOSIGA.Numcad
		AND bk_senior.bk_senior.R046VER.TipCol = BKIntegraRubi.dbo.CUSTOSIGA.TipCol
		AND bk_senior.bk_senior.R044cal.Codcal = BKIntegraRubi.dbo.CUSTOSIGA.Codcal
	INNER JOIN bk_senior.bk_senior.R008EVC ON 
		bk_senior.bk_senior.R046VER.TabEve = bk_senior.bk_senior.R008EVC.CodTab
		AND bk_senior.bk_senior.R046VER.CodEve = bk_senior.bk_senior.R008EVC.CodEve
	INNER JOIN bk_senior.bk_senior.R008INC ON 
		bk_senior.bk_senior.R046VER.TabEve = bk_senior.bk_senior.R008INC.CodTab
		AND bk_senior.bk_senior.R046VER.CodEve = bk_senior.bk_senior.R008INC.CodEve
 WHERE 
	bk_senior.bk_senior.R046VER.NumEmp='01' 
	AND (bk_senior.bk_senior.R008INC.IncInm = '+' OR bk_senior.bk_senior.R008INC.IncInd = '+' OR bk_senior.bk_senior.R008INC.incina = '+')
	AND Tipcal In(11) And Sitcal = 'T' 
	AND MONTH(PerRef) = 5 AND YEAR(PerRef) = 2023

20/09/23 - Testes userlga

     SELECT 
         B1_COD, 
         B1_DESC, 
         B1_TIPO, 
          
         USR_I.USR_ID AS USRINC_COD, 
         USR_I.USR_NOME AS USRINC_NOM, 
         --CONVERT(VARCHAR,DATEADD(DAY,CONVERT(INT,CONCAT(ASCII(SUBSTRING(B1_USERLGI,12,1)) - 50, ASCII(SUBSTRING(B1_USERLGI,16,1)) - 50)),'1996-01-01'), 112) AS DATA_INC, 
		 CONVERT(VARCHAR,DATEADD(DAY,((ASCII(SUBSTRING(B1_USERLGI,12,1)) - 50) * 100 + (ASCII(SUBSTRING(B1_USERLGI,16,1)) - 50)),'19960101') , 112) AS DATA_INC, 
        
         USR_A.USR_ID AS USRALT_COD, 
         USR_A.USR_NOME AS USRALT_NOM, 
         CASE WHEN SUBSTRING(B1_USERLGA, 03, 1) != ' ' THEN 
             CONVERT(VARCHAR,DATEADD(DAY,((ASCII(SUBSTRING(B1_USERLGA,12,1)) - 50) * 100 + (ASCII(SUBSTRING(B1_USERLGA,16,1)) - 50)),'1996-01-01'),112) 
         ELSE '' 
         END AS DATA_ALT 
     FROM 
         SB1010 SB1
         LEFT JOIN SYS_USR USR_I ON ( 
             USR_I.USR_ID = ( 
                 SUBSTRING(B1_USERLGI, 11, 1) + 
                 SUBSTRING(B1_USERLGI, 15, 1) + 
                 SUBSTRING(B1_USERLGI, 19, 1) + 
                 SUBSTRING(B1_USERLGI, 02, 1) + 
                 SUBSTRING(B1_USERLGI, 06, 1) + 
                 SUBSTRING(B1_USERLGI, 10, 1) + 
                 SUBSTRING(B1_USERLGI, 14, 1) + 
                 SUBSTRING(B1_USERLGI, 01, 1) + 
                 SUBSTRING(B1_USERLGI, 18, 1) + 
                 SUBSTRING(B1_USERLGI, 05, 1) + 
                 SUBSTRING(B1_USERLGI, 09, 1) + 
                 SUBSTRING(B1_USERLGI, 13, 1) + 
                 SUBSTRING(B1_USERLGI, 17, 1) + 
                 SUBSTRING(B1_USERLGI, 04, 1) + 
                 SUBSTRING(B1_USERLGI, 08, 1) 
             ) 
         ) 
         LEFT JOIN SYS_USR USR_A ON ( 
             USR_A.USR_ID = ( 
                 SUBSTRING(B1_USERLGA, 11, 1) + 
                 SUBSTRING(B1_USERLGA, 15, 1) + 
                 SUBSTRING(B1_USERLGA, 19, 1) + 
                 SUBSTRING(B1_USERLGA, 02, 1) + 
                 SUBSTRING(B1_USERLGA, 06, 1) + 
                 SUBSTRING(B1_USERLGA, 10, 1) + 
                 SUBSTRING(B1_USERLGA, 14, 1) + 
                 SUBSTRING(B1_USERLGA, 01, 1) + 
                 SUBSTRING(B1_USERLGA, 18, 1) + 
                 SUBSTRING(B1_USERLGA, 05, 1) + 
                 SUBSTRING(B1_USERLGA, 09, 1) + 
                 SUBSTRING(B1_USERLGA, 13, 1) + 
                 SUBSTRING(B1_USERLGA, 17, 1) + 
                 SUBSTRING(B1_USERLGA, 04, 1) + 
                 SUBSTRING(B1_USERLGA, 08, 1) 
             ) 
         ) 
     WHERE 
         B1_FILIAL = '01' 
         AND B1_MSBLQL != '1' 
         AND SB1.D_E_L_E_T_ = ' '

20/09/23 - Acerto campo CN9_LOGUSR

SELECT CN9_LOGUSR,CN9_USERGA ,

SUBSTRING(CN9_USERGI, 11, 1) + SUBSTRING(CN9_USERGI, 15, 1) +
SUBSTRING(CN9_USERGI, 2, 1) + SUBSTRING(CN9_USERGI, 6, 1) +
SUBSTRING(CN9_USERGI, 10, 1) + SUBSTRING(CN9_USERGI, 14, 1) CODIGO_USUARIO
, INC.USR_CODIGO NOME_USUARIO_INCLUSAO , ALT.USR_CODIGO NOME_USUARIO_ALTERACAO

FROM CN9010 CN9

LEFT JOIN SYS_USR ALT ON ALT.USR_ID = SUBSTRING(CN9_USERGA, 11, 1) + SUBSTRING(CN9_USERGA, 15, 1) + SUBSTRING(CN9_USERGA, 2, 1) + SUBSTRING(CN9_USERGA, 6, 1) + SUBSTRING(CN9_USERGA, 10, 1) + SUBSTRING(CN9_USERGA, 14, 1)
LEFT JOIN SYS_USR INC ON INC.USR_ID = SUBSTRING(CN9_USERGI, 11, 1) + SUBSTRING(CN9_USERGI, 15, 1) + SUBSTRING(CN9_USERGI, 2, 1) + SUBSTRING(CN9_USERGI, 6, 1) + SUBSTRING(CN9_USERGI, 10, 1) + SUBSTRING(CN9_USERGI, 14, 1)

UPDATE CN9010 SET CN9_LOGUSR = SUBSTRING(CN9_USERGA, 11, 1) + SUBSTRING(CN9_USERGA, 15, 1) +
SUBSTRING(CN9_USERGA, 2, 1) + SUBSTRING(CN9_USERGA, 6, 1) +
SUBSTRING(CN9_USERGA, 10, 1) + SUBSTRING(CN9_USERGA, 14, 1) WHERE CN9_LOGUSR = ' '

UPDATE CN9010 SET CN9_LOGUSR = SUBSTRING(CN9_USERGI, 11, 1) + SUBSTRING(CN9_USERGI, 15, 1) +
SUBSTRING(CN9_USERGI, 2, 1) + SUBSTRING(CN9_USERGI, 6, 1) +
SUBSTRING(CN9_USERGI, 10, 1) + SUBSTRING(CN9_USERGI, 14, 1) WHERE CN9_LOGUSR = ' '


-- ACERTO RETORNO DO BACKUP
SELECT * INTO CN9R FROM dataP10R.dbo.CN9010 

SELECT CN9.CN9_LOGUSR,CN9.CN9_USERGA , CN9R.CN9_LOGUSR,CN9R.CN9_USERGA , CN9.R_E_C_N_O_,CN9R.R_E_C_N_O_
FROM CN9010 CN9
LEFT JOIN CN9R ON CN9.R_E_C_N_O_ = CN9R.R_E_C_N_O_

UPDATE CN9010 SET CN9_USERGA = CN9R.CN9_USERGA 
FROM CN9010 CN9
LEFT JOIN CN9R ON CN9.R_E_C_N_O_ = CN9R.R_E_C_N_O_

UPDATE CN9010 SET CN9_LOGUSR = ' '

19/07/23 - CUMULATIVO
SELECT D2_DOC,D2_EMISSAO,D2_BASIMP5,D2_VALIMP5,D2_ALQIMP5,ROUND(D2_BASIMP5 * 3 /100,2) AS IMP5,
                  D2_BASIMP6,D2_VALIMP6,D2_ALQIMP6,ROUND(D2_BASIMP6 * 0.65 /100,2) AS IMP6

FROM SD2010 WHERE D2_TES = '510' AND D_E_L_E_T_ = '' AND D2_DOC IN ('000009916','000010200')

UPDATE SD2010 SET D2_ALQIMP5 = 3,D2_ALQIMP6 = 0.65,D2_VALIMP5 = ROUND(D2_BASIMP5 * 3 /100,2),D2_VALIMP6 = ROUND(D2_BASIMP6 * 0.65 /100,2) FROM SD2010 WHERE D2_TES = '510' AND D_E_L_E_T_ = '' AND D2_DOC IN ('000009916','000010200')

SELECT F2_DOC,F2_EMISSAO,F2_VALIMP5,F2_VALIMP6 FROM SF2010 
WHERE F2_SERIE = '001' AND F2_DOC IN ('000009916','000010200')
AND D_E_L_E_T_ =''

UPDATE SF2010 SET F2_VALIMP5 = ROUND(F2_BASIMP5 * 3 /100,2),F2_VALIMP6 = ROUND(F2_BASIMP6 * 0.65 /100,2) 
WHERE F2_SERIE = '001' AND F2_DOC IN ('000009916','000010200')
AND D_E_L_E_T_ =''

USE dataP12Tst
UPDATE SE5010 SET E5_RECONC = ' ' FROM SE5010

UPDATE SE1010 SET E1_VENCTO = E1_EMISSAO, E1_VENCREA = E1_EMISSAO, E1_MOVIMEN = E1_EMISSAO, E1_VENCORI = E1_EMISSAO  WHERE SUBSTRING(E1_EMISSAO,1,6) >= '201801' AND SE1010.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''

UPDATE SE1010 SET E1_BAIXA = E1_EMISSAO WHERE SUBSTRING(E1_EMISSAO,1,6) >= '201801' AND SE1010.D_E_L_E_T_ = '' AND E1_BAIXA <> ''

UPDATE SE5010 SET E5_DATA=E1_EMISSAO,E5_VENCTO=E1_EMISSAO,E5_DTDIGIT=E1_EMISSAO,E5_DTDISPO=E1_EMISSAO
 FROM SE5010 INNER JOIN SE1010 ON E5_FILIAL+E5_PREFIXO+E5_NUMERO+E5_PARCELA+E5_CLIFOR+E5_LOJA = E1_FILIAL+E1_PREFIXO+E1_NUM+E1_PARCELA+E1_CLIENTE+E1_LOJA 
WHERE SUBSTRING(E1_EMISSAO,1,6) >= '201801'  AND E1_BAIXA <> '' AND SE1010.D_E_L_E_T_ = '' AND SE5010.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''

UPDATE FK1010 SET FK1_DATA = E5_DATA FROM FK1010 INNER JOIN SE5010 ON FK1_IDFK1 = E5_IDORIG
WHERE SUBSTRING(E5_DATA,1,6) >= '201801'

-- Mai 2023
SELECT C5_NUM,C5_NOTA,C5_CLIENTE,C5_LOJACLI,C5_RECISS,A1_COD,A1_LOJA,A1_RECISS ,C5_NATUREZ,A1_NATUREZ,ED_CODIGO,ED_CALCISS
FROM SC5010 SC5
LEFT JOIN SA1010 SA1 ON A1_COD = C5_CLIENTE AND A1_LOJA = C5_LOJACLI AND SA1.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''
LEFT JOIN SED010 SED ON ED_CODIGO = C5_NATUREZ AND SED.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''
WHERE C5_NOTA IN ('000009734','000009738','000009742','000009746','000009892')
AND SC5.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''

SELECT C6_NUM,C6_NOTA,C6_PRODUTO
FROM SC6010 SC6
LEFT JOIN SB1010 SB1 ON B1_COD = C6_PRODUTO AND SB1.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''
WHERE C6_NOTA IN ('000009734','000009738','000009742','000009746','000009892')
AND SC6.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''

UPDATE SC5010 SET C5_RECISS = '1' FROM SC5010 WHERE C5_NOTA IN ('000009734','000009738','000009742','000009746','000009892')
UPDATE SA1010 SET A1_RECISS = '1' FROM SA1010 WHERE (A1_COD = '000371' OR A1_COD = '000103' OR A1_COD = '000008') AND A1_LOJA = '01'

                  D2_BASIMP6,D2_VALIMP6,D2_ALQIMP6,ROUND(D2_BASIMP6 * 0.65 /100,2) AS IMP6

FROM SD2010 WHERE D2_TES = '510' AND D_E_L_E_T_ = '' AND D2_EMISSAO < '20230504' 

--UPDATE SD2010 SET D2_ALQIMP5 = 3,D2_ALQIMP6 = 0.65,D2_VALIMP5 = ROUND(D2_BASIMP5 * 3 /100,2),D2_VALIMP6 = ROUND(D2_BASIMP6 * 0.65 /100,2) FROM SD2010 WHERE D2_TES = '510' AND D_E_L_E_T_ = '' AND D2_EMISSAO < '20230504' 

SELECT F2_DOC,F2_EMISSAO,F2_VALIMP5,F2_VALIMP6 FROM SF2010 
WHERE F2_SERIE = '001' AND F2_DOC IN ('000009049','000009342','000009349','000008687','000008687','000008697','000009053','000009059','000009629','000009629')

SELECT A2_COD,A2_LOJA,A2_NOME,A2_ULTCOM,F1_XXAVAL,F1_XXAVALI 
FROM SA2010 SA2
LEFT JOIN SF1010 SF1 ON F1_FORNECE = A2_COD AND A2_LOJA = F1_LOJA AND SA2.D_E_L_E_T_ = '' 
WHERE SA2.D_E_L_E_T_ = '' AND A2_MSBLQL <> '1'
GROUP BY A2_COD,A2_LOJA,A2_NOME,A2_ULTCOM,F1_XXAVAL,F1_XXAVALI 
ORDER BY A2_COD,A2_LOJA,A2_NOME,A2_ULTCOM,F1_XXAVAL,F1_XXAVALI

SELECT [Z2_FILIAL]
      ,[Z2_CTRID]
      ,[Z2_CODEMP]
      ,[Z2_PRONT]
      ,[Z2_NOME]
      ,[Z2_VALOR]
      ,[Z2_TIPO]
      ,[Z2_BANCO]
      ,[Z2_AGENCIA]
      ,[Z2_DIGAGEN]
      ,[Z2_CONTA]
      ,[Z2_DIGCONT]
      ,[Z2_STATUS]
      ,[Z2_DATAEMI]
      ,[Z2_DATAPGT]
      ,[Z2_USUARIO]
      ,[Z2_TITULO]
      ,[Z2_CALC]
      ,[D_E_L_E_T_]
      ,[R_E_C_N_O_]
      ,[Z2_CODFOR]
      ,[Z2_LOJFOR]
      ,[Z2_PRODUTO]
      ,[Z2_TIPOPES]
      ,[Z2_CC]
      ,[Z2_E2PRF]
      ,[Z2_E2NUM]
      ,[Z2_E2PARC]
      ,[Z2_E2TIPO]
      ,[Z2_E2FORN]
      ,[Z2_E2LOJA]
      ,[Z2_ANEXO]
      ,[Z2_OBS]
      ,[Z2_CONTAB]
      ,[Z2_OBSTITU]
      ,[Z2_CPF]
      ,[Z2_TIPCOL]
      ,[Z2_BORDERO]
      ,[Z2_HORALIB]
      ,[Z2_APROV]
      ,[Z2_NDC]
      ,[Z2_VALNDC]
      ,[Z2_NOMDEP]
      ,[Z2_NOMMAE]
      ,[Z2_CODDEP]
	  INTO [dataP10].[dbo].[SZ2DIF]
  FROM (
  SELECT [Z2_FILIAL]
      ,[Z2_CTRID]
      ,[Z2_CODEMP]
      ,[Z2_PRONT]
      ,[Z2_NOME]
      ,[Z2_VALOR]
      ,[Z2_TIPO]
      ,[Z2_BANCO]
      ,[Z2_AGENCIA]
      ,[Z2_DIGAGEN]
      ,[Z2_CONTA]
      ,[Z2_DIGCONT]
      ,[Z2_STATUS]
      ,[Z2_DATAEMI]
      ,[Z2_DATAPGT]
      ,[Z2_USUARIO]
      ,[Z2_TITULO]
      ,[Z2_CALC]
      ,[D_E_L_E_T_]
      ,[R_E_C_N_O_]
      ,[Z2_CODFOR]
      ,[Z2_LOJFOR]
      ,[Z2_PRODUTO]
      ,[Z2_TIPOPES]
      ,[Z2_CC]
      ,[Z2_E2PRF]
      ,[Z2_E2NUM]
      ,[Z2_E2PARC]
      ,[Z2_E2TIPO]
      ,[Z2_E2FORN]
      ,[Z2_E2LOJA]
      ,[Z2_ANEXO]
      ,[Z2_OBS]
      ,[Z2_CONTAB]
      ,[Z2_OBSTITU]
      ,[Z2_CPF]
      ,[Z2_TIPCOL]
      ,[Z2_BORDERO]
      ,[Z2_HORALIB]
      ,[Z2_APROV]
      ,[Z2_NDC]
      ,[Z2_VALNDC]
      ,[Z2_NOMDEP]
      ,[Z2_NOMMAE]
      ,[Z2_CODDEP]
      
  FROM [dataP12Tst].[dbo].[SZ2010]
  UNION ALL

  SELECT [Z2_FILIAL]
      ,[Z2_CTRID]
      ,[Z2_CODEMP]
      ,[Z2_PRONT]
      ,[Z2_NOME]
      ,[Z2_VALOR]
      ,[Z2_TIPO]
      ,[Z2_BANCO]
      ,[Z2_AGENCIA]
      ,[Z2_DIGAGEN]
      ,[Z2_CONTA]
      ,[Z2_DIGCONT]
      ,[Z2_STATUS]
      ,[Z2_DATAEMI]
      ,[Z2_DATAPGT]
      ,[Z2_USUARIO]
      ,[Z2_TITULO]
      ,[Z2_CALC]
      ,[D_E_L_E_T_]
      ,[R_E_C_N_O_]
      ,[Z2_CODFOR]
      ,[Z2_LOJFOR]
      ,[Z2_PRODUTO]
      ,[Z2_TIPOPES]
      ,[Z2_CC]
      ,[Z2_E2PRF]
      ,[Z2_E2NUM]
      ,[Z2_E2PARC]
      ,[Z2_E2TIPO]
      ,[Z2_E2FORN]
      ,[Z2_E2LOJA]
      ,[Z2_ANEXO]
      ,[Z2_OBS]
      ,[Z2_CONTAB]
      ,[Z2_OBSTITU]
      ,[Z2_CPF]
      ,[Z2_TIPCOL]
      ,[Z2_BORDERO]
      ,[Z2_HORALIB]
      ,[Z2_APROV]
      ,[Z2_NDC]
      ,[Z2_VALNDC]
      ,[Z2_NOMDEP]
      ,[Z2_NOMMAE]
      ,[Z2_CODDEP]
	  
  FROM [dataP10].[dbo].[SZ2010]) AS T1
  GROUP BY [Z2_FILIAL]
      ,[Z2_CTRID]
      ,[Z2_CODEMP]
      ,[Z2_PRONT]
      ,[Z2_NOME]
      ,[Z2_VALOR]
      ,[Z2_TIPO]
      ,[Z2_BANCO]
      ,[Z2_AGENCIA]
      ,[Z2_DIGAGEN]
      ,[Z2_CONTA]
      ,[Z2_DIGCONT]
      ,[Z2_STATUS]
      ,[Z2_DATAEMI]
      ,[Z2_DATAPGT]
      ,[Z2_USUARIO]
      ,[Z2_TITULO]
      ,[Z2_CALC]
      ,[D_E_L_E_T_]
      ,[R_E_C_N_O_]
      ,[Z2_CODFOR]
      ,[Z2_LOJFOR]
      ,[Z2_PRODUTO]
      ,[Z2_TIPOPES]
      ,[Z2_CC]
      ,[Z2_E2PRF]
      ,[Z2_E2NUM]
      ,[Z2_E2PARC]
      ,[Z2_E2TIPO]
      ,[Z2_E2FORN]
      ,[Z2_E2LOJA]
      ,[Z2_ANEXO]
      ,[Z2_OBS]
      ,[Z2_CONTAB]
      ,[Z2_OBSTITU]
      ,[Z2_CPF]
      ,[Z2_TIPCOL]
      ,[Z2_BORDERO]
      ,[Z2_HORALIB]
      ,[Z2_APROV]
      ,[Z2_NDC]
      ,[Z2_VALNDC]
      ,[Z2_NOMDEP]
      ,[Z2_NOMMAE]
      ,[Z2_CODDEP]
	HAVING COUNT(*) = 1
      order by R_E_C_N_O_

08/11/2022



SELECT * into Powerbk.dbo.R040PER FROM bk_senior.bk_senior.R040PER


--SELECT * FROM SC1010

SELECT
C1_NUM,
C1_ITEM,
C1_PRODUTO,
C1_DESCRI,
C1_QUANT,
C1_QUJE,
C1_UM,
CONVERT(DATE,C1_DATPRF,112) AS C1_DATPRF,
C1_CC,
CONVERT(DATE,C1_EMISSAO,112) AS C1_EMISSAO,
C1_PEDIDO,
C1_ITEMPED,
C1_USER,
C7_NUM,
CONVERT(DATE,C7_EMISSAO,112) AS C7_EMISSAO,
C7_QUANT,
C7_QUJE,
C7_QTDACLA,
C7_USER,
C7_APROV,
D1_PEDIDO,
D1_ITEMPC,
D1_SERIE,
D1_DOC,
CONVERT(DATE,D1_DTDIGIT,112) AS D1_DTDIGIT,
F1_XXAVALI,
CASE WHEN SUBSTRING(F1_XXAVALI,1,1) = 'S' THEN 25 ELSE 0 END AS AVALPRECO,
CASE WHEN SUBSTRING(F1_XXAVALI,2,1) = 'S' THEN 25 ELSE 0 END AS AVALPRAZO,
CASE WHEN SUBSTRING(F1_XXAVALI,3,1) = 'S' THEN 25 ELSE 0 END AS AVALQUAL,
CASE WHEN SUBSTRING(F1_XXAVALI,4,1) = 'S' THEN 25 ELSE 0 END AS AVALATEND

INTO Powerbk.dbo.SOLCOMPRAS
FROM SC1010
LEFT JOIN SC7010 ON C7_FILIAL = C1_FILIAL AND C7_NUMSC = C1_NUM AND C7_ITEMSC = C1_ITEM AND SC7010.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''
LEFT JOIN SD1010 ON D1_FILIAL = C1_FILIAL AND D1_PEDIDO = C1_PEDIDO AND D1_ITEMPC = C1_ITEMPED AND D1_PEDIDO <> ' ' AND SD1010.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''
LEFT JOIN SF1010 SF1
 ON (F1_SERIE = D1_SERIE
 AND F1_DOC = D1_DOC
 AND F1_FORNECE = D1_FORNECE
 AND F1_LOJA = D1_LOJA
 AND F1_FILIAL = D1_FILIAL 
 AND SF1.D_E_L_E_T_ = '')
WHERE SC1010.D_E_L_E_T_ = ' '
AND C1_APROV <> 'B' AND C1_APROV <> 'R'

/*
DROP TABLE Powerbk.dbo.SOLCOMPRAS
SELECT * FROM Powerbk.dbo.SOLCOMPRAS

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT C1_PEDIDO) FROM Powerbk.dbo.SOLCOMPRAS WHERE C1_PEDIDO IS NOT NULL  --GROUP BY C1_NUM
SELECT COUNT(C1_PEDIDO) FROM Powerbk.dbo.SOLCOMPRAS --WHERE C1_PEDIDO IS NOT NULL --GROUP BY C1_NUM

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT C7_NUM) FROM SC7010 WHERE D_E_L_E_T_ = ''
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT D1_PEDIDO) FROM SD1010 WHERE D_E_L_E_T_ = '' AND D1_PEDIDO <> ' '
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT C7_NUM)  FROM SC7010 WHERE C7_QUJE = 0 AND D_E_L_E_T_ = '' 

SELECT * FROM SC7010 WHERE C7_NUMSC = ' '
SELECT C1_APROV,* FROM SC1010
SELECT C1_APROV FROM SC1010 GROUP BY C1_APROV
SELECT  * FROM Powerbk.dbo.USUARIOS
*/

31/10/2022
-- Acerto nas avaliaes no realizadas

UPDATE SF1010 SET F1_XXAVALI = 'SSSS'
 FROM SF1010 SF1
 INNER JOIN SA2010 SA2 ON SA2.A2_FILIAL='  ' AND SF1.F1_FORNECE=SA2.A2_COD AND SF1.F1_LOJA=SA2.A2_LOJA AND SA2.D_E_L_E_T_=''
 LEFT JOIN SD1010 SD1 ON F1_FILIAL = D1_FILIAL AND F1_DOC = D1_DOC AND F1_SERIE = D1_SERIE AND F1_FORNECE = D1_FORNECE AND F1_LOJA = D1_LOJA AND SF1.D_E_L_E_T_ = ' '
 WHERE SF1.D_E_L_E_T_='' AND SF1.F1_DTDIGIT >= '20220701' AND SF1.F1_DTDIGIT <= '20222031' 
 AND F1_XXAVALI = 'NNNN' AND D1_PEDIDO <> ' '

UPDATE SF1010 SET F1_XXAVALI = 'SNSS'
 FROM SF1010 SF1
 INNER JOIN SA2010 SA2 ON SA2.A2_FILIAL='  ' AND SF1.F1_FORNECE=SA2.A2_COD AND SF1.F1_LOJA=SA2.A2_LOJA AND SA2.D_E_L_E_T_=''
 LEFT JOIN SD1010 SD1 ON F1_FILIAL = D1_FILIAL AND F1_DOC = D1_DOC AND F1_SERIE = D1_SERIE AND F1_FORNECE = D1_FORNECE AND F1_LOJA = D1_LOJA AND SF1.D_E_L_E_T_ = ' '
 WHERE SF1.D_E_L_E_T_='' AND SF1.F1_DTDIGIT >= '20220701' AND SF1.F1_DTDIGIT <= '20222031' 
AND D1_PEDIDO <> ' '
and A2_NOME LIKE '%GUAIRA%'

13/10/22 Criar campos nas tabelas CX* do PowerBK

ALTER TABLE dbo.CXFATURAMENTO
ADD CHAVECX VARCHAR(17) NULL, CHAVECT VARCHAR(17) NULL ;

ALTER TABLE dbo.CXFOLHA
ADD CHAVECX VARCHAR(17) NULL, CHAVECT VARCHAR(17) NULL ;

ALTER TABLE dbo.CXGASTOS
ADD CHAVECX VARCHAR(17) NULL, CHAVECT VARCHAR(17) NULL ;

UPDATE CXFATURAMENTO 
SET CHAVECX = EMPRESA+CONTRATO+COMPETAM, CHAVECT = EMPRESA+CONTRATO+SUBSTRING(COMPETCT,4,4)+SUBSTRING(COMPETCT,1,2)

UPDATE CXFOLHA
SET CHAVECX = EMPRESA+CONTRATO+COMPETAM, CHAVECT = EMPRESA+CONTRATO+SUBSTRING(COMPETCT,4,4)+SUBSTRING(COMPETCT,1,2)

UPDATE CXGASTOS
SET CHAVECX = EMPRESA+CONTRATO+COMPETAM, CHAVECT = EMPRESA+CONTRATO+SUBSTRING(COMPETCT,4,4)+SUBSTRING(COMPETCT,1,2)

08/10/22 - Popular campos da CXN_XXMUN e CNA_XXMOT, aps serem convertidos para campos reais

SELECT CXN_NUMMED,CXN_CONTRA,CNA_CONTRA,CXN_REVISA,CNA_REVISA,CXN_NUMPLA,CNA_NUMERO,
		CXN_XXMUN,CNA_XXMUN

--UPDATE CXN010 SET CXN_XXMUN = CNA_XXMUN, CXN_XXMOT = CNA_XXMOT
FROM CXN010 
LEFT JOIN CNA010 ON
	CXN_CONTRA = CNA_CONTRA AND CXN_REVISA = CNA_REVISA AND CXN_NUMPLA = CNA_NUMERO
	--WHERE CXN_XXMUN = ''
	
SELECT CXN_NUMMED,CXN_CONTRA,CNA_CONTRA,CXN_REVISA,CNA_REVISA,CXN_NUMPLA,CNA_NUMERO,
		CXN_XXMUN,CNA_XXMUN

--UPDATE CXN140 SET CXN_XXMUN = CNA_XXMUN, CXN_XXMOT = CNA_XXMOT
FROM CXN140 
LEFT JOIN CNA140 ON
	CXN_CONTRA = CNA_CONTRA AND CXN_REVISA = CNA_REVISA AND CXN_NUMPLA = CNA_NUMERO
	--WHERE CXN_XXMUN = ''

02/08/2022 - Acerto pedidos com C5_XXREV incorretos

SELECT C5_NUM,C5_MDCONTR,C5_MDNUMED,C5_MDPLANI,C5_XXREV,C5_XXPARC,CND_PARCEL,CNE_CONTRA,CNE_NUMMED,CNE_REVISA,C5_EMISSAO,CNE.R_E_C_N_O_
--UPDATE SC5010 SET C5_XXREV = CNE_REVISA,C5_XXPARC = CND_PARCEL
FROM SC5010 SC5
LEFT JOIN CND010 CND
 	ON (CND_NUMMED = C5_MDNUMED
         AND CND_FILIAL = '01'
         AND CND.D_E_L_E_T_ = '' 
         AND CND.R_E_C_N_O_ = (
            SELECT 
                MIN(R_E_C_N_O_) 
              FROM 
                CND010 CND1 
              WHERE 
                CND1.CND_NUMMED = C5_MDNUMED 
                AND CND1.CND_FILIAL = '01' 
                AND CND1.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''
    			)
    )
OUTER APPLY (SELECT TOP 1 * FROM CNE010 WHERE
CNE_NUMMED = C5_MDNUMED  AND CNE_CONTRA = C5_MDCONTR AND CNE010.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''  ORDER BY CNE010.R_E_C_N_O_) AS CNE

WHERE SC5.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''
AND C5_XXREV NOT IN (SELECT CNE_REVISA FROM CNE010 CNE WHERE CNE_NUMMED = C5_MDNUMED AND CNE_CONTRA = C5_MDCONTR AND CNE.D_E_L_E_T_ = '')
AND C5_MDCONTR <> ' '
--ORDER BY C5_MDCONTR,C5_MDNUMED,C5_MDPLANI,C5_XXREV,CNE_CONTRA,CNE_NUMMED,CNE_REVISA

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
--SELECT C5_NUM,C5_MDCONTR,C5_MDNUMED,C5_MDPLANI,C5_XXREV,C5_XXPARC,CND_PARCEL,CNE_CONTRA,CNE_NUMMED,CNE_REVISA,C5_EMISSAO,CNE.R_E_C_N_O_
UPDATE SC5020 SET C5_XXREV = CNE_REVISA,C5_XXPARC = CND_PARCEL
FROM SC5020 SC5
LEFT JOIN CND020 CND
 	ON (CND_NUMMED = C5_MDNUMED
         AND CND_FILIAL = '01'
         AND CND.D_E_L_E_T_ = '' 
         AND CND.R_E_C_N_O_ = (
            SELECT 
                MIN(R_E_C_N_O_) 
              FROM 
                CND020 CND1 
              WHERE 
                CND1.CND_NUMMED = C5_MDNUMED 
                AND CND1.CND_FILIAL = '01' 
                AND CND1.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''
    			)
    )
OUTER APPLY (SELECT TOP 1 * FROM CNE020 WHERE
CNE_NUMMED = C5_MDNUMED  AND CNE_CONTRA = C5_MDCONTR AND CNE020.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''  ORDER BY CNE020.R_E_C_N_O_) AS CNE

WHERE SC5.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''
AND C5_XXREV NOT IN (SELECT CNE_REVISA FROM CNE020 CNE WHERE CNE_NUMMED = C5_MDNUMED AND CNE_CONTRA = C5_MDCONTR AND CNE.D_E_L_E_T_ = '')
AND C5_MDCONTR <> ' '
--ORDER BY C5_MDCONTR,C5_MDNUMED,C5_MDPLANI,C5_XXREV,CNE_CONTRA,CNE_NUMMED,CNE_REVISA

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------


SELECT C5_NUM,C5_MDCONTR,C5_MDNUMED,C5_MDPLANI,C5_XXREV,C5_XXPARC,CND_PARCEL,CNE_CONTRA,CNE_NUMMED,CNE_REVISA,C5_EMISSAO,CNE.R_E_C_N_O_
--UPDATE SC5140 SET C5_XXREV = CNE_REVISA,C5_XXPARC = CND_PARCEL
FROM SC5140 SC5
LEFT JOIN CND140 CND
 	ON (CND_NUMMED = C5_MDNUMED
         AND CND_FILIAL = '01'
         AND CND.D_E_L_E_T_ = '' 
         AND CND.R_E_C_N_O_ = (
            SELECT 
                MIN(R_E_C_N_O_) 
              FROM 
                CND140 CND1 
              WHERE 
                CND1.CND_NUMMED = C5_MDNUMED 
                AND CND1.CND_FILIAL = '01' 
                AND CND1.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''
    			)
    )
OUTER APPLY (SELECT TOP 1 * FROM CNE140 WHERE
CNE_NUMMED = C5_MDNUMED  AND CNE_CONTRA = C5_MDCONTR AND CNE140.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''  ORDER BY CNE140.R_E_C_N_O_) AS CNE

WHERE SC5.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''
AND C5_XXREV NOT IN (SELECT CNE_REVISA FROM CNE140 CNE WHERE CNE_NUMMED = C5_MDNUMED AND CNE_CONTRA = C5_MDCONTR AND CNE.D_E_L_E_T_ = '')
AND C5_MDCONTR <> ' '
ORDER BY C5_MDCONTR,C5_MDNUMED,C5_MDPLANI,C5_XXREV,CNE_CONTRA,CNE_NUMMED,CNE_REVISA

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

UPDATE SC5010 SET C5_XXREV = ' ',C5_XXPARC = ' ' WHERE C5_MDNUMED = ' ' AND C5_MDCONTR = ' ' AND C5_XXREV <> ' '
UPDATE SC5020 SET C5_XXREV = ' ',C5_XXPARC = ' ' WHERE C5_MDNUMED = ' ' AND C5_MDCONTR = ' ' AND C5_XXREV <> ' '
UPDATE SC5140 SET C5_XXREV = ' ',C5_XXPARC = ' ' WHERE C5_MDNUMED = ' ' AND C5_MDCONTR = ' ' AND C5_XXREV <> ' '

SELECT C5_XXREV,* FROM SC5010 WHERE C5_NOTA = '000005049'
SELECT * FROM CNE010  WHERE CNE_PEDIDO = '050324'

SELECT C5_XXREV,* FROM SC5010 WHERE C5_NOTA = '000005050'
SELECT * FROM CNE010  WHERE CNE_PEDIDO = '050325'

SELECT C5_XXREV,* FROM SC5010 WHERE C5_NOTA = '000005671'
SELECT * FROM CNE010  WHERE CNE_PEDIDO = '051032' order by R_E_C_N_O_

25/07/22 - 12/07/22 EFD na Base Teste

BAIXA DA NF 006-000000535 FOI REFEITA (DELETADO OS CANCELAMENTOS) ESTA NF NO APARECIA NOS retidos

* * * BAIXAR OS TITULOS EM ABERTO ANTES DE EXECUTAR AS QUERYES ABAIXO * * *

use dataP12Tst

UPDATE SE1010 SET E1_VENCTO = E1_EMISSAO, E1_VENCREA = E1_EMISSAO, E1_MOVIMEN = E1_EMISSAO, E1_VENCORI = E1_EMISSAO  WHERE SUBSTRING(E1_EMISSAO,1,6) >= '202001' AND SE1010.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''

UPDATE SE1010 SET E1_BAIXA = E1_EMISSAO WHERE SUBSTRING(E1_EMISSAO,1,6) >= '202001' AND SE1010.D_E_L_E_T_ = '' AND E1_BAIXA <> ''

UPDATE SE5010 SET E5_DATA=E1_EMISSAO,E5_VENCTO=E1_EMISSAO,E5_DTDIGIT=E1_EMISSAO,E5_DTDISPO=E1_EMISSAO
 FROM SE5010 INNER JOIN SE1010 ON E5_FILIAL+E5_PREFIXO+E5_NUMERO+E5_PARCELA+E5_CLIFOR+E5_LOJA = E1_FILIAL+E1_PREFIXO+E1_NUM+E1_PARCELA+E1_CLIENTE+E1_LOJA 
WHERE SUBSTRING(E1_EMISSAO,1,6) >= '202001'  AND E1_BAIXA <> '' AND SE1010.D_E_L_E_T_ = '' AND SE5010.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''

UPDATE FK1010 SET FK1_DATA = E5_DATA FROM FK1010 INNER JOIN SE5010 ON FK1_IDFK1 = E5_IDORIG
WHERE SUBSTRING(E5_DATA,1,6) >= '202001'

UPDATE SE1010 SET E1_BAIXA = E1_EMISSAO WHERE SUBSTRING(E1_EMISSAO,1,6) >= '202101' AND SE1010.D_E_L_E_T_ = '' AND E1_BAIXA <> ''

UPDATE SE5010 SET E5_DATA=E1_EMISSAO,E5_VENCTO=E1_EMISSAO,E5_DTDIGIT=E1_EMISSAO,E5_DTDISPO=E1_EMISSAO
 FROM SE5010 INNER JOIN SE1010 ON E5_FILIAL+E5_PREFIXO+E5_NUMERO+E5_PARCELA+E5_CLIFOR+E5_LOJA = E1_FILIAL+E1_PREFIXO+E1_NUM+E1_PARCELA+E1_CLIENTE+E1_LOJA 
WHERE SUBSTRING(E1_EMISSAO,1,6) >= '202101'  AND E1_BAIXA <> '' AND SE1010.D_E_L_E_T_ = '' AND SE5010.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''

WHERE SUBSTRING(E5_DATA,1,6) >= '202101'

30/05/22 - Acerto na competencia do pedido de vendas

WITH X AS (
SELECT 
  '01' AS EMPRESA,
  'BK' AS NOMEEMP,
  GETDATE() AS DATAPRC,
  ISNULL(CND_CONTRA, C5_ESPECI1) AS CND_CONTRA, 
  CTT_DESC01, 
  --CONVERT(DATE,CONVERT(VARCHAR,SUBSTRING(C5_XXCOMPM,4,4)+SUBSTRING(C5_XXCOMPM,1,2)+'01'),112) AS C5XXCOMPM, 
  C5_XXCOMPT,
  C5_XXCOMPM,
  SUBSTRING(F2_EMISSAO,5,2)+'/'+SUBSTRING(F2_EMISSAO,1,4) AS COMPET,
  SUBSTRING(F2_EMISSAO,1,6) AS COMPET1,
  C5_NUM, 
  C5_MDNUMED, 
  C5_MDPLANI, 
  F2_SERIE, 
  F2_DOC, 
  CONVERT(DATE,F2_EMISSAO,112) AS F2_EMISSAO,  
  F2_VALFAT, 
  CND_USUAR, 
  (
    CASE WHEN CND_NUMERO = '' THEN 'NOVA' ELSE 'ANTIGA' END
  ) AS FORMAMED, 
  CNA_XXMUN  AS CNA_XXMUN,
  CASE WHEN ISNULL(CXN_VLPREV, CND_VLPREV) = CNF_VLPREV THEN CNF_VLPREV ELSE 0 END AS CXN_VLPREV,
   (SELECT SUM(CNR_VALOR)
        FROM CNR010 CNR 
        WHERE 
          C5_MDNUMED = CNR.CNR_NUMMED 
          AND (CNR_CODPLA = ' ' OR CNR_CODPLA = ISNULL(CXN_NUMPLA,CND_NUMERO))
          AND CNR_FILIAL = '01'
          AND CNR.D_E_L_E_T_ = ' ' 
          AND CNR_TIPO = '2' ) AS CNRVLBONI,
   (SELECT SUM(CNR_VALOR)
        FROM CNR010 CNR 
        WHERE 
          C5_MDNUMED = CNR.CNR_NUMMED 
          AND (CNR_CODPLA = ' ' OR CNR_CODPLA = ISNULL(CXN_NUMPLA,CND_NUMERO))
          AND CNR_FILIAL = '01'
          AND CNR.D_E_L_E_T_ = ' ' 
          AND CNR_TIPO = '1' ) AS CNRVLMULT,
  STUFF (
    (
      SELECT 
        ';' + RTRIM(CNR_XTPJUS + '-' + ZR_DESCR) 
      FROM 
        CNR010 CNR 
        INNER JOIN SZR010 SZR ON ZR_TIPO = CNR_XTPJUS 
      WHERE 
        C5_MDNUMED = CNR.CNR_NUMMED 
        AND (CNR_CODPLA = ' ' OR CNR_CODPLA = ISNULL(CXN_NUMPLA,CND_NUMERO))
        AND CNR_FILIAL = CND_FILIAL
        AND CNR.D_E_L_E_T_ = ' ' 
        AND CNR_TIPO = '1' 
      ORDER BY 
        ';' + RTRIM(CNR_XTPJUS + '-' + ZR_DESCR) FOR XML PATH (''), 
        TYPE
    ).value('.', 'varchar(100)'), 
    1, 
    1, 
    ''
  ) AS CNRTPMUL, 
  STUFF (
    (
      SELECT 
        ';' + RTRIM(CNR_DESCRI) 
      FROM 
        CNR010 CNR 
      WHERE 
        C5_MDNUMED = CNR.CNR_NUMMED 
        AND (CNR_CODPLA = ' ' OR CNR_CODPLA = ISNULL(CXN_NUMPLA,CND_NUMERO))
        AND CNR_FILIAL = CND_FILIAL
        AND CNR.D_E_L_E_T_ = ' ' 
        AND CNR_TIPO = '1' 
      ORDER BY 
        ';' + RTRIM(CNR_DESCRI) FOR XML PATH (''), 
        TYPE
    ).value('.', 'varchar(100)'), 
    1, 
    1, 
    ''
  ) AS CNRDESCMUL, 
  STUFF (
    (
      SELECT 
        ';' + RTRIM(CNR_XTPJUS + '-' + ZR_DESCR) 
      FROM 
        CNR010 CNR 
        INNER JOIN SZR010 SZR ON ZR_TIPO = CNR_XTPJUS 
      WHERE 
        C5_MDNUMED = CNR.CNR_NUMMED 
        AND (CNR_CODPLA = ' ' OR CNR_CODPLA = ISNULL(CXN_NUMPLA,CND_NUMERO))
        AND CNR_FILIAL = CND_FILIAL
        AND CNR.D_E_L_E_T_ = ' ' 
        AND CNR_TIPO = '2' 
      ORDER BY 
        ';' + RTRIM(CNR_XTPJUS + '-' + ZR_DESCR) FOR XML PATH (''), 
        TYPE
    ).value('.', 'varchar(100)'), 
    1, 
    1, 
    ''
  ) AS CNRTPBON, 
  STUFF (
    (
      SELECT 
        ';' + RTRIM(CNR_DESCRI) 
      FROM 
        CNR010 CNR 
      WHERE 
        C5_MDNUMED = CNR.CNR_NUMMED 
        AND (CNR_CODPLA = ' ' OR CNR_CODPLA = ISNULL(CXN_NUMPLA,CND_NUMERO))
        AND CNR_FILIAL = CND_FILIAL
        AND CNR.D_E_L_E_T_ = ' ' 
        AND CNR_TIPO = '2' 
      ORDER BY 
        ';' + RTRIM(CNR_DESCRI) FOR XML PATH (''), 
        TYPE
    ).value('.', 'varchar(100)'), 
    1, 
    1, 
    ''
  ) AS CNRDESCBON 
  --INTO PowerBk.dbo.FATURAMENTO 
FROM 
  SF2010 SF2 
 LEFT JOIN SC5010 SC5
     ON (C5_NOTA = F2_DOC 
         AND C5_SERIE = F2_SERIE 
         AND C5_FILIAL = F2_FILIAL 
         AND SC5.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''
 ) 
 LEFT JOIN CND010 CND
     ON (CND_NUMMED = C5_MDNUMED 
         AND CND_FILIAL = '01' 
         AND CND.D_E_L_E_T_ = '' 
         AND CND.R_E_C_N_O_ = (
         SELECT 
            MIN(R_E_C_N_O_) 
         FROM 
            CND010 CND1 
         WHERE 
            CND1.CND_NUMMED = C5_MDNUMED 
            AND CND1.CND_FILIAL = '01' 
            AND CND1.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''
    )
  ) 
 LEFT JOIN CXN010 CXN
     ON (CXN_CONTRA = C5_MDCONTR 
         AND CXN_NUMMED = C5_MDNUMED 
         AND CXN_NUMPLA = C5_MDPLANI 
         AND CXN_REVISA = CND_REVISA 
         AND CXN.CXN_CHECK = 'T' 
         AND CXN_FILIAL = F2_FILIAL 
         AND CXN.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''
  ) 
 LEFT JOIN CNF010 CNF
 	ON (CND_CONTRA = CNF_CONTRA AND C5_XXCOMPM = CNF_COMPET
 	    AND ISNULL(CXN_NUMPLA,CND_NUMERO) = CNF_NUMPLA
 	    AND ISNULL(CXN_REVISA,CND_REVISA) = CNF_REVISA
 	    AND CNF_PARCEL = ISNULL(CXN_PARCEL,CND_PARCEL)
 	 	AND CNF_FILIAL = F2_FILIAL AND CNF.D_E_L_E_T_=''
  ) 
 LEFT JOIN CNA010 CNA
 	ON (CNA_CONTRA = CNF_CONTRA
 	 	AND CNA_CRONOG = CNF_NUMERO
 	 	AND CNA_REVISA = CNF_REVISA
 	 	AND CNA_NUMERO = CNF_NUMPLA
 		AND CNA_FILIAL = CNF_FILIAL AND CNA.D_E_L_E_T_=''
  ) 
 LEFT JOIN CTT010 CTT
     ON (ISNULL(CND_CONTRA, C5_ESPECI1) = CTT_CUSTO 
 		AND CTT_FILIAL = '01'
         AND CTT.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''
  ) 
WHERE 
  SF2.D_E_L_E_T_ = '' 
)
--SELECT SC5010.C5_NUM,X.C5_NUM,SC5010.C5_XXCOMPM,SC5010.C5_XXCOMPT,SC5010.C5_MDCONTR,SC5010.C5_MDNUMED,X.C5_MDNUMED,X.COMPET,X.COMPET1 FROM X 
UPDATE SC5010 SET SC5010.C5_XXCOMPM = COMPET FROM X
--UPDATE SC5010 SET SC5010.C5_XXCOMPT = COMPET1 FROM X
INNER JOIN SC5010 ON SC5010.C5_NUM = X.C5_NUM
WHERE --X.C5_MDNUMED = ' '

--AND 
(SUBSTRING(X.C5_XXCOMPM,1,2) < '01' 
OR SUBSTRING(X.C5_XXCOMPM,1,2) > '12')
  --AND X.C5_MDNUMED = ' '
--AND 
  --X.C5_XXCOMPM <> ' '



--SELECT C5_XXCOMPT,C5_XXCOMPM,C5_MDCONTR FROM SC5010

==============================================================

UPDATE CT1010 SET CT1_NTSPED = '02' WHERE SUBSTRING(CT1_CONTA,1,1) = '2' AND CT1_NTSPED = ' '
UPDATE CT1010 SET CT1_NTSPED = '04' WHERE SUBSTRING(CT1_CONTA,1,1) = '3' AND CT1_NTSPED = ' '

==============================================================
27/05/22 - Gravao dos campos C5_XXREV e C5_XXPARC

 WITH X AS (
 SELECT 
   ISNULL(CND_CONTRA,C5_ESPECI1) AS CND_CONTRA
	,CND_PEDIDO
	,CND_NUMMED
   ,CNF_CONTRA
   ,CNF_REVISA
   ,CNF_PARCEL
   ,CND_PARCEL
   ,CNA_REVISA
   ,CND_REVISA
   ,CND_REVGER
   ,CXN_REVISA
   ,C5_MDCONTR
,C5_XXREV
,C5_XXPARC
,CXN_PARCEL
,SC5.R_E_C_N_O_ AS C5RECNO
   ,CTT_DESC01
   ,C5_XXCOMPM
   ,C5_NUM
   ,C5_MDNUMED
   ,C5_MDPLANI
   ,F2_SERIE
   ,F2_DOC
   ,F2_EMISSAO
   ,F2_VALFAT
   ,CND_USUAR
   ,(CASE WHEN CND_NUMERO = '' THEN 'NOVA' ELSE 'ANTIGA' END) AS FORMAMED
   ,CNA_XXMUN
   ,CASE WHEN ISNULL(CXN_VLPREV, CND_VLPREV) = CNF_VLPREV THEN CNF_VLPREV ELSE 0 END AS CXN_VLPREV
   ,(SELECT SUM(CNR_VALOR)
        FROM CNR010 CNR
        WHERE 
          C5_MDNUMED = CNR.CNR_NUMMED 
          AND (CNR_CODPLA = ' ' OR CNR_CODPLA = ISNULL(CXN_NUMPLA,CND_NUMERO))
          AND CNR_FILIAL = '01'
          AND CNR.D_E_L_E_T_ = ' ' 
          AND CNR_TIPO = '2' ) AS CXN_VLBONI
   ,(SELECT SUM(CNR_VALOR)
        FROM CNR010 CNR
        WHERE 
          C5_MDNUMED = CNR.CNR_NUMMED 
          AND (CNR_CODPLA = ' ' OR CNR_CODPLA = ISNULL(CXN_NUMPLA,CND_NUMERO))
          AND CNR_FILIAL = '01'
          AND CNR.D_E_L_E_T_ = ' ' 
          AND CNR_TIPO = '1' ) AS CXN_VLMULT
   ,STUFF ((SELECT ';' + RTRIM(CNR_XTPJUS+'-'+ZR_DESCR)
          FROM CNR010 CNR
   			INNER JOIN SZR010 SZR ON ZR_TIPO = CNR_XTPJUS
          WHERE C5_MDNUMED = CNR.CNR_NUMMED
                AND (CNR_CODPLA = ' ' OR CNR_CODPLA = ISNULL(CXN_NUMPLA,CND_NUMERO))
                AND CNR_FILIAL = '01' AND CNR.D_E_L_E_T_ = ' ' AND CNR_TIPO = '1'
          ORDER BY ';' + RTRIM(CNR_XTPJUS+ '-'+ZR_DESCR)
          FOR XML PATH (''), TYPE).value('.', 'varchar(100)'           ), 1, 1, '') AS CNRTPMUL
   ,STUFF ((SELECT ';' + RTRIM(CNR_DESCRI)
          FROM CNR010 CNR
          WHERE C5_MDNUMED = CNR.CNR_NUMMED
                AND (CNR_CODPLA = ' ' OR CNR_CODPLA = ISNULL(CXN_NUMPLA,CND_NUMERO))
                AND CNR_FILIAL = '01' AND CNR.D_E_L_E_T_ = ' ' AND CNR_TIPO = '1'
          ORDER BY ';' + RTRIM(CNR_DESCRI)
          FOR XML PATH (''), TYPE).value('.', 'varchar(100)'          ), 1, 1, '') AS CNRDESCMUL
   ,STUFF ((SELECT ';' + RTRIM(CNR_XTPJUS+'-'+ZR_DESCR)
          FROM CNR010 CNR
   			INNER JOIN SZR010 SZR ON ZR_TIPO = CNR_XTPJUS
          WHERE C5_MDNUMED = CNR.CNR_NUMMED
                AND (CNR_CODPLA = ' ' OR CNR_CODPLA = ISNULL(CXN_NUMPLA,CND_NUMERO))
                AND CNR_FILIAL = '01' AND CNR.D_E_L_E_T_ = ' ' AND CNR_TIPO = '2'
          ORDER BY ';' + RTRIM(CNR_XTPJUS+ '-'+ZR_DESCR)
          FOR XML PATH (''), TYPE).value('.', 'varchar(100)'          ), 1, 1, '') AS CNRTPBON
   ,STUFF ((SELECT ';' + RTRIM(CNR_DESCRI)
          FROM CNR010 CNR
          WHERE C5_MDNUMED = CNR.CNR_NUMMED
                AND (CNR_CODPLA = ' ' OR CNR_CODPLA = ISNULL(CXN_NUMPLA,CND_NUMERO))
                AND CNR_FILIAL = '01' AND CNR.D_E_L_E_T_ = ' ' AND CNR_TIPO = '2'
          ORDER BY ';' + RTRIM(CNR_DESCRI)
          FOR XML PATH (''), TYPE).value('.', 'varchar(100)'          ), 1, 1, '') AS CNRDESCBON
 FROM SF2010 SF2
 LEFT JOIN SC5010 SC5
 	ON (C5_NOTA = F2_DOC AND C5_SERIE = F2_SERIE
 		AND C5_FILIAL = F2_FILIAL AND SC5.D_E_L_E_T_='')
 LEFT JOIN CND010 CND
 	ON (CND_NUMMED = C5_MDNUMED
         AND CND_FILIAL = '01'
         AND CND.D_E_L_E_T_ = '' 
         AND CND.R_E_C_N_O_ = (
            SELECT 
                MIN(R_E_C_N_O_) 
              FROM 
                CND010 CND1 
              WHERE 
                CND1.CND_NUMMED = C5_MDNUMED 
                AND CND1.CND_FILIAL = '01' 
                AND CND1.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''
    			)
    )
 LEFT JOIN CXN010 CXN
    ON (CXN_CONTRA = C5_MDCONTR 
        AND CXN_NUMMED = C5_MDNUMED 
        AND CXN_NUMPLA = C5_MDPLANI 
        AND CXN_REVISA = CND_REVISA 
        AND CXN.CXN_CHECK = 'T' 
        AND CXN_FILIAL = '01' 
        AND CXN.D_E_L_E_T_ = '') 
 LEFT JOIN CNF010 CNF
 	ON (CND_CONTRA = CNF_CONTRA
 	    AND C5_XXCOMPM = CNF_COMPET
 	    AND ISNULL(CXN_NUMPLA,CND_NUMERO) = CNF_NUMPLA
 	    AND ISNULL(CXN_REVISA, CND_REVISA) = CNF_REVISA
 	    AND CNF_PARCEL = ISNULL(CXN_PARCEL,CND_PARCEL)
 	 	AND CNF_FILIAL = '01' AND CNF.D_E_L_E_T_='')
 LEFT JOIN CNA010 CNA
 	ON (CNA_CONTRA = CNF_CONTRA
 	    AND CNA_CRONOG = CNF_NUMERO
 	    AND CNA_REVISA = CNF_REVISA
 	    AND CNA_NUMERO = CNF_NUMPLA
 		AND CNA_FILIAL = CNF_FILIAL
 	    AND CNA.D_E_L_E_T_='')
 LEFT JOIN CTT010 CTT
 	ON (ISNULL(CND_CONTRA,C5_ESPECI1) = CTT_CUSTO
 		AND CTT_FILIAL = '01'
 		AND CTT.D_E_L_E_T_='')
 WHERE 
 --SUBSTRING(F2_EMISSAO,1,6) >= '201910'
 --AND
 SF2.D_E_L_E_T_=''
 )
  
SELECT CND_CONTRA,X.C5_MDCONTR,X.C5_NUM,X.C5_MDNUMED,X.C5_MDPLANI,CND_REVISA,X.C5_XXREV,CND_PARCEL,CXN_PARCEL,X.C5_XXPARC FROM X 
 --UPDATE SC5010 SET C5_XXREV = X.CND_REVISA,C5_XXPARC = ISNULL(X.CXN_PARCEL,X.CND_PARCEL) FROM X 
 INNER JOIN SC5010  ON SC5010.R_E_C_N_O_ = X.C5RECNO
  WHERE X.C5_MDNUMED <> ' ' AND X.CND_REVISA IS NULL

---- BKTER
 WITH X AS (

SELECT 
    '02' AS EMPRESA,
    'BKTER' AS NOMEEMP,
    '20220527' AS DATAPRC,
    '11:38' AS HORAPRC,
  ISNULL(CND_CONTRA, C5_ESPECI1) AS CND_CONTRA

  	,CND_PEDIDO
	,CND_NUMMED
   ,CNF_CONTRA
   ,CNF_REVISA
   ,CNF_PARCEL
   ,CND_PARCEL
   ,CNA_REVISA
   ,CND_REVISA
   ,CND_REVGER
   ,CXN_REVISA
   ,C5_MDCONTR
,C5_XXREV
,C5_XXPARC
,CXN_PARCEL
,SC5.R_E_C_N_O_ AS C5RECNO,

  CTT_DESC01, 
  C5_XXCOMPM, 
  C5_NUM, 
  C5_MDNUMED, 
  C5_MDPLANI, 
  F2_SERIE, 
  F2_DOC, 
  F2_EMISSAO, 
  F2_VALFAT, 
  CND_USUAR, 
  (
    CASE WHEN CND_NUMERO = '' THEN 'NOVA' ELSE 'ANTIGA' END
  ) AS FORMAMED, 
  CNA_XXMUN  AS CNA_XXMUN,
  CASE WHEN ISNULL(CXN_VLPREV, CND_VLPREV) = CNF_VLPREV THEN CNF_VLPREV ELSE 0 END AS CXN_VLPREV,
   (SELECT SUM(CNR_VALOR)
        FROM CNR020 CNR 
        WHERE 
          C5_MDNUMED = CNR.CNR_NUMMED 
          AND (CNR_CODPLA = ' ' OR CNR_CODPLA = ISNULL(CXN_NUMPLA,CND_NUMERO))
          AND CNR_FILIAL = '01'
          AND CNR.D_E_L_E_T_ = ' ' 
          AND CNR_TIPO = '2' ) AS CNRVLBONI,
   (SELECT SUM(CNR_VALOR)
        FROM CNR020 CNR 
        WHERE 
          C5_MDNUMED = CNR.CNR_NUMMED 
          AND (CNR_CODPLA = ' ' OR CNR_CODPLA = ISNULL(CXN_NUMPLA,CND_NUMERO))
          AND CNR_FILIAL = '01'
          AND CNR.D_E_L_E_T_ = ' ' 
          AND CNR_TIPO = '1' ) AS CNRVLMULT,
  STUFF (
    (
      SELECT 
        ';' + RTRIM(CNR_XTPJUS + '-' + ZR_DESCR) 
      FROM 
        CNR020 CNR 
        INNER JOIN SZR010 SZR ON ZR_TIPO = CNR_XTPJUS 
      WHERE 
        C5_MDNUMED = CNR.CNR_NUMMED 
        AND (CNR_CODPLA = ' ' OR CNR_CODPLA = ISNULL(CXN_NUMPLA,CND_NUMERO))
        AND CNR_FILIAL = CND_FILIAL
        AND CNR.D_E_L_E_T_ = ' ' 
        AND CNR_TIPO = '1' 
      ORDER BY 
        ';' + RTRIM(CNR_XTPJUS + '-' + ZR_DESCR) FOR XML PATH (''), 
        TYPE
    ).value('.', 'varchar(100)'), 
    1, 
    1, 
    ''
  ) AS CNRTPMUL, 
  STUFF (
    (
      SELECT 
        ';' + RTRIM(CNR_DESCRI) 
      FROM 
        CNR020 CNR 
      WHERE 
        C5_MDNUMED = CNR.CNR_NUMMED 
        AND (CNR_CODPLA = ' ' OR CNR_CODPLA = ISNULL(CXN_NUMPLA,CND_NUMERO))
        AND CNR_FILIAL = CND_FILIAL
        AND CNR.D_E_L_E_T_ = ' ' 
        AND CNR_TIPO = '1' 
      ORDER BY 
        ';' + RTRIM(CNR_DESCRI) FOR XML PATH (''), 
        TYPE
    ).value('.', 'varchar(100)'), 
    1, 
    1, 
    ''
  ) AS CNRDESCMUL, 
  STUFF (
    (
      SELECT 
        ';' + RTRIM(CNR_XTPJUS + '-' + ZR_DESCR) 
      FROM 
        CNR020 CNR 
        INNER JOIN SZR010 SZR ON ZR_TIPO = CNR_XTPJUS 
      WHERE 
        C5_MDNUMED = CNR.CNR_NUMMED 
        AND (CNR_CODPLA = ' ' OR CNR_CODPLA = ISNULL(CXN_NUMPLA,CND_NUMERO))
        AND CNR_FILIAL = CND_FILIAL
        AND CNR.D_E_L_E_T_ = ' ' 
        AND CNR_TIPO = '2' 
      ORDER BY 
        ';' + RTRIM(CNR_XTPJUS + '-' + ZR_DESCR) FOR XML PATH (''), 
        TYPE
    ).value('.', 'varchar(100)'), 
    1, 
    1, 
    ''
  ) AS CNRTPBON, 
  STUFF (
    (
      SELECT 
        ';' + RTRIM(CNR_DESCRI) 
      FROM 
        CNR020 CNR 
      WHERE 
        C5_MDNUMED = CNR.CNR_NUMMED 
        AND (CNR_CODPLA = ' ' OR CNR_CODPLA = ISNULL(CXN_NUMPLA,CND_NUMERO))
        AND CNR_FILIAL = CND_FILIAL
        AND CNR.D_E_L_E_T_ = ' ' 
        AND CNR_TIPO = '2' 
      ORDER BY 
        ';' + RTRIM(CNR_DESCRI) FOR XML PATH (''), 
        TYPE
    ).value('.', 'varchar(100)'), 
    1, 
    1, 
    ''
  ) AS CNRDESCBON 
FROM 
  SF2020 SF2 
 LEFT JOIN SC5020 SC5
     ON (C5_NOTA = F2_DOC 
         AND C5_SERIE = F2_SERIE 
         AND C5_FILIAL = F2_FILIAL 
         AND SC5.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''
 ) 
 LEFT JOIN CND020 CND
     ON (CND_NUMMED = C5_MDNUMED 
         AND CND_FILIAL = '01' 
         AND CND.D_E_L_E_T_ = '' 
         AND CND.R_E_C_N_O_ = (
         SELECT 
            MIN(R_E_C_N_O_) 
         FROM 
            CND020 CND1 
         WHERE 
            CND1.CND_NUMMED = C5_MDNUMED 
            AND CND1.CND_FILIAL = '01' 
            AND CND1.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''
    )
  ) 
 LEFT JOIN CXN020 CXN
     ON (CXN_CONTRA = C5_MDCONTR 
         AND CXN_NUMMED = C5_MDNUMED 
         AND CXN_NUMPLA = C5_MDPLANI 
         AND CXN_REVISA = CND_REVISA 
         AND CXN.CXN_CHECK = 'T' 
         AND CXN_FILIAL = F2_FILIAL 
         AND CXN.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''
  ) 
 LEFT JOIN CNF020 CNF
 	ON (CND_CONTRA = CNF_CONTRA AND C5_XXCOMPM = CNF_COMPET
 	    AND ISNULL(CXN_NUMPLA,CND_NUMERO) = CNF_NUMPLA
 	    AND ISNULL(CXN_REVISA,CND_REVISA) = CNF_REVISA
 	    AND CNF_PARCEL = ISNULL(CXN_PARCEL,CND_PARCEL)
 	 	AND CNF_FILIAL = F2_FILIAL AND CNF.D_E_L_E_T_=''
  ) 
 LEFT JOIN CNA020 CNA
 	ON (CNA_CONTRA = CNF_CONTRA
 	 	AND CNA_CRONOG = CNF_NUMERO
 	 	AND CNA_REVISA = CNF_REVISA
 	 	AND CNA_NUMERO = CNF_NUMPLA
 		AND CNA_FILIAL = CNF_FILIAL AND CNA.D_E_L_E_T_=''
  ) 
 LEFT JOIN CTT020 CTT
     ON (ISNULL(CND_CONTRA, C5_ESPECI1) = CTT_CUSTO 
 		AND CTT_FILIAL = '01'
         AND CTT.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''
  ) 
WHERE 
  SF2.D_E_L_E_T_ = '' 
)
--SELECT * FROM X 
 
 --SELECT CND_CONTRA,X.C5_MDCONTR,X.C5_NUM,X.C5_MDNUMED,X.C5_MDPLANI,CND_REVISA,X.C5_XXREV,CND_PARCEL,CXN_PARCEL,X.C5_XXPARC FROM X 
 UPDATE SC5020 SET C5_XXREV = X.CND_REVISA,C5_XXPARC = ISNULL(X.CXN_PARCEL,X.CND_PARCEL) FROM X 
 INNER JOIN SC5020  ON SC5020.R_E_C_N_O_ = X.C5RECNO
  WHERE X.C5_MDNUMED <> ' ' --AND X.CND_REVISA <> CND_REVGER --IS NULL

----- BALSA

WITH X AS (
SELECT 
    '14' AS EMPRESA,
    'BALSA NOVA' AS NOMEEMP,
    '20220527' AS DATAPRC,
    '11:38' AS HORAPRC,
  ISNULL(CND_CONTRA, C5_ESPECI1) AS CND_CONTRA, 

  	CND_PEDIDO
	,CND_NUMMED
   ,CNF_CONTRA
   ,CNF_REVISA
   ,CNF_PARCEL
   ,CND_PARCEL
   ,CNA_REVISA
   ,CND_REVISA
   ,CND_REVGER
   ,CXN_REVISA
   ,C5_MDCONTR
,C5_XXREV
,C5_XXPARC
,CXN_PARCEL
,SC5.R_E_C_N_O_ AS C5RECNO,

  CTT_DESC01, 
  C5_XXCOMPM, 
  C5_NUM, 
  C5_MDNUMED, 
  C5_MDPLANI, 
  F2_SERIE, 
  F2_DOC, 
  F2_EMISSAO, 
  F2_VALFAT, 
  CND_USUAR, 
  (
    CASE WHEN CND_NUMERO = '' THEN 'NOVA' ELSE 'ANTIGA' END
  ) AS FORMAMED, 
  CNA_XXMUN  AS CNA_XXMUN,
  CASE WHEN ISNULL(CXN_VLPREV, CND_VLPREV) = CNF_VLPREV THEN CNF_VLPREV ELSE 0 END AS CXN_VLPREV,
   (SELECT SUM(CNR_VALOR)
        FROM CNR140 CNR 
        WHERE 
          C5_MDNUMED = CNR.CNR_NUMMED 
          AND (CNR_CODPLA = ' ' OR CNR_CODPLA = ISNULL(CXN_NUMPLA,CND_NUMERO))
          AND CNR_FILIAL = '01'
          AND CNR.D_E_L_E_T_ = ' ' 
          AND CNR_TIPO = '2' ) AS CNRVLBONI,
   (SELECT SUM(CNR_VALOR)
        FROM CNR140 CNR 
        WHERE 
          C5_MDNUMED = CNR.CNR_NUMMED 
          AND (CNR_CODPLA = ' ' OR CNR_CODPLA = ISNULL(CXN_NUMPLA,CND_NUMERO))
          AND CNR_FILIAL = '01'
          AND CNR.D_E_L_E_T_ = ' ' 
          AND CNR_TIPO = '1' ) AS CNRVLMULT,
  STUFF (
    (
      SELECT 
        ';' + RTRIM(CNR_XTPJUS + '-' + ZR_DESCR) 
      FROM 
        CNR140 CNR 
        INNER JOIN SZR010 SZR ON ZR_TIPO = CNR_XTPJUS 
      WHERE 
        C5_MDNUMED = CNR.CNR_NUMMED 
        AND (CNR_CODPLA = ' ' OR CNR_CODPLA = ISNULL(CXN_NUMPLA,CND_NUMERO))
        AND CNR_FILIAL = CND_FILIAL
        AND CNR.D_E_L_E_T_ = ' ' 
        AND CNR_TIPO = '1' 
      ORDER BY 
        ';' + RTRIM(CNR_XTPJUS + '-' + ZR_DESCR) FOR XML PATH (''), 
        TYPE
    ).value('.', 'varchar(100)'), 
    1, 
    1, 
    ''
  ) AS CNRTPMUL, 
  STUFF (
    (
      SELECT 
        ';' + RTRIM(CNR_DESCRI) 
      FROM 
        CNR140 CNR 
      WHERE 
        C5_MDNUMED = CNR.CNR_NUMMED 
        AND (CNR_CODPLA = ' ' OR CNR_CODPLA = ISNULL(CXN_NUMPLA,CND_NUMERO))
        AND CNR_FILIAL = CND_FILIAL
        AND CNR.D_E_L_E_T_ = ' ' 
        AND CNR_TIPO = '1' 
      ORDER BY 
        ';' + RTRIM(CNR_DESCRI) FOR XML PATH (''), 
        TYPE
    ).value('.', 'varchar(100)'), 
    1, 
    1, 
    ''
  ) AS CNRDESCMUL, 
  STUFF (
    (
      SELECT 
        ';' + RTRIM(CNR_XTPJUS + '-' + ZR_DESCR) 
      FROM 
        CNR140 CNR 
        INNER JOIN SZR010 SZR ON ZR_TIPO = CNR_XTPJUS 
      WHERE 
        C5_MDNUMED = CNR.CNR_NUMMED 
        AND (CNR_CODPLA = ' ' OR CNR_CODPLA = ISNULL(CXN_NUMPLA,CND_NUMERO))
        AND CNR_FILIAL = CND_FILIAL
        AND CNR.D_E_L_E_T_ = ' ' 
        AND CNR_TIPO = '2' 
      ORDER BY 
        ';' + RTRIM(CNR_XTPJUS + '-' + ZR_DESCR) FOR XML PATH (''), 
        TYPE
    ).value('.', 'varchar(100)'), 
    1, 
    1, 
    ''
  ) AS CNRTPBON, 
  STUFF (
    (
      SELECT 
        ';' + RTRIM(CNR_DESCRI) 
      FROM 
        CNR140 CNR 
      WHERE 
        C5_MDNUMED = CNR.CNR_NUMMED 
        AND (CNR_CODPLA = ' ' OR CNR_CODPLA = ISNULL(CXN_NUMPLA,CND_NUMERO))
        AND CNR_FILIAL = CND_FILIAL
        AND CNR.D_E_L_E_T_ = ' ' 
        AND CNR_TIPO = '2' 
      ORDER BY 
        ';' + RTRIM(CNR_DESCRI) FOR XML PATH (''), 
        TYPE
    ).value('.', 'varchar(100)'), 
    1, 
    1, 
    ''
  ) AS CNRDESCBON 
FROM 
  SF2140 SF2 
 LEFT JOIN SC5140 SC5
     ON (C5_NOTA = F2_DOC 
         AND C5_SERIE = F2_SERIE 
         AND C5_FILIAL = F2_FILIAL 
         AND SC5.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''
 ) 
 LEFT JOIN CND140 CND
     ON (CND_NUMMED = C5_MDNUMED 
         AND CND_FILIAL = '01' 
         AND CND.D_E_L_E_T_ = '' 
         AND CND.R_E_C_N_O_ = (
         SELECT 
            MIN(R_E_C_N_O_) 
         FROM 
            CND140 CND1 
         WHERE 
            CND1.CND_NUMMED = C5_MDNUMED 
            AND CND1.CND_FILIAL = '01' 
            AND CND1.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''
    )
  ) 
 LEFT JOIN CXN140 CXN
     ON (CXN_CONTRA = C5_MDCONTR 
         AND CXN_NUMMED = C5_MDNUMED 
         AND CXN_NUMPLA = C5_MDPLANI 
         AND CXN_REVISA = CND_REVISA 
         AND CXN.CXN_CHECK = 'T' 
         AND CXN_FILIAL = F2_FILIAL 
         AND CXN.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''
  ) 
 LEFT JOIN CNF140 CNF
 	ON (CND_CONTRA = CNF_CONTRA AND C5_XXCOMPM = CNF_COMPET
 	    AND ISNULL(CXN_NUMPLA,CND_NUMERO) = CNF_NUMPLA
 	    AND ISNULL(CXN_REVISA,CND_REVISA) = CNF_REVISA
 	    AND CNF_PARCEL = ISNULL(CXN_PARCEL,CND_PARCEL)
 	 	AND CNF_FILIAL = F2_FILIAL AND CNF.D_E_L_E_T_=''
  ) 
 LEFT JOIN CNA140 CNA
 	ON (CNA_CONTRA = CNF_CONTRA
 	 	AND CNA_CRONOG = CNF_NUMERO
 	 	AND CNA_REVISA = CNF_REVISA
 	 	AND CNA_NUMERO = CNF_NUMPLA
 		AND CNA_FILIAL = CNF_FILIAL AND CNA.D_E_L_E_T_=''
  ) 
 LEFT JOIN CTT140 CTT
     ON (ISNULL(CND_CONTRA, C5_ESPECI1) = CTT_CUSTO 
 		AND CTT_FILIAL = '01'
         AND CTT.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''
  ) 
WHERE 
  SF2.D_E_L_E_T_ = '' 
  )
--SELECT * FROM X 
 
 --SELECT CND_CONTRA,X.C5_MDCONTR,X.C5_NUM,X.C5_MDNUMED,X.C5_MDPLANI,CND_REVISA,X.C5_XXREV,CND_PARCEL,CXN_PARCEL,X.C5_XXPARC FROM X 
UPDATE SC5140 SET C5_XXREV = X.CND_REVISA,C5_XXPARC = ISNULL(X.CXN_PARCEL,X.CND_PARCEL) FROM X 
 INNER JOIN SC5140  ON SC5140.R_E_C_N_O_ = X.C5RECNO
  WHERE X.C5_MDNUMED <> ' ' --AND X.CND_REVISA IS NULL -- <> CND_REVGER

SELECT EMPRESA,F2_SERIE,F2_DOC FROM FATURAMENTO --WHERE CND_CONTRA = '385000595'
GROUP BY EMPRESA,F2_SERIE,F2_DOC
HAVING Count(*) > 1

SELECT SUM(CNRVLBONI),SUM(CNRVLMULT) FROM FATURAMENTO WHERE  C5_XXCOMPM = '04/2022'AND EMPRESA = '14'
SELECT SUM(CNR_VALOR) FROM GLOSAS WHERE CNR_TIPO = '2'AND C5_XXCOMPM = '04/2022' AND EMPRESA = '14'
SELECT SUM(CNR_VALOR) FROM GLOSAS WHERE CNR_TIPO = '1'AND C5_XXCOMPM = '04/2022'AND EMPRESA = '14'

SELECT SUM(F2_VALFAT) FROM FATURAMENTO WHERE C5_XXCOMPM = '04/2022'

SELECT * FROM GLOSAS

20/05/22  - Alterao de Fornecedor - Doc de Entrada

SELECT * FROM SA2010 WHERE A2_COD = '500626'

SELECT E2_EMISSAO,E2_NUM,E2_FORNECE,E2_LOJA,E2_NOMFOR,E2_BAIXA,* FROM SE2010 
WHERE E2_NUM IN ('000428607' ,'000430004') 
	  AND E2_FORNECE ='000075'

UPDATE SE2010 SET E2_FORNECE='500626', E2_NOMFOR = 'TELEFONICA BRASIL SA'
WHERE E2_NUM IN ('000428607' ,'000430004') 
	  AND E2_FORNECE ='000075'

SELECT E5_DATA,E5_NUMERO,E5_CLIFOR,E5_LOJA,E5_BENEF,E5_FORNECE,* FROM SE5010 
WHERE E5_NUMERO IN ('000428607' ,'000430004') 
	  AND E5_FORNECE ='000075'

UPDATE SE5010 SET E5_FORNECE='500626', E5_CLIFOR='500626', E5_BENEF = 'TELEFONICA BRASIL S.A.'
WHERE E5_NUMERO IN ('000428607' ,'000430004') 
	  AND E5_FORNECE ='000075'

	  --AND EF_FORNECE ='000075'

	  AND F1_FORNECE ='000075'

	  AND D1_FORNECE ='000075'

select D_E_L_E_T_,* from CT2010 WHERE CT2_HIST LIKE 'NF: 000002640%'
UNION ALL
select D_E_L_E_T_,* from CT2010 WHERE CT2_HIST LIKE 'NF: 000002641%'
UNION ALL
select D_E_L_E_T_,* from CT2010 WHERE CT2_HIST LIKE 'NF: 000003075%'
UNION ALL
select D_E_L_E_T_,* from CT2010 WHERE CT2_HIST LIKE 'NF: 000003076%'
UNION ALL
select D_E_L_E_T_,* from CT2010 WHERE CT2_HIST LIKE 'NF: 000003282%'
UNION ALL
select D_E_L_E_T_,* from CT2010 WHERE CT2_HIST LIKE 'NF: 000003283%'
UNION ALL
select D_E_L_E_T_,* from CT2010 WHERE CT2_HIST LIKE 'NF: FC0000021%'
UNION ALL
select D_E_L_E_T_,* from CT2010 WHERE CT2_HIST LIKE 'NF: FEE000008%'
UNION ALL
select D_E_L_E_T_,* from CT2010 WHERE CT2_HIST LIKE 'NF:000003459%'
UNION ALL
select D_E_L_E_T_,* from CT2010 WHERE CT2_HIST LIKE 'NF:000003460:%'
UNION ALL
select D_E_L_E_T_,* from CT2010 WHERE CT2_HIST LIKE 'NF:000004100:M%'
UNION ALL

UNION ALL

12/05/22 

--DROP TABLE PowerBk.dbo.GASTOSGERAIS

WITH GASTOSGERAIS AS (
SELECT 

 SUBSTRING(E2_VENCREA,5,2)+'/'+SUBSTRING(E2_VENCREA,1,4) AS COMPET,
 D1_FILIAL,
 D1_SERIE,
 D1_DOC,
 D1_FORNECE,
 D1_LOJA,
 D1_ITEM,
 D1_COD,
 B1_DESC,
 B1_GRUPO,
 D1_CC,
 F1_VALBRUT,
 E2_PARCELA,
 E2_VENCREA,
 E2_VALOR,
 E2_DESCONT,
 E2_MULTA,
 E2_JUROS,
 E2_ACRESC,
 E2_DECRESC,
 E2_VRETPIS,
 E2_VRETCOF,
 E2_VRETCSL,
 E2_VRETINS,
 E2_VRETIRF,
 E2_VRETISS,

 E2_VALOR+E2_VRETPIS+E2_VRETCOF+E2_VRETCSL+E2_VRETINS+E2_VRETIRF+E2_VRETISS AS E2VALTIT,
 (D1_TOTAL+D1_VALFRE+D1_SEGURO+D1_DESPESA-D1_VALDESC)  AS D1TOTAL,

 CASE WHEN E2_ACRESC  > 0 THEN E2_ACRESC  ELSE E2_MULTA+E2_JUROS END - 
 CASE WHEN E2_DECRESC > 0 THEN E2_DECRESC ELSE E2_DESCONT END AS E2ACDEC

 FROM SD1010 SD1
 INNER JOIN SB1010 SB1 ON B1_FILIAL = '01' AND D1_COD = B1_COD  AND SB1.D_E_L_E_T_ = '' 
 INNER JOIN SE2010 SE2 ON SE2.D_E_L_E_T_='' AND SE2.E2_FILIAL = '01' AND E2_TIPO ='NF' 
   AND E2_PREFIXO = D1_SERIE
   AND E2_NUM = D1_DOC
   AND E2_FORNECE = D1_FORNECE
   AND E2_LOJA = D1_LOJA
 INNER JOIN SF1010 SF1 ON F1_FILIAL = D1_FILIAL AND F1_DOC = D1_DOC AND F1_SERIE = D1_SERIE AND F1_FORNECE = D1_FORNECE AND F1_LOJA = D1_LOJA AND SF1.D_E_L_E_T_ = ' '

 WHERE SD1.D_E_L_E_T_ = '' 
 --AND SUBSTRING(D1_DTDIGIT,1,6)  = '202302' 
 --AND D1_CC = '005000114'
 AND D1_FILIAL = '01'
 AND (SUBSTRING(B1_CONTA,1,1) = '3' OR B1_CONTA in ('29104004') OR SUBSTRING(B1_CONTA,1,5) IN ('12201','12105'))
 
 --AND D1_DOC = '000305019' and D1_FORNECE = '500095'
 )
SELECT *,
	   (E2ACDEC  / F1_VALBRUT * D1TOTAL)   AS E2ACDECIT,
	   (E2VALTIT / F1_VALBRUT * D1TOTAL)   AS D1TOTIT,
       (E2ACDEC  / F1_VALBRUT * D1TOTAL) + (E2VALTIT / F1_VALBRUT * D1TOTAL)  AS DESPESA
	   
	   INTO PowerBk.dbo.DESPESAS FROM DESPESAS

	  
--SELECT SUM(D1TOTAL+E2ACDECIT),SUM(E2ACDECIT),SUM(D1TOTAL),MAX(F1_VALBRUT) FROM DESPESAS

 /*

 GROUP BY SUBSTRING(D1_DTDIGIT,1,6),D1_FILIAL,D1_SERIE,D1_DOC,D1_FORNECE,D1_LOJA,D1_COD,B1_DESC,B1_GRUPO,D1_CC
 UNION ALL

 SELECT SUBSTRING(D3_EMISSAO,1,6) AS COMPET,D3_FILIAL,MAX(' '),MAX(' '),MAX(' '),MAX(' '),D3_COD,B1_DESC,B1_GRUPO,D3_CC,SUM(D3_CUSTO1) FROM SD3010 SD3
 INNER JOIN SB1010 SB1 ON B1_FILIAL = '01' AND D3_COD = B1_COD  AND SB1.D_E_L_E_T_ = '' 
 WHERE SD3.D_E_L_E_T_='' AND D3_TM='501' 
 --AND SUBSTRING(D3_EMISSAO,1,6) = '202302'
 --AND D3_CC = '005000114'
 AND (SUBSTRING(D3_CONTA,1,1) = '3' OR D3_CONTA in ('29104004') OR SUBSTRING(D3_CONTA,1,5) IN ('12201','12105'))
 GROUP BY SUBSTRING(D3_EMISSAO,1,6),D3_FILIAL,D3_COD,B1_DESC,B1_GRUPO,D3_CC
*/

DROP TABLE PROJXREALT
SELECT 
XX_LINHA,
[XX_CODGCT],
[XX_COMPET],
[XX_DESC],
[XX_PROJ],
[XX_REAL],
[XX_DIF],
[XX_PROJN],
[XX_REALN],
[XX_DIFN],
[XX_POWERBK],
[D_E_L_E_T_],
[R_E_C_N_O_],
[R_E_C_D_E_L_]
INTO PROJXREALT FROM PROJXREALT01
UNION SELECT 
XX_LINHA,
[XX_CODGCT],
[XX_COMPET],
[XX_DESC],
[XX_PROJ],
[XX_REAL],
[XX_DIF],
[XX_PROJN],
[XX_REALN],
[XX_DIFN],
[XX_POWERBK],
[D_E_L_E_T_],
[R_E_C_N_O_],
[R_E_C_D_E_L_]

FROM PROJXREALT02
UNION  SELECT 
XX_LINHA,
[XX_CODGCT],
[XX_COMPET],
[XX_DESC],
[XX_PROJ],
[XX_REAL],
[XX_DIF],
[XX_PROJN],
[XX_REALN],
[XX_DIFN],
[XX_POWERBK],
[D_E_L_E_T_],
[R_E_C_N_O_],
[R_E_C_D_E_L_]
FROM PROJXREALT14

10/05/22 

select DISTINCT F2_SERIE,F2_DOC,F2_TIPO,F2_XXVCVIN,F2_XXVRETC,F2_VALFAT,E1_VALOR,E1_XXVCVIN ,E1_XXVRETC
--UPDATE SE1010 SET E1_XXVCVIN = F2_XXVCVIN
FROM SF2010 SF2
LEFT JOIN
 SE1010 SE1 ON E1_PREFIXO = F2_SERIE AND E1_NUM = F2_DOC AND E1_TIPO = 'NF'
   	AND SE1.D_E_L_E_T_ = ' ' 
	WHERE (F2_XXVCVIN > 0 OR F2_XXVRETC > 0) AND SF2.D_E_L_E_T_ = ' ' --AND E1_XXVCVIN = 0

09/05/22 EFD na Base Teste

UPDATE SE1010 SET E1_VENCTO = E1_EMISSAO, E1_VENCREA = E1_EMISSAO, E1_MOVIMEN = E1_EMISSAO, E1_VENCORI = E1_EMISSAO  WHERE SUBSTRING(E1_EMISSAO,1,6) >= '201901' AND SE1010.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''
UPDATE SE1010 SET E1_BAIXA = E1_EMISSAO WHERE SUBSTRING(E1_EMISSAO,1,6) >= '201901' AND SE1010.D_E_L_E_T_ = '' AND E1_BAIXA <> ''

UPDATE SE5010 SET E5_DATA=E1_EMISSAO,E5_VENCTO=E1_EMISSAO,E5_DTDIGIT=E1_EMISSAO,E5_DTDISPO=E1_EMISSAO
 FROM SE5010 INNER JOIN SE1010 ON E5_FILIAL+E5_PREFIXO+E5_NUMERO+E5_PARCELA+E5_CLIFOR+E5_LOJA = E1_FILIAL+E1_PREFIXO+E1_NUM+E1_PARCELA+E1_CLIENTE+E1_LOJA 
WHERE SUBSTRING(E1_EMISSAO,1,6) >= '201901'  AND E1_BAIXA <> '' AND SE1010.D_E_L_E_T_ = '' AND SE5010.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''

UPDATE FK1010 SET FK1_DATA = E5_DATA FROM FK1010 INNER JOIN SE5010 ON FK1_IDFK1 = E5_IDORIG
WHERE SUBSTRING(E5_DATA,1,6) >= '201901' 


SELECT D_E_L_E_T_,* FROM SE1010 WHERE E1_NUM >= 'EL0000100' AND E1_NUM <= 'EL0000110'
SELECT D_E_L_E_T_,* FROM SF2010 WHERE F2_DOC >= 'EL0000100' AND F2_DOC <= 'EL0000110'

SELECT D_E_L_E_T_,* FROM SE5010 WHERE E5_NUMERO >= 'EL0000100' AND E5_NUMERO <= 'EL0000110'


SELECT * FROM SD2010 WHERE D2_DOC = 'EL0000104'

-- Baixar os titulos em aberto no periodo (Baixa automatica) de 01/01/2019 a 31/12/2022 database 31/12/2022

SELECT * FROM SE1010 WHERE E1_BAIXA = '' AND SUBSTRING(E1_VENCREA,1,6) > '202112' AND E1_TIPO = 'NF' AND SE1010.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''

UPDATE SE1010 SET E1_VENCTO = E1_EMISSAO, E1_VENCREA = E1_EMISSAO, E1_MOVIMEN = E1_EMISSAO, E1_VENCORI = E1_EMISSAO  WHERE SUBSTRING(E1_EMISSAO,1,6) >= '202112' AND SE1010.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''
UPDATE SE1010 SET E1_BAIXA = E1_EMISSAO WHERE SUBSTRING(E1_EMISSAO,1,6) >= '202112' AND SE1010.D_E_L_E_T_ = '' AND E1_BAIXA <> ''

SELECT E5_FILIAL+E5_PREFIXO+E5_NUMERO+E5_PARCELA+E5_TIPO+E5_CLIFOR+E5_LOJA,E1_FILIAL+E1_PREFIXO+E1_NUM+E1_PARCELA+E1_TIPO+E1_CLIENTE+E1_LOJA,
E1_VALOR,E5_VALOR,E1_EMISSAO,E1_BAIXA,E5_DATA,E5_VENCTO,E5_DTDIGIT,E5_DTDISPO
 FROM SE5010 LEFT JOIN SE1010 ON E5_FILIAL+E5_PREFIXO+E5_NUMERO+E5_PARCELA+E5_CLIFOR+E5_LOJA = E1_FILIAL+E1_PREFIXO+E1_NUM+E1_PARCELA+E1_CLIENTE+E1_LOJA 
WHERE SUBSTRING(E1_EMISSAO,1,6) >= '202112'  AND E1_BAIXA <> '' AND SE1010.D_E_L_E_T_ = '' AND SE5010.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''


UPDATE SE5010 SET E5_DATA=E1_EMISSAO,E5_VENCTO=E1_EMISSAO,E5_DTDIGIT=E1_EMISSAO,E5_DTDISPO=E1_EMISSAO
 FROM SE5010 INNER JOIN SE1010 ON E5_FILIAL+E5_PREFIXO+E5_NUMERO+E5_PARCELA+E5_CLIFOR+E5_LOJA = E1_FILIAL+E1_PREFIXO+E1_NUM+E1_PARCELA+E1_CLIENTE+E1_LOJA 
WHERE SUBSTRING(E1_EMISSAO,1,6) >= '202112'  AND E1_BAIXA <> '' AND SE1010.D_E_L_E_T_ = '' AND SE5010.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''

UPDATE FK1010 SET FK1_DATA = E5_DATA FROM FK1010 INNER JOIN SE5010 ON FK1_IDFK1 = E5_IDORIG
WHERE SUBSTRING(E5_DATA,1,6) >= '202112'

--Remover flag de cauo em contratos com situao = sol Finalizao

SELECT CN9_NUMERO,CN9_REVISA,CN9_XXDESC,CN9_FLGCAU FROM CN9010 WHERE CN9_SITUAC = '07' AND D_E_L_E_T_ = ''
ORDER BY CN9_NUMERO,CN9_REVISA
UPDATE CN9010 SET CN9_FLGCAU = '2' WHERE CN9_SITUAC = '07' AND D_E_L_E_T_ = ''

--Remover falg de cauo em contratos com situao = vigente
UPDATE CN9010 SET CN9_FLGCAU = '2' WHERE CN9_SITUAC = '05' AND D_E_L_E_T_ = ''
