UPDATE SE1010 SET E1_VENCTO = E1_EMISSAO, E1_VENCREA = E1_EMISSAO, E1_MOVIMEN = E1_EMISSAO, E1_VENCORI = E1_EMISSAO  WHERE SUBSTRING(E1_EMISSAO,1,6) >= '201901' AND SE1010.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''
UPDATE SE1010 SET E1_BAIXA = E1_EMISSAO WHERE SUBSTRING(E1_EMISSAO,1,6) >= '201901' AND SE1010.D_E_L_E_T_ = '' AND E1_BAIXA <> ''

UPDATE SE1140 SET E1_VENCTO = E1_EMISSAO, E1_VENCREA = E1_EMISSAO, E1_MOVIMEN = E1_EMISSAO, E1_VENCORI = E1_EMISSAO  WHERE SUBSTRING(E1_EMISSAO,1,6) >= '201901' AND SE1140.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''
UPDATE SE1140 SET E1_BAIXA = E1_EMISSAO WHERE SUBSTRING(E1_EMISSAO,1,6) >= '201901' AND SE1140.D_E_L_E_T_ = '' AND E1_BAIXA <> ''


SELECT E5_FILIAL+E5_PREFIXO+E5_NUMERO+E5_PARCELA+E5_TIPO+E5_CLIFOR+E5_LOJA,E1_FILIAL+E1_PREFIXO+E1_NUM+E1_PARCELA+E1_TIPO+E1_CLIENTE+E1_LOJA,
E1_VALOR,E5_VALOR,E1_EMISSAO,E1_BAIXA,E5_DATA,E5_VENCTO,E5_DTDIGIT,E5_DTDISPO
 FROM SE5010 LEFT JOIN SE1010 ON E5_FILIAL+E5_PREFIXO+E5_NUMERO+E5_PARCELA+E5_CLIFOR+E5_LOJA = E1_FILIAL+E1_PREFIXO+E1_NUM+E1_PARCELA+E1_CLIENTE+E1_LOJA 
WHERE SUBSTRING(E1_EMISSAO,1,6) >= '201901'  AND E1_BAIXA <> '' AND SE1010.D_E_L_E_T_ = '' AND SE5010.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''


UPDATE SE5010 SET E5_DATA=E1_EMISSAO,E5_VENCTO=E1_EMISSAO,E5_DTDIGIT=E1_EMISSAO,E5_DTDISPO=E1_EMISSAO
 FROM SE5010 INNER JOIN SE1010 ON E5_FILIAL+E5_PREFIXO+E5_NUMERO+E5_PARCELA+E5_CLIFOR+E5_LOJA = E1_FILIAL+E1_PREFIXO+E1_NUM+E1_PARCELA+E1_CLIENTE+E1_LOJA 
WHERE SUBSTRING(E1_EMISSAO,1,6) >= '201901'  AND E1_BAIXA <> '' AND SE1010.D_E_L_E_T_ = '' AND SE5010.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''

UPDATE FK1010 SET FK1_DATA = E5_DATA FROM FK1010 INNER JOIN SE5010 ON FK1_IDFK1 = E5_IDORIG
WHERE SUBSTRING(E5_DATA,1,6) >= '201901' 

-- Baixar os titulos em aberto no periodo (Baixa automatica)

SELECT * FROM SE1140 WHERE E1_BAIXA = '' AND SUBSTRING(E1_EMISSAO,1,6) = '201912' AND E1_TIPO = 'NF' AND SE1140.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''

22/04/22 - LANAMENTOS EM CONTRATOS VENCIDOS

WITH AVISO AS ( 
SELECT 
    '01' AS EMPRESA,
    'BK' AS NOMEEMP,
    E2_VENCREA, 
    E2_EMIS1, 
    E2_PREFIXO, 
    E2_NUM, 
    E2_PARCELA, 
    ISNULL(Z2_CC, D1_CC) AS D1_CC, 
    CTT_DESC01, 
    ISNULL(D1_COD, 'RH') AS D1_COD, 
    ISNULL(Z2_NOME, B1_DESC) AS B1_DESC, 
    ISNULL(D1_TOTAL, Z2_VALOR) AS D1_TOTAL, 
    (
      SELECT 
        MAX(CNF_DTVENC) 
      FROM 
        CNF010 CNF 
      WHERE 
        CNF_CONTRA = ISNULL(Z2_CC, D1_CC) 
        AND CNF.D_E_L_E_T_ = '' 
      GROUP BY 
        CNF_CONTRA
    ) AS CNFDVIG 
  FROM 
    SE2010 SE2 
    LEFT JOIN SZ2010 SZ2 ON Z2_CODEMP = '01' 
    AND Z2_E2PRF = E2_PREFIXO 
    AND Z2_E2NUM = E2_NUM 
    AND Z2_E2PARC = E2_PARCELA 
    AND Z2_E2TIPO = E2_TIPO 
    AND Z2_E2FORN = E2_FORNECE 
    AND Z2_E2LOJA = E2_LOJA 
    AND SZ2.D_E_L_E_T_ = '' 
    LEFT JOIN SD1010 SD1 ON D1_DOC = E2_NUM 
    AND D1_SERIE = E2_PREFIXO 
    AND D1_FORNECE = E2_FORNECE 
    AND D1_LOJA = E2_LOJA 
    AND SD1.D_E_L_E_T_ = '' 
    LEFT JOIN SB1010 SB1 ON B1_COD = D1_COD 
    AND SB1.D_E_L_E_T_ = '' 
    LEFT JOIN CTT010 CTT ON CTT_CUSTO = ISNULL(D1_CC, Z2_CC) 
    AND CTT.D_E_L_E_T_ = '' 
  WHERE 
    E2_VENCREA > '20220422' 
    AND SE2.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''
UNION ALL 
SELECT 
    '02' AS EMPRESA,
    'BKTER' AS NOMEEMP,
    E2_VENCREA, 
    E2_EMIS1, 
    E2_PREFIXO, 
    E2_NUM, 
    E2_PARCELA, 
    ISNULL(Z2_CC, D1_CC) AS D1_CC, 
    CTT_DESC01, 
    ISNULL(D1_COD, 'RH') AS D1_COD, 
    ISNULL(Z2_NOME, B1_DESC) AS B1_DESC, 
    ISNULL(D1_TOTAL, Z2_VALOR) AS D1_TOTAL, 
    (
      SELECT 
        MAX(CNF_DTVENC) 
      FROM 
        CNF020 CNF 
      WHERE 
        CNF_CONTRA = ISNULL(Z2_CC, D1_CC) 
        AND CNF.D_E_L_E_T_ = '' 
      GROUP BY 
        CNF_CONTRA
    ) AS CNFDVIG 
  FROM 
    SE2020 SE2 
    LEFT JOIN SZ2010 SZ2 ON Z2_CODEMP = '02' 
    AND Z2_E2PRF = E2_PREFIXO 
    AND Z2_E2NUM = E2_NUM 
    AND Z2_E2PARC = E2_PARCELA 
    AND Z2_E2TIPO = E2_TIPO 
    AND Z2_E2FORN = E2_FORNECE 
    AND Z2_E2LOJA = E2_LOJA 
    AND SZ2.D_E_L_E_T_ = '' 
    LEFT JOIN SD1020 SD1 ON D1_DOC = E2_NUM 
    AND D1_SERIE = E2_PREFIXO 
    AND D1_FORNECE = E2_FORNECE 
    AND D1_LOJA = E2_LOJA 
    AND SD1.D_E_L_E_T_ = '' 
    LEFT JOIN SB1020 SB1 ON B1_COD = D1_COD 
    AND SB1.D_E_L_E_T_ = '' 
    LEFT JOIN CTT010 CTT ON CTT_CUSTO = ISNULL(D1_CC, Z2_CC) 
    AND CTT.D_E_L_E_T_ = '' 
  WHERE 
    E2_VENCREA > '20220422' 
    AND SE2.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''
UNION ALL 
SELECT 
    '14' AS EMPRESA,
    'BALSA NOVA' AS NOMEEMP,
    E2_VENCREA, 
    E2_EMIS1, 
    E2_PREFIXO, 
    E2_NUM, 
    E2_PARCELA, 
    ISNULL(Z2_CC, D1_CC) AS D1_CC, 
    CTT_DESC01, 
    ISNULL(D1_COD, 'RH') AS D1_COD, 
    ISNULL(Z2_NOME, B1_DESC) AS B1_DESC, 
    ISNULL(D1_TOTAL, Z2_VALOR) AS D1_TOTAL, 
    (
      SELECT 
        MAX(CNF_DTVENC) 
      FROM 
        CNF140 CNF 
      WHERE 
        CNF_CONTRA = ISNULL(Z2_CC, D1_CC) 
        AND CNF.D_E_L_E_T_ = '' 
      GROUP BY 
        CNF_CONTRA
    ) AS CNFDVIG 
  FROM 
    SE2140 SE2 
    LEFT JOIN SZ2010 SZ2 ON Z2_CODEMP = '14' 
    AND Z2_E2PRF = E2_PREFIXO 
    AND Z2_E2NUM = E2_NUM 
    AND Z2_E2PARC = E2_PARCELA 
    AND Z2_E2TIPO = E2_TIPO 
    AND Z2_E2FORN = E2_FORNECE 
    AND Z2_E2LOJA = E2_LOJA 
    AND SZ2.D_E_L_E_T_ = '' 
    LEFT JOIN SD1140 SD1 ON D1_DOC = E2_NUM 
    AND D1_SERIE = E2_PREFIXO 
    AND D1_FORNECE = E2_FORNECE 
    AND D1_LOJA = E2_LOJA 
    AND SD1.D_E_L_E_T_ = '' 
    LEFT JOIN SB1140 SB1 ON B1_COD = D1_COD 
    AND SB1.D_E_L_E_T_ = '' 
    LEFT JOIN CTT010 CTT ON CTT_CUSTO = ISNULL(D1_CC, Z2_CC) 
    AND CTT.D_E_L_E_T_ = '' 
  WHERE 
    E2_VENCREA > '20220422' 
    AND SE2.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''
UNION ALL 
SELECT 
    '15' AS EMPRESA,
    'BHG INT 3' AS NOMEEMP,
    E2_VENCREA, 
    E2_EMIS1, 
    E2_PREFIXO, 
    E2_NUM, 
    E2_PARCELA, 
    ISNULL(Z2_CC, D1_CC) AS D1_CC, 
    CTT_DESC01, 
    ISNULL(D1_COD, 'RH') AS D1_COD, 
    ISNULL(Z2_NOME, B1_DESC) AS B1_DESC, 
    ISNULL(D1_TOTAL, Z2_VALOR) AS D1_TOTAL, 
    (
      SELECT 
        MAX(CNF_DTVENC) 
      FROM 
        CNF150 CNF 
      WHERE 
        CNF_CONTRA = ISNULL(Z2_CC, D1_CC) 
        AND CNF.D_E_L_E_T_ = '' 
      GROUP BY 
        CNF_CONTRA
    ) AS CNFDVIG 
  FROM 
    SE2150 SE2 
    LEFT JOIN SZ2010 SZ2 ON Z2_CODEMP = '15' 
    AND Z2_E2PRF = E2_PREFIXO 
    AND Z2_E2NUM = E2_NUM 
    AND Z2_E2PARC = E2_PARCELA 
    AND Z2_E2TIPO = E2_TIPO 
    AND Z2_E2FORN = E2_FORNECE 
    AND Z2_E2LOJA = E2_LOJA 
    AND SZ2.D_E_L_E_T_ = '' 
    LEFT JOIN SD1150 SD1 ON D1_DOC = E2_NUM 
    AND D1_SERIE = E2_PREFIXO 
    AND D1_FORNECE = E2_FORNECE 
    AND D1_LOJA = E2_LOJA 
    AND SD1.D_E_L_E_T_ = '' 
    LEFT JOIN SB1150 SB1 ON B1_COD = D1_COD 
    AND SB1.D_E_L_E_T_ = '' 
    LEFT JOIN CTT010 CTT ON CTT_CUSTO = ISNULL(D1_CC, Z2_CC) 
    AND CTT.D_E_L_E_T_ = '' 
  WHERE 
    E2_VENCREA > '20220422' 
    AND SE2.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''
) 
SELECT 
  * 
FROM 
  AVISO 
WHERE 
  CNFDVIG <= '20220422' 
  OR SUBSTRING(D1_CC,1,1) = 'E' 
ORDER BY 
  E2_NUM

19/04/22 - BKGTR08 PARA AGENDAR

DROP TABLE powerbk.dbo.GLOSAS
SELECT 
  '01' AS EMPRESA,
  'BK' AS NOMEEMP,
  ISNULL(CND_CONTRA, C5_ESPECI1) AS CND_CONTRA, 
  CTT_DESC01, 
  C5_XXCOMPM, 
  C5_NUM, 
  C5_MDNUMED, 
  C5_MDPLANI, 
  F2_SERIE, 
  F2_DOC, 
  F2_EMISSAO, 
  F2_VALFAT, 
  CND_USUAR, 
  (
    CASE WHEN CND_NUMERO = '' THEN 'NOVA' ELSE 'ANTIGA' END
  ) AS FORMAMED, 
  ISNULL(CXN_VLPREV, CND_VLPREV) AS CXN_VLPREV, 
  ISNULL(CXN_VLBONI, CND_VLBONI) AS CXN_VLBONI, 
  ISNULL(CXN_VLMULT, CND_VLMULT) AS CXN_VLMULT, 
  STUFF (
    (
      SELECT 
        ';' + RTRIM(CNR_XTPJUS + '-' + ZR_DESCR) 
      FROM 
        CNR010 CNR 
        INNER JOIN SZR010 SZR ON ZR_TIPO = CNR_XTPJUS 
      WHERE 
        C5_MDNUMED = CNR.CNR_NUMMED 
        AND (
          CASE WHEN CND_NUMERO = '' THEN CXN_NUMPLA ELSE '' END
        ) = CNR_CODPLA 
        AND CNR_FILIAL = '01' 
        AND CNR.D_E_L_E_T_ = ' ' 
        AND CNR_TIPO = '1' 
      ORDER BY 
        ';' + RTRIM(CNR_XTPJUS + '-' + ZR_DESCR) FOR XML PATH (''), 
        TYPE
    ).value('.', 'varchar(100)'), 
    1, 
    1, 
    ''
  ) AS CNRTPMUL, 
  STUFF (
    (
      SELECT 
        ';' + RTRIM(CNR_DESCRI) 
      FROM 
        CNR010 CNR 
      WHERE 
        C5_MDNUMED = CNR.CNR_NUMMED 
        AND (
          CASE WHEN CND_NUMERO = '' THEN CXN_NUMPLA ELSE '' END
        ) = CNR_CODPLA 
        AND CNR_FILIAL = '01' 
        AND CNR.D_E_L_E_T_ = ' ' 
        AND CNR_TIPO = '1' 
      ORDER BY 
        ';' + RTRIM(CNR_DESCRI) FOR XML PATH (''), 
        TYPE
    ).value('.', 'varchar(100)'), 
    1, 
    1, 
    ''
  ) AS CNRDESCMUL, 
  STUFF (
    (
      SELECT 
        ';' + RTRIM(CNR_XTPJUS + '-' + ZR_DESCR) 
      FROM 
        CNR010 CNR 
        INNER JOIN SZR010 SZR ON ZR_TIPO = CNR_XTPJUS 
      WHERE 
        C5_MDNUMED = CNR.CNR_NUMMED 
        AND (
          CASE WHEN CND_NUMERO = '' THEN CXN_NUMPLA ELSE '' END
        ) = CNR_CODPLA 
        AND CNR_FILIAL = '01' 
        AND CNR.D_E_L_E_T_ = ' ' 
        AND CNR_TIPO = '2' 
      ORDER BY 
        ';' + RTRIM(CNR_XTPJUS + '-' + ZR_DESCR) FOR XML PATH (''), 
        TYPE
    ).value('.', 'varchar(100)'), 
    1, 
    1, 
    ''
  ) AS CNRTPBON, 
  STUFF (
    (
      SELECT 
        ';' + RTRIM(CNR_DESCRI) 
      FROM 
        CNR010 CNR 
      WHERE 
        C5_MDNUMED = CNR.CNR_NUMMED 
        AND (
          CASE WHEN CND_NUMERO = '' THEN CXN_NUMPLA ELSE '' END
        ) = CNR_CODPLA 
        AND CNR_FILIAL = '01' 
        AND CNR.D_E_L_E_T_ = ' ' 
        AND CNR_TIPO = '2' 
      ORDER BY 
        ';' + RTRIM(CNR_DESCRI) FOR XML PATH (''), 
        TYPE
    ).value('.', 'varchar(100)'), 
    1, 
    1, 
    ''
  ) AS CNRDESCBON into powerbk.dbo.GLOSAS 
FROM 
  SF2010 SF2 
  LEFT JOIN SC5010 SC5 ON (
    C5_NOTA = F2_DOC 
    AND C5_SERIE = F2_SERIE 
    AND C5_FILIAL = F2_FILIAL 
    AND SC5.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''
  ) 
  LEFT JOIN CXN010 CXN ON (
    CXN_CONTRA = C5_MDCONTR 
    AND CXN_NUMMED = C5_MDNUMED 
    AND CXN_NUMPLA = C5_MDPLANI 
    AND CXN.CXN_CHECK = 'T' 
    AND CXN_FILIAL = '01' 
    AND CXN.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''
  ) 
  LEFT JOIN CND010 CND ON (
    CND_NUMMED = C5_MDNUMED 
    AND CND_FILIAL = '01' 
    AND CND.D_E_L_E_T_ = '' 
    AND CND.R_E_C_N_O_ = (
      SELECT 
        TOP 1 R_E_C_N_O_ 
      FROM 
        CND010 CND1 
      WHERE 
        CND1.CND_NUMMED = C5_MDNUMED 
        AND CND1.CND_FILIAL = '01' 
        AND CND1.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''
    )
  ) 
  LEFT JOIN CTT010 CTT ON (
    ISNULL(CND_CONTRA, C5_ESPECI1) = CTT_CUSTO 
    AND CTT_FILIAL = '01' 
    AND CTT.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''
  ) 
WHERE 
  --SUBSTRING(F2_EMISSAO,1,6) = '202204' AND
  SF2.D_E_L_E_T_ = '' 
UNION ALL 
SELECT 
  DISTINCT 
  '01' AS EMPRESA,
  'BK' AS NOMEEMP,
  CNF_CONTRA AS CND_CONTRA, 
  CTT_DESC01, 
  CNF_COMPET AS C5_XXCOMPM, 
  ' ' AS C5_NUM, 
  ' ' AS C5_MDNUMED, 
  CNF_NUMPLA AS C5_MDPLANI, 
  ' ' AS F2_SERIE, 
  'PREVISTO' AS F2_DOC, 
  ' ' AS F2_EMISSAO, 
  0 AS F2_VALFAT, 
  ' ' AS CND_USUAR, 
  ' ' AS FORMAMED, 
  CNF_VLPREV AS CXN_VLPREV, 
  0 AS CXN_VLBONI, 
  0 AS CXN_VLMULT, 
  ' ' AS CNRTPMUL, 
  ' ' AS CNRDESCMUL, 
  ' ' AS CNRTPBON, 
  ' ' AS CNRDESCBON 
FROM 
  CNF010 CNF 
  INNER JOIN CN9010 CN9 ON CN9_NUMERO = CNF_CONTRA 
  AND CN9_REVISA = CNF_REVISA 
  AND CN9_REVATU = ' ' 
  AND CN9_FILIAL = '01' 
  AND CN9.D_E_L_E_T_ = ' ' 
  LEFT JOIN CTT010 CTT ON CTT_CUSTO = CNF_CONTRA 
  AND CTT_FILIAL = '01' 
  AND CTT.D_E_L_E_T_ = ' ' 
WHERE 
  --CNF_COMPET = '03/2022' AND
  CNF_SALDO = CNF_VLPREV 
  AND CNF_FILIAL = '01' 
  AND CNF.D_E_L_E_T_ = ' ' 

UNION ALL
SELECT 
  '14' AS EMPRESA,
  'BALSA NOVA' AS NOMEEMP,
  ISNULL(CND_CONTRA, C5_ESPECI1) AS CND_CONTRA, 
  CTT_DESC01, 
  C5_XXCOMPM, 
  C5_NUM, 
  C5_MDNUMED, 
  C5_MDPLANI, 
  F2_SERIE, 
  F2_DOC, 
  F2_EMISSAO, 
  F2_VALFAT, 
  CND_USUAR, 
  (
    CASE WHEN CND_NUMERO = '' THEN 'NOVA' ELSE 'ANTIGA' END
  ) AS FORMAMED, 
  ISNULL(CXN_VLPREV, CND_VLPREV) AS CXN_VLPREV, 
  ISNULL(CXN_VLBONI, CND_VLBONI) AS CXN_VLBONI, 
  ISNULL(CXN_VLMULT, CND_VLMULT) AS CXN_VLMULT, 
  STUFF (
    (
      SELECT 
        ';' + RTRIM(CNR_XTPJUS + '-' + ZR_DESCR) 
      FROM 
        CNR140 CNR 
        INNER JOIN SZR010 SZR ON ZR_TIPO = CNR_XTPJUS 
      WHERE 
        C5_MDNUMED = CNR.CNR_NUMMED 
        AND (
          CASE WHEN CND_NUMERO = '' THEN CXN_NUMPLA ELSE '' END
        ) = CNR_CODPLA 
        AND CNR_FILIAL = '01' 
        AND CNR.D_E_L_E_T_ = ' ' 
        AND CNR_TIPO = '1' 
      ORDER BY 
        ';' + RTRIM(CNR_XTPJUS + '-' + ZR_DESCR) FOR XML PATH (''), 
        TYPE
    ).value('.', 'varchar(100)'), 
    1, 
    1, 
    ''
  ) AS CNRTPMUL, 
  STUFF (
    (
      SELECT 
        ';' + RTRIM(CNR_DESCRI) 
      FROM 
        CNR140 CNR 
      WHERE 
        C5_MDNUMED = CNR.CNR_NUMMED 
        AND (
          CASE WHEN CND_NUMERO = '' THEN CXN_NUMPLA ELSE '' END
        ) = CNR_CODPLA 
        AND CNR_FILIAL = '01' 
        AND CNR.D_E_L_E_T_ = ' ' 
        AND CNR_TIPO = '1' 
      ORDER BY 
        ';' + RTRIM(CNR_DESCRI) FOR XML PATH (''), 
        TYPE
    ).value('.', 'varchar(100)'), 
    1, 
    1, 
    ''
  ) AS CNRDESCMUL, 
  STUFF (
    (
      SELECT 
        ';' + RTRIM(CNR_XTPJUS + '-' + ZR_DESCR) 
      FROM 
        CNR140 CNR 
        INNER JOIN SZR010 SZR ON ZR_TIPO = CNR_XTPJUS 
      WHERE 
        C5_MDNUMED = CNR.CNR_NUMMED 
        AND (
          CASE WHEN CND_NUMERO = '' THEN CXN_NUMPLA ELSE '' END
        ) = CNR_CODPLA 
        AND CNR_FILIAL = '01' 
        AND CNR.D_E_L_E_T_ = ' ' 
        AND CNR_TIPO = '2' 
      ORDER BY 
        ';' + RTRIM(CNR_XTPJUS + '-' + ZR_DESCR) FOR XML PATH (''), 
        TYPE
    ).value('.', 'varchar(100)'), 
    1, 
    1, 
    ''
  ) AS CNRTPBON, 
  STUFF (
    (
      SELECT 
        ';' + RTRIM(CNR_DESCRI) 
      FROM 
        CNR140 CNR 
      WHERE 
        C5_MDNUMED = CNR.CNR_NUMMED 
        AND (
          CASE WHEN CND_NUMERO = '' THEN CXN_NUMPLA ELSE '' END
        ) = CNR_CODPLA 
        AND CNR_FILIAL = '01' 
        AND CNR.D_E_L_E_T_ = ' ' 
        AND CNR_TIPO = '2' 
      ORDER BY 
        ';' + RTRIM(CNR_DESCRI) FOR XML PATH (''), 
        TYPE
    ).value('.', 'varchar(100)'), 
    1, 
    1, 
    ''
  ) AS CNRDESCBON  
FROM 
  SF2140 SF2 
  LEFT JOIN SC5140 SC5 ON (
    C5_NOTA = F2_DOC 
    AND C5_SERIE = F2_SERIE 
    AND C5_FILIAL = F2_FILIAL 
    AND SC5.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''
  ) 
  LEFT JOIN CXN140 CXN ON (
    CXN_CONTRA = C5_MDCONTR 
    AND CXN_NUMMED = C5_MDNUMED 
    AND CXN_NUMPLA = C5_MDPLANI 
    AND CXN.CXN_CHECK = 'T' 
    AND CXN_FILIAL = '01' 
    AND CXN.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''
  ) 
  LEFT JOIN CND140 CND ON (
    CND_NUMMED = C5_MDNUMED 
    AND CND_FILIAL = '01' 
    AND CND.D_E_L_E_T_ = '' 
    AND CND.R_E_C_N_O_ = (
      SELECT 
        TOP 1 R_E_C_N_O_ 
      FROM 
        CND140 CND1 
      WHERE 
        CND1.CND_NUMMED = C5_MDNUMED 
        AND CND1.CND_FILIAL = '01' 
        AND CND1.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''
    )
  ) 
  LEFT JOIN CTT140 CTT ON (
    ISNULL(CND_CONTRA, C5_ESPECI1) = CTT_CUSTO 
    AND CTT_FILIAL = '01' 
    AND CTT.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''
  ) 
WHERE 
  --SUBSTRING(F2_EMISSAO,1,6) = '202204' AND
  SF2.D_E_L_E_T_ = '' 
UNION ALL 
SELECT 
  DISTINCT 
  '14' AS EMPRESA,
  'BALSA NOVA' AS NOMEEMP,
  CNF_CONTRA AS CND_CONTRA, 
  CTT_DESC01, 
  CNF_COMPET AS C5_XXCOMPM, 
  ' ' AS C5_NUM, 
  ' ' AS C5_MDNUMED, 
  CNF_NUMPLA AS C5_MDPLANI, 
  ' ' AS F2_SERIE, 
  'PREVISTO' AS F2_DOC, 
  ' ' AS F2_EMISSAO, 
  0 AS F2_VALFAT, 
  ' ' AS CND_USUAR, 
  ' ' AS FORMAMED, 
  CNF_VLPREV AS CXN_VLPREV, 
  0 AS CXN_VLBONI, 
  0 AS CXN_VLMULT, 
  ' ' AS CNRTPMUL, 
  ' ' AS CNRDESCMUL, 
  ' ' AS CNRTPBON, 
  ' ' AS CNRDESCBON 
FROM 
  CNF140 CNF 
  INNER JOIN CN9140 CN9 ON CN9_NUMERO = CNF_CONTRA 
  AND CN9_REVISA = CNF_REVISA 
  AND CN9_REVATU = ' ' 
  AND CN9_FILIAL = '01' 
  AND CN9.D_E_L_E_T_ = ' ' 
  LEFT JOIN CTT140 CTT ON CTT_CUSTO = CNF_CONTRA 
  AND CTT_FILIAL = '01' 
  AND CTT.D_E_L_E_T_ = ' ' 
WHERE 
  --CNF_COMPET = '03/2022' AND
  CNF_SALDO = CNF_VLPREV 
  AND CNF_FILIAL = '01' 
  AND CNF.D_E_L_E_T_ = ' ' 
   
  ORDER BY
    EMPRESA,F2_DOC

UPDATE CNR010 SET CNR_XTPJUS = '01' WHERE CNR_DESCRI LIKE '%POSTO%' AND CNR_XTPJUS = ' ' AND CNR_TIPO = '1'

UPDATE CNR010 SET CNR_XTPJUS = '02' WHERE CNR_DESCRI LIKE '%POSTOS NAO IMPLANTADOS PELO CLIENTE%' AND CNR_XTPJUS = ' ' 
UPDATE CNR010 SET CNR_XTPJUS = '02' WHERE CNR_DESCRI LIKE '%POSTOS NAO IMPLANTADOS CLIENTE%' AND CNR_XTPJUS = ' ' 
UPDATE CNR010 SET CNR_XTPJUS = '02' WHERE CNR_DESCRI LIKE '%POSTOS NAO IMPLANTADOS  PELO CLIENTE%' AND CNR_XTPJUS = ' '

25/02/22 - Alterar data de vencimento de Pgtos

SELECT * FROM SZ2010 WHERE Z2_DATAPGT = '20220301'

UPDATE SZ2010 SET Z2_DATAPGT = '20220302' WHERE Z2_DATAPGT = '20220301'
UPDATE SZ2010 SET Z2_DATAPGT = '20220302' WHERE Z2_DATAPGT = '20220228'

SELECT E2_VENCTO,E2_VENCREA FROM SE2010 WHERE E2_VENCREA = '20220301' AND D_E_L_E_T_ = ''
SELECT E2_VENCTO,E2_VENCREA,E2_BAIXA FROM SE2010 WHERE E2_VENCREA = '20220228' AND D_E_L_E_T_ = ''AND E2_BAIXA = ''

UPDATE SE2010 SET E2_VENCTO = '20220302',E2_VENCREA = '20220302' WHERE E2_VENCREA = '20220228' AND D_E_L_E_T_ = '' AND E2_BAIXA = ''
UPDATE SE2020 SET E2_VENCTO = '20220302',E2_VENCREA = '20220302' WHERE E2_VENCREA = '20220228' AND D_E_L_E_T_ = '' AND E2_BAIXA = ''
UPDATE SE2120 SET E2_VENCTO = '20220302',E2_VENCREA = '20220302' WHERE E2_VENCREA = '20220228' AND D_E_L_E_T_ = '' AND E2_BAIXA = ''
UPDATE SE2140 SET E2_VENCTO = '20220302',E2_VENCREA = '20220302' WHERE E2_VENCREA = '20220228' AND D_E_L_E_T_ = '' AND E2_BAIXA = ''
UPDATE SE2150 SET E2_VENCTO = '20220302',E2_VENCREA = '20220302' WHERE E2_VENCREA = '20220228' AND D_E_L_E_T_ = '' AND E2_BAIXA = ''

UPDATE SE2010 SET E2_VENCTO = '20220302',E2_VENCREA = '20220302' WHERE E2_VENCREA = '20220301' AND D_E_L_E_T_ = '' AND E2_BAIXA = ''
UPDATE SE2020 SET E2_VENCTO = '20220302',E2_VENCREA = '20220302' WHERE E2_VENCREA = '20220301' AND D_E_L_E_T_ = '' AND E2_BAIXA = ''

AND D_E_L_E_T_= '' AND E1_TIPO = 'NF'
AND E1_BAIXA <> ''

AND D_E_L_E_T_= '' AND E1_TIPO = 'NF'
AND E1_BAIXA <> ''

11/02/22 - Teste Mapa de INSS Retido:


WITH gct07 as (
 SELECT DISTINCT
   F2_FILIAL,
   D2_CLIENTE AS XX_CLIENTE,
   D2_LOJA XX_LOJA,
   C6_PRODUTO AS XX_PROD,
   B1_DESC,
   B1_CODISS,
   B1_ALIQISS,
   CNF_CONTRA,
   CNF_REVISA,
   CNF_COMPET,
   (CASE WHEN CN9_SITUAC = '05' THEN CNF_VLPREV ELSE CNF_VLREAL END) AS CNF_VLPREV,
   (CASE WHEN CN9_SITUAC = '05' THEN CNF_SALDO  ELSE 0 END) AS CNF_SALDO,
   CTT_DESC01,
   CNA_NUMERO,
   CNA_XXMUN,
   CNA_FLREAJ,
   CND_NUMMED,
   ISNULL(CXN_PARCEL,CND_PARCEL) AS CXN_PARCEL,
   CND_XXRM,
   C6_NUM,
   (SELECT SUM(CNR_VALOR) FROM CNR010 CNR WHERE CNR_NUMMED = CNE_NUMMED AND CNR_CODPLA = ISNULL(CXN_NUMPLA,'      ')
   	AND CNR_FILIAL = CND_FILIAL AND CNR.D_E_L_E_T_ = ' ' AND CNR_TIPO = '2') AS XX_BONIF,
   (SELECT SUM(CNR_VALOR) FROM CNR010 CNR WHERE CNR_NUMMED = CNE_NUMMED AND CNR_CODPLA = ISNULL(CXN_NUMPLA,'      ')
   	AND  CNR_FILIAL = CND_FILIAL AND CNR.D_E_L_E_T_ = ' ' AND CNR_TIPO = '1') AS XX_MULTA,
   F2_SERIE,
   F2_DOC,
   F2_EMISSAO,
   F2_VALFAT,
   F2_VALIRRF,
   F2_VALINSS,
   F2_VALPIS,
   F2_VALCOFI,
   F2_VALCSLL,
   F2_RECISS,
   F2_VALISS,
   F2_VLCPM,
   F2_XXVRETC,
   (SELECT TOP 1 E1_VENCTO FROM SE1010 SE1 WHERE E1_PREFIXO = F2_SERIE AND E1_NUM = F2_DOC
   	AND SE1.D_E_L_E_T_ = ' ' AND E1_FILIAL = '01') AS XX_VENCTO, 
   (SELECT TOP 1 E1_VENCORI FROM SE1010 SE1 WHERE E1_PREFIXO = F2_SERIE AND E1_NUM = F2_DOC
   	AND SE1.D_E_L_E_T_ = ' ' AND E1_FILIAL = '01') AS XX_VENCORI, 
   (SELECT TOP 1 E1_BAIXA FROM SE1010 SE1 WHERE E1_PREFIXO = F2_SERIE AND E1_NUM = F2_DOC
   	AND SE1.D_E_L_E_T_ = ' ' AND E1_FILIAL = '01') AS XX_BAIXA, 
   (SELECT SUM(E5_VALOR) FROM SE5010 SE5 WHERE E5_PREFIXO = F2_SERIE AND E5_NUMERO = F2_DOC  AND E5_TIPO = 'NF' AND  E5_CLIFOR = F2_CLIENTE AND E5_LOJA = F2_LOJA AND E5_TIPODOC = 'DC' AND E5_RECPAG = 'R' AND E5_SITUACA <> 'C' 
   	AND SE5.D_E_L_E_T_ = ' ' AND E5_FILIAL = '01') AS XX_E5DESC, 
   (SELECT SUM(E5_VALOR) FROM SE5010 SE5 WHERE E5_PREFIXO = F2_SERIE AND E5_NUMERO = F2_DOC  AND E5_TIPO = 'NF' AND  E5_CLIFOR = F2_CLIENTE AND E5_LOJA = F2_LOJA AND E5_TIPODOC IN ('MT','JR','CM') AND E5_RECPAG = 'R' AND E5_SITUACA <> 'C' 
   	AND SE5.D_E_L_E_T_ = ' ' AND E5_FILIAL = '01') AS XX_E5MULTA
 FROM CNE010 CNE
 INNER JOIN CND010 CND
 	ON (CND_NUMMED = CNE_NUMMED AND CND_CONTRA = CNE_CONTRA AND CND_REVISA = CNE_REVISA
 		AND CND.CND_FILIAL = CNE.CNE_FILIAL AND CND.D_E_L_E_T_='')
 LEFT JOIN CXN010 CXN
 	ON (CXN_CONTRA = CNE_CONTRA AND CXN_REVISA = CNE_REVISA AND CXN_NUMMED = CNE_NUMMED AND CXN_NUMPLA = CNE_NUMERO AND CXN.CXN_CHECK = 'T'
 		AND CXN.CXN_FILIAL = CNE.CNE_FILIAL AND CXN.D_E_L_E_T_='')
 INNER JOIN CTT010 CTT
 	ON (CTT_CUSTO = CNE_CONTRA
 		AND CTT_FILIAL = '01' AND CTT.D_E_L_E_T_='')
 INNER JOIN CN9010 CN9
 	ON (CN9_FILCTR = CND_FILCTR AND CN9_NUMERO = CNE_CONTRA AND CN9_REVISA = CNE_REVISA
 	 	AND CN9.D_E_L_E_T_='')
 INNER JOIN CNF010 CNF
 	ON (CNE_CONTRA = CNF_CONTRA AND CND_COMPET = CNF_COMPET AND CNE_NUMERO = CNF_NUMPLA AND CNE_REVISA = CNF_REVISA
 	    AND CNF_PARCEL = ISNULL(CXN_PARCEL,CND_PARCEL)
 	 	AND CNF_FILIAL = '01' AND CNF.D_E_L_E_T_='')
 INNER JOIN CNA010 CNA
 	ON (CNA_CONTRA = CNE_CONTRA AND CNA_CRONOG = CNF_NUMERO AND CNA_REVISA = CNF_REVISA AND CNA_NUMERO = CNF_NUMPLA
 		AND CNA_FILIAL = CND_FILCTR AND CNA.D_E_L_E_T_='')
 INNER JOIN SC6010 SC6
 	ON (C6_NUM = CNE_PEDIDO AND C6_ITEMED = CNE_ITEM
 		AND SC6.C6_FILIAL = CNE.CNE_FILIAL AND SC6.D_E_L_E_T_='')
 INNER JOIN SD2010 SD2
 	ON (D2_PEDIDO = C6_NUM AND D2_ITEMPV = C6_ITEM
 		AND SD2.D2_FILIAL = SC6.C6_FILIAL AND SD2.D_E_L_E_T_='')
 INNER JOIN SF2010 SF2
 	ON (C6_SERIE = F2_SERIE AND C6_NOTA = F2_DOC AND F2_CLIENTE = C6_CLI AND F2_LOJA = C6_LOJA AND F2_TIPO = 'N' AND F2_FORMUL = ' '
 		AND SF2.F2_FILIAL = SC6.C6_FILIAL AND SF2.D_E_L_E_T_='')
 INNER JOIN SB1010 SB1
 	ON (C6_PRODUTO = B1_COD
 		AND B1_FILIAL = '01' AND SB1.D_E_L_E_T_='')
 WHERE CNE.D_E_L_E_T_ = ' '
 	AND CN9.CN9_REVATU = '   '
 AND SUBSTRING(F2_EMISSAO,1,6) >= '202101'
 UNION ALL 
 SELECT DISTINCT
   F2_FILIAL,
   F2_CLIENTE AS XX_CLIENTE,
   F2_LOJA AS XX_LOJA,
   D2_COD AS XX_PROD,
   B1_DESC,
   B1_CODISS,
   B1_ALIQISS,
   CASE WHEN (C5_ESPECI1 = ' ' OR C5_ESPECI1 IS NULL) THEN 'XXXXXXXXXX' ELSE C5_ESPECI1 END AS CNF_CONTRA,
   ' ' AS CNF_REVISA,
   SUBSTRING(C5_XXCOMPT,1,2)+'/'+SUBSTRING(C5_XXCOMPT,3,4) AS CNF_COMPET,
   0,
   0,
   A1_NOME,
   ' ',
   CASE WHEN (C5_DESCMUN = ' ' OR C5_DESCMUN IS NULL) THEN SA1.A1_MUN ELSE C5_DESCMUN END AS CNA_XXMUN, 
   ' ',
   ' ',
   ' ',
   C5_XXRM,
   C5_NUM AS C6_NUM,
   0,
   0,
   F2_SERIE,
   F2_DOC,
   F2_EMISSAO,
   F2_VALFAT,
   F2_VALIRRF,
   F2_VALINSS,
   F2_VALPIS,
   F2_VALCOFI,
   F2_VALCSLL,
   F2_RECISS,
   F2_VALISS,
   F2_VLCPM,
   F2_XXVRETC,
   (SELECT TOP 1 E1_VENCTO FROM SE1010 SE1 WHERE E1_PREFIXO = F2_SERIE AND E1_NUM = F2_DOC
       AND SE1.D_E_L_E_T_ = ' ' AND E1_FILIAL = '01') AS XX_VENCTO, 
   (SELECT TOP 1 E1_VENCORI FROM SE1010 SE1 WHERE E1_PREFIXO = F2_SERIE AND E1_NUM = F2_DOC
       AND SE1.D_E_L_E_T_ = ' ' AND E1_FILIAL = '01') AS XX_VENCORI, 
   (SELECT TOP 1 E1_BAIXA FROM SE1010 SE1 WHERE E1_PREFIXO = F2_SERIE AND E1_NUM = F2_DOC
       AND SE1.D_E_L_E_T_ = ' ' AND E1_FILIAL = '01') AS XX_BAIXA, 
   (SELECT SUM(E5_VALOR) FROM SE5010 SE5 WHERE E5_PREFIXO = F2_SERIE AND E5_NUMERO = F2_DOC  AND E5_TIPO = 'NF' AND  E5_CLIFOR = F2_CLIENTE AND E5_LOJA = F2_LOJA AND E5_TIPODOC = 'DC' AND E5_RECPAG = 'R' AND E5_SITUACA <> 'C' 
       AND SE5.D_E_L_E_T_ = ' ' AND E5_FILIAL = '01') AS XX_E5DESC, 
   (SELECT SUM(E5_VALOR) FROM SE5010 SE5 WHERE E5_PREFIXO = F2_SERIE AND E5_NUMERO = F2_DOC  AND E5_TIPO = 'NF' AND  E5_CLIFOR = F2_CLIENTE AND E5_LOJA = F2_LOJA AND E5_TIPODOC IN ('MT','JR','CM') AND E5_RECPAG = 'R' AND E5_SITUACA <> 'C' 
       AND SE5.D_E_L_E_T_ = ' ' AND E5_FILIAL = '01') AS XX_E5MULTA 
 FROM SF2010 SF2
 LEFT JOIN SA1010 SA1 ON F2_CLIENTE = A1_COD AND F2_LOJA = A1_LOJA
      AND  A1_FILIAL = '  ' AND  SA1.D_E_L_E_T_ = ' '
 LEFT JOIN SD2010 SD2 ON D2_DOC = F2_DOC AND D2_SERIE = F2_SERIE AND D2_CLIENTE = F2_CLIENTE AND D2_LOJA = F2_LOJA
      AND  D2_FILIAL = '01' AND  SD2.D_E_L_E_T_ = ' '
 LEFT JOIN SC5010 SC5 ON C5_NOTA = F2_DOC AND C5_SERIE = F2_SERIE 
      AND  C5_FILIAL = F2_FILIAL AND SC5.D_E_L_E_T_ = ' '
 LEFT JOIN SB1010 SB1 ON D2_COD = B1_COD
      AND  B1_FILIAL = '01' AND SB1.D_E_L_E_T_ = ' '
 WHERE (C5_MDCONTR = ' ' OR C5_MDCONTR IS NULL)
      AND C5_NUM IS NOT NULL
  AND SUBSTRING(F2_EMISSAO,1,6) >= '202101'       AND SF2.D_E_L_E_T_ = ' '
 --ORDER BY CNF_CONTRA,CNF_REVISA,CNF_COMPET,F2_SERIE,F2_DOC
)
SELECT SUBSTRING(F2_EMISSAO,1,6),SUM(F2_VALFAT),COUNT(*) FROM gct07 GROUP BY SUBSTRING(F2_EMISSAO,1,6)
ORDER BY  SUBSTRING(F2_EMISSAO,1,6)

(Nenhum nome de coluna)	(Nenhum nome de coluna)	(Nenhum nome de coluna)

Query alterada Inner para Left:

 
WITH gct07 as (
 SELECT DISTINCT
   F2_FILIAL,
   D2_CLIENTE AS XX_CLIENTE,
   D2_LOJA XX_LOJA,
   C6_PRODUTO AS XX_PROD,
   B1_DESC,
   B1_CODISS,
   B1_ALIQISS,
   CNF_CONTRA,
   CNF_REVISA,
   CNF_COMPET,
   (CASE WHEN CN9_SITUAC = '05' THEN CNF_VLPREV ELSE CNF_VLREAL END) AS CNF_VLPREV,
   (CASE WHEN CN9_SITUAC = '05' THEN CNF_SALDO  ELSE 0 END) AS CNF_SALDO,
   CTT_DESC01,
   CNA_NUMERO,
   CNA_XXMUN,
   CNA_FLREAJ,
   CND_NUMMED,
   ISNULL(CXN_PARCEL,CND_PARCEL) AS CXN_PARCEL,
   CND_XXRM,
   C6_NUM,
   (SELECT SUM(CNR_VALOR) FROM CNR010 CNR WHERE CNR_NUMMED = CNE_NUMMED AND CNR_CODPLA = ISNULL(CXN_NUMPLA,'      ')
   	AND CNR_FILIAL = CND_FILIAL AND CNR.D_E_L_E_T_ = ' ' AND CNR_TIPO = '2') AS XX_BONIF,
   (SELECT SUM(CNR_VALOR) FROM CNR010 CNR WHERE CNR_NUMMED = CNE_NUMMED AND CNR_CODPLA = ISNULL(CXN_NUMPLA,'      ')
   	AND  CNR_FILIAL = CND_FILIAL AND CNR.D_E_L_E_T_ = ' ' AND CNR_TIPO = '1') AS XX_MULTA,
   F2_SERIE,
   F2_DOC,
   F2_EMISSAO,
   F2_VALFAT,
   F2_VALIRRF,
   F2_VALINSS,
   F2_VALPIS,
   F2_VALCOFI,
   F2_VALCSLL,
   F2_RECISS,
   F2_VALISS,
   F2_VLCPM,
   F2_XXVRETC,
   (SELECT TOP 1 E1_VENCTO FROM SE1010 SE1 WHERE E1_PREFIXO = F2_SERIE AND E1_NUM = F2_DOC
   	AND SE1.D_E_L_E_T_ = ' ' AND E1_FILIAL = '01') AS XX_VENCTO, 
   (SELECT TOP 1 E1_VENCORI FROM SE1010 SE1 WHERE E1_PREFIXO = F2_SERIE AND E1_NUM = F2_DOC
   	AND SE1.D_E_L_E_T_ = ' ' AND E1_FILIAL = '01') AS XX_VENCORI, 
   (SELECT TOP 1 E1_BAIXA FROM SE1010 SE1 WHERE E1_PREFIXO = F2_SERIE AND E1_NUM = F2_DOC
   	AND SE1.D_E_L_E_T_ = ' ' AND E1_FILIAL = '01') AS XX_BAIXA, 
   (SELECT SUM(E5_VALOR) FROM SE5010 SE5 WHERE E5_PREFIXO = F2_SERIE AND E5_NUMERO = F2_DOC  AND E5_TIPO = 'NF' AND  E5_CLIFOR = F2_CLIENTE AND E5_LOJA = F2_LOJA AND E5_TIPODOC = 'DC' AND E5_RECPAG = 'R' AND E5_SITUACA <> 'C' 
   	AND SE5.D_E_L_E_T_ = ' ' AND E5_FILIAL = '01') AS XX_E5DESC, 
   (SELECT SUM(E5_VALOR) FROM SE5010 SE5 WHERE E5_PREFIXO = F2_SERIE AND E5_NUMERO = F2_DOC  AND E5_TIPO = 'NF' AND  E5_CLIFOR = F2_CLIENTE AND E5_LOJA = F2_LOJA AND E5_TIPODOC IN ('MT','JR','CM') AND E5_RECPAG = 'R' AND E5_SITUACA <> 'C' 
   	AND SE5.D_E_L_E_T_ = ' ' AND E5_FILIAL = '01') AS XX_E5MULTA
 FROM CNE010 CNE
 INNER JOIN CND010 CND
 	ON (CND_NUMMED = CNE_NUMMED AND CND_CONTRA = CNE_CONTRA AND CND_REVISA = CNE_REVISA
 		AND CND.CND_FILIAL = CNE.CNE_FILIAL AND CND.D_E_L_E_T_='')
 LEFT JOIN CXN010 CXN
 	ON (CXN_CONTRA = CNE_CONTRA AND CXN_REVISA = CNE_REVISA AND CXN_NUMMED = CNE_NUMMED AND CXN_NUMPLA = CNE_NUMERO AND CXN.CXN_CHECK = 'T'
 		AND CXN.CXN_FILIAL = CNE.CNE_FILIAL AND CXN.D_E_L_E_T_='')
 LEFT JOIN CTT010 CTT
 	ON (CTT_CUSTO = CNE_CONTRA
 		AND CTT_FILIAL = '01' AND CTT.D_E_L_E_T_='')
 LEFT JOIN CN9010 CN9
 	ON (CN9_FILCTR = CND_FILCTR AND CN9_NUMERO = CNE_CONTRA AND CN9_REVISA = CNE_REVISA
 	 	AND CN9.D_E_L_E_T_='')
 LEFT JOIN CNF010 CNF
 	ON (CNE_CONTRA = CNF_CONTRA AND CND_COMPET = CNF_COMPET AND CNE_NUMERO = CNF_NUMPLA AND CNE_REVISA = CNF_REVISA
 	    AND CNF_PARCEL = ISNULL(CXN_PARCEL,CND_PARCEL)
 	 	AND CNF_FILIAL = '01' AND CNF.D_E_L_E_T_='')
 LEFT JOIN CNA010 CNA
 	ON (CNA_CONTRA = CNE_CONTRA AND CNA_CRONOG = CNF_NUMERO AND CNA_REVISA = CNF_REVISA AND CNA_NUMERO = CNF_NUMPLA
 		AND CNA_FILIAL = CND_FILCTR AND CNA.D_E_L_E_T_='')
 LEFT JOIN SC6010 SC6
 	ON (C6_NUM = CNE_PEDIDO AND C6_ITEMED = CNE_ITEM
 		AND SC6.C6_FILIAL = CNE.CNE_FILIAL AND SC6.D_E_L_E_T_='')
 LEFT JOIN SD2010 SD2
 	ON (D2_PEDIDO = C6_NUM AND D2_ITEMPV = C6_ITEM
 		AND SD2.D2_FILIAL = SC6.C6_FILIAL AND SD2.D_E_L_E_T_='')
 LEFT JOIN SF2010 SF2
 	ON (C6_SERIE = F2_SERIE AND C6_NOTA = F2_DOC AND F2_CLIENTE = C6_CLI AND F2_LOJA = C6_LOJA AND F2_TIPO = 'N' AND F2_FORMUL = ' '
 		AND SF2.F2_FILIAL = SC6.C6_FILIAL AND SF2.D_E_L_E_T_='')
 LEFT JOIN SB1010 SB1
 	ON (C6_PRODUTO = B1_COD
 		AND B1_FILIAL = '01' AND SB1.D_E_L_E_T_='')
 WHERE CNE.D_E_L_E_T_ = ' '
 	AND CN9.CN9_REVATU = '   '
 AND SUBSTRING(F2_EMISSAO,1,6) >= '202101'
 UNION ALL 
 SELECT DISTINCT
   F2_FILIAL,
   F2_CLIENTE AS XX_CLIENTE,
   F2_LOJA AS XX_LOJA,
   D2_COD AS XX_PROD,
   B1_DESC,
   B1_CODISS,
   B1_ALIQISS,
   CASE WHEN (C5_ESPECI1 = ' ' OR C5_ESPECI1 IS NULL) THEN 'XXXXXXXXXX' ELSE C5_ESPECI1 END AS CNF_CONTRA,
   ' ' AS CNF_REVISA,
   SUBSTRING(C5_XXCOMPT,1,2)+'/'+SUBSTRING(C5_XXCOMPT,3,4) AS CNF_COMPET,
   0,
   0,
   A1_NOME,
   ' ',
   CASE WHEN (C5_DESCMUN = ' ' OR C5_DESCMUN IS NULL) THEN SA1.A1_MUN ELSE C5_DESCMUN END AS CNA_XXMUN, 
   ' ',
   ' ',
   ' ',
   C5_XXRM,
   C5_NUM AS C6_NUM,
   0,
   0,
   F2_SERIE,
   F2_DOC,
   F2_EMISSAO,
   F2_VALFAT,
   F2_VALIRRF,
   F2_VALINSS,
   F2_VALPIS,
   F2_VALCOFI,
   F2_VALCSLL,
   F2_RECISS,
   F2_VALISS,
   F2_VLCPM,
   F2_XXVRETC,
   (SELECT TOP 1 E1_VENCTO FROM SE1010 SE1 WHERE E1_PREFIXO = F2_SERIE AND E1_NUM = F2_DOC
       AND SE1.D_E_L_E_T_ = ' ' AND E1_FILIAL = '01') AS XX_VENCTO, 
   (SELECT TOP 1 E1_VENCORI FROM SE1010 SE1 WHERE E1_PREFIXO = F2_SERIE AND E1_NUM = F2_DOC
       AND SE1.D_E_L_E_T_ = ' ' AND E1_FILIAL = '01') AS XX_VENCORI, 
   (SELECT TOP 1 E1_BAIXA FROM SE1010 SE1 WHERE E1_PREFIXO = F2_SERIE AND E1_NUM = F2_DOC
       AND SE1.D_E_L_E_T_ = ' ' AND E1_FILIAL = '01') AS XX_BAIXA, 
   (SELECT SUM(E5_VALOR) FROM SE5010 SE5 WHERE E5_PREFIXO = F2_SERIE AND E5_NUMERO = F2_DOC  AND E5_TIPO = 'NF' AND  E5_CLIFOR = F2_CLIENTE AND E5_LOJA = F2_LOJA AND E5_TIPODOC = 'DC' AND E5_RECPAG = 'R' AND E5_SITUACA <> 'C' 
       AND SE5.D_E_L_E_T_ = ' ' AND E5_FILIAL = '01') AS XX_E5DESC, 
   (SELECT SUM(E5_VALOR) FROM SE5010 SE5 WHERE E5_PREFIXO = F2_SERIE AND E5_NUMERO = F2_DOC  AND E5_TIPO = 'NF' AND  E5_CLIFOR = F2_CLIENTE AND E5_LOJA = F2_LOJA AND E5_TIPODOC IN ('MT','JR','CM') AND E5_RECPAG = 'R' AND E5_SITUACA <> 'C' 
       AND SE5.D_E_L_E_T_ = ' ' AND E5_FILIAL = '01') AS XX_E5MULTA 
 FROM SF2010 SF2
 LEFT JOIN SA1010 SA1 ON F2_CLIENTE = A1_COD AND F2_LOJA = A1_LOJA
      AND  A1_FILIAL = '  ' AND  SA1.D_E_L_E_T_ = ' '
 LEFT JOIN SD2010 SD2 ON D2_DOC = F2_DOC AND D2_SERIE = F2_SERIE AND D2_CLIENTE = F2_CLIENTE AND D2_LOJA = F2_LOJA
      AND  D2_FILIAL = '01' AND  SD2.D_E_L_E_T_ = ' '
 LEFT JOIN SC5010 SC5 ON C5_NOTA = F2_DOC AND C5_SERIE = F2_SERIE 
      AND  C5_FILIAL = F2_FILIAL AND SC5.D_E_L_E_T_ = ' '
 LEFT JOIN SB1010 SB1 ON D2_COD = B1_COD
      AND  B1_FILIAL = '01' AND SB1.D_E_L_E_T_ = ' '
 WHERE (C5_MDCONTR = ' ' OR C5_MDCONTR IS NULL)
      AND C5_NUM IS NOT NULL
  AND SUBSTRING(F2_EMISSAO,1,6) >= '202101'       AND SF2.D_E_L_E_T_ = ' '
 --ORDER BY CNF_CONTRA,CNF_REVISA,CNF_COMPET,F2_SERIE,F2_DOC
)
SELECT SUBSTRING(F2_EMISSAO,1,6),SUM(F2_VALFAT),COUNT(*) FROM gct07 GROUP BY SUBSTRING(F2_EMISSAO,1,6)
ORDER BY  SUBSTRING(F2_EMISSAO,1,6)

07/02/22 - CONTA VINCULADA

SELECT F2_CLIENTE,F2_LOJA,A1_NOME FROM SF2010 
LEFT JOIN SA1010 ON A1_COD = F2_CLIENTE AND A1_LOJA = F2_LOJA AND SA1010.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''
WHERE  SF2010.D_E_L_E_T_ = '' AND F2_XXVCVIN > 0 
GROUP BY F2_CLIENTE,F2_LOJA,A1_NOME
ORDER BY F2_CLIENTE,F2_LOJA,A1_NOME

SELECT F2_CLIENTE,F2_LOJA,A1_NOME FROM SF2020 
LEFT JOIN SA1020 ON A1_COD = F2_CLIENTE AND A1_LOJA = F2_LOJA AND SA1020.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''
WHERE  SF2020.D_E_L_E_T_ = '' AND F2_XXVCVIN > 0 
GROUP BY F2_CLIENTE,F2_LOJA,A1_NOME
ORDER BY F2_CLIENTE,F2_LOJA,A1_NOME

SELECT F2_CLIENTE,F2_LOJA,A1_NOME FROM SF2140 
LEFT JOIN SA1140 ON A1_COD = F2_CLIENTE AND A1_LOJA = F2_LOJA AND SA1140.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''
WHERE  SF2140.D_E_L_E_T_ = '' AND F2_XXVCVIN > 0 
GROUP BY F2_CLIENTE,F2_LOJA,A1_NOME
ORDER BY F2_CLIENTE,F2_LOJA,A1_NOME

25/11/2021 - Relao de pagamentos integrao rubi da Balsa Nova. Somente as datas: 04/06, 06/07, 06/08, 06/09, 06/10 e 05/11

SELECT Z2_CODEMP,Z2_TIPO,'="'+Z2_PRONT+'"',Z2_NOME,CONVERT(VARCHAR,CONVERT(DATE,Z2_DATAPGT),103) AS DATAPGT,'="'+Z2_BANCO+'"' AS BANCO,SUBSTRING(Z2_DATAPGT,1,6) AS MES FROM SZ2010 WHERE 
(Z2_DATAPGT = '20210604' 
OR Z2_DATAPGT = '20210706'
OR Z2_DATAPGT = '20210806'
OR Z2_DATAPGT = '20210906'
OR Z2_DATAPGT = '20211006'
OR Z2_DATAPGT = '20211105')
AND D_E_L_E_T_ = '' 
AND Z2_STATUS = 'S'
AND Z2_CODEMP = '14'
GROUP BY Z2_CODEMP,Z2_TIPO,Z2_DATAPGT,Z2_PRONT,Z2_NOME,Z2_BANCO
ORDER BY Z2_CODEMP,Z2_TIPO,Z2_DATAPGT,Z2_PRONT,Z2_NOME,Z2_BANCO

==============================================================
16/11/2021 - Relao de pagamentos integrao rubi da Balsa Nova nos meses 01/02/03/04/07/08 de 2021

SELECT Z2_CODEMP,'="'+Z2_PRONT+'"',Z2_NOME,CONVERT(VARCHAR,CONVERT(DATE,Z2_DATAPGT),103) AS DATAPGT,'="'+Z2_BANCO+'"' AS BANCO,SUBSTRING(Z2_DATAPGT,1,6) AS MES FROM SZ2010 WHERE 
(SUBSTRING(Z2_DATAPGT,1,6) = '202101' 
OR SUBSTRING(Z2_DATAPGT,1,6) = '202102'
OR SUBSTRING(Z2_DATAPGT,1,6) = '202103'
OR SUBSTRING(Z2_DATAPGT,1,6) = '202104'
OR SUBSTRING(Z2_DATAPGT,1,6) = '202107'
OR SUBSTRING(Z2_DATAPGT,1,6) = '202108')
AND D_E_L_E_T_ = '' 
AND Z2_STATUS = 'S'
AND Z2_CODEMP = '14'
GROUP BY Z2_CODEMP,Z2_DATAPGT,Z2_PRONT,Z2_NOME,Z2_BANCO
ORDER BY Z2_CODEMP,Z2_DATAPGT,Z2_PRONT,Z2_NOME,Z2_BANCO

12/11/2021 - Relao de pagamentos integrao rubi da Balsa Nova nos meses 01/03/07 de 2021

SELECT Z2_CODEMP,'="'+Z2_PRONT+'"',Z2_NOME,CONVERT(VARCHAR,CONVERT(DATE,Z2_DATAPGT),103) AS DATAPGT,'="'+Z2_BANCO+'"' AS BANCO,SUBSTRING(Z2_DATAPGT,1,6) AS MES FROM SZ2010 WHERE 
(SUBSTRING(Z2_DATAPGT,1,6) = '202101' 
OR SUBSTRING(Z2_DATAPGT,1,6) = '202103'
OR SUBSTRING(Z2_DATAPGT,1,6) = '202107')
AND D_E_L_E_T_ = '' 
AND Z2_STATUS = 'S'
AND Z2_CODEMP = '14'
GROUP BY Z2_CODEMP,Z2_DATAPGT,Z2_PRONT,Z2_NOME,Z2_BANCO
ORDER BY Z2_CODEMP,Z2_DATAPGT,Z2_PRONT,Z2_NOME,Z2_BANCO

select B1_COD,B1_CODISS,B1_ALIQISS from SB1140  WHERE B1_CODISS <> ' '

SELECT C9_NFISCAL,C9_CODISS,C9_DATALIB,C9_PRODUTO,B1_COD,B1_CODISS FROM SC9140 SC9
LEFT JOIN SB1140 SB1 ON B1_COD = C9_PRODUTO AND SB1.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''
WHERE C9_NFISCAL = ' ' AND SC9.D_E_L_E_T_ =''

UPDATE SC9140 SET C9_CODISS = B1_CODISS FROM SC9140 SC9
LEFT JOIN SB1140 SB1 ON B1_COD = C9_PRODUTO AND SB1.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''
WHERE C9_NFISCAL = ' ' AND SC9.D_E_L_E_T_ =''

SELECT C6_NUM,C6_QTDENT,C6_CODISS,C6_ENTREG,C6_PRODUTO,B1_COD,B1_CODISS FROM SC6140 SC6
LEFT JOIN SB1140 SB1 ON B1_COD = C6_PRODUTO AND SB1.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''
WHERE C6_NOTA = ' ' AND SC6.D_E_L_E_T_ =''
ORDER BY C6_NUM

UPDATE SC6140 SET C6_CODISS = B1_CODISS FROM SC6140 SC6
LEFT JOIN SB1140 SB1 ON B1_COD = C6_PRODUTO AND SB1.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''
WHERE C6_NOTA = ' ' AND SC6.D_E_L_E_T_ =''

 and F1_DTDIGIT > '20211031'
 and F1_EMISSAO < '20211101'

07/10/2021 - Acerto de Bancos no cadastro de clientes

SELECT A1_XXCTABC,COUNT(*) FROM SA1010 GROUP BY A1_XXCTABC ORDER BY A1_XXCTABC

SELECT A1_XXCTABC,* FROM SA1010 WHERE A1_XXCTABC LIKE '%3320%'
AND A1_XXCTABC LIKE '%177676%'

SELECT ''''+D2_CLIENTE+'''',''''+D2_LOJA+'''',''''+D2_CCUSTO+'''',''''+A1_CGC+'''',A1_NOME FROM SD2010 SD2
LEFT JOIN SA1010 SA1 ON A1_COD = D2_CLIENTE AND A1_LOJA = D2_LOJA AND SA1.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''
WHERE D2_EMISSAO > '20201231' AND SD2.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''
GROUP BY D2_CLIENTE,D2_LOJA,D2_CCUSTO,A1_CGC,A1_NOME

SELECT ED_RECIRRF,* FROM SED010 WHERE ED_COND = 'R' AND SUBSTRING(ED_CODIGO,1,1) = '0' 
SELECT ED_RECIRRF,* FROM SED020 WHERE ED_COND = 'R' AND SUBSTRING(ED_CODIGO,1,1) = '0' 
SELECT ED_RECIRRF,* FROM SED120 WHERE ED_COND = 'R' AND SUBSTRING(ED_CODIGO,1,1) = '0' 
SELECT ED_RECIRRF,* FROM SED140 WHERE ED_COND = 'R' AND SUBSTRING(ED_CODIGO,1,1) = '0' 
SELECT ED_RECIRRF,* FROM SED150 WHERE ED_COND = 'R' AND SUBSTRING(ED_CODIGO,1,1) = '0' 
ORDER BY ED_CODIGO 

UPDATE SED010 SET ED_RECIRRF = '3' WHERE ED_COND = 'R' AND SUBSTRING(ED_CODIGO,1,1) = '0' AND ED_RECIRRF = ' '
UPDATE SED020 SET ED_RECIRRF = '3' WHERE ED_COND = 'R' AND SUBSTRING(ED_CODIGO,1,1) = '0' AND ED_RECIRRF = ' '
UPDATE SED120 SET ED_RECIRRF = '3' WHERE ED_COND = 'R' AND SUBSTRING(ED_CODIGO,1,1) = '0' AND ED_RECIRRF = ' '
UPDATE SED140 SET ED_RECIRRF = '3' WHERE ED_COND = 'R' AND SUBSTRING(ED_CODIGO,1,1) = '0' AND ED_RECIRRF = ' '

INDICES CRIADOS===========================================

--11/11/2020
DROP INDEX SE5010W01 ON [dbo].SE5010
CREATE NONCLUSTERED INDEX SE5010W01
ON [dbo].SE5010 (E5_NUMERO,E5_CLIFOR,E5_PREFIXO)
INCLUDE (E5_LOJA, D_E_L_E_T_,E5_VALOR,E5_TIPO,E5_TIPODOC,E5_RECPAG,E5_SITUACA,E5_FILIAL) 

--16/11/2020
DROP INDEX CND010W01 ON [dbo].CND010
CREATE NONCLUSTERED INDEX CND010W01
ON [dbo].CND010 (CND_CONTRA,CND_REVISA,CND_COMPET,CND_PARCEL,CND_NUMERO,D_E_L_E_T_)
INCLUDE ([CND_FILIAL],[CND_PEDIDO])

--16/11/2020
DROP INDEX CNF010W01 ON [dbo].CNF010
CREATE NONCLUSTERED INDEX CNF010W01
ON [dbo].[CNF010] ([CNF_COMPET],[CNF_CONTRA],[D_E_L_E_T_])
INCLUDE ([CNF_NUMERO],[CNF_PARCEL],[CNF_REVISA])

SELECT E1_NUM,E1_SERIE,E1_NATUREZ,E1_PARCELA,E1_CLIENTE,E1_LOJA,E1_NOMCLI,E1_SALDO,E1_VALOR,E1_ISS,E1_XXVRETC,E1_TIPO,E1_INSS,E1_BASEINS,E1_VENCTO,E1_VENCREA,E1_BAIXA,D_E_L_E_T_,E1_VRETBIS,E1_BTRISS,E1_CODISS,R_E_C_N_O_ FROM SE1010
WHERE SE1010.D_E_L_E_T_='' --AND E1_TIPO= 'I2-' --AND E1_VRETBIS > 0
AND E1_NUM IN ('000000359')
--AND E1_CLIENTE = '000040'
ORDER BY E1_NUM,R_E_C_N_O_


SELECT F2_DOC,F2_EMISSAO,F2_CLIENTE,F2_LOJA,F2_BASEISS,F2_BASEIRR,F2_VALISS,F2_VALBRUT,F2_RECISS,F2_ESTPRES,F2_MUNPRES,F2_VLCPM,F2_XXVRETC,F2_XXCVINC FROM SF2010

--AND  F2_DOC IN ('000000317','000000318','000000319','000000320')
AND  F2_DOC IN ('000000359')
--AND F2_CLIENT = '000273'
ORDER BY F2_DOC

SELECT C5_NUM,C5_EMISSAO,C5_NOTA,C5_CLIENTE,C5_LOJACLI,A1_NOME,C5_MUNPRES,C5_DESCMUN,C5_MDCONTR,C5_MDNUMED,C5_MDPLANI,C5_RECISS,A1_NATUREZ,C5_NATUREZ,C5_XXRETC,C5_XXRM,C5_XXTPNF

FROM SC5010
LEFT JOIN SA1010 ON C5_CLIENTE = A1_COD AND C5_LOJACLI = A1_LOJA
WHERE SC5010.D_E_L_E_T_=''  AND SA1010.D_E_L_E_T_ = '' --AND C5_NATUREZ = ''
--AND C5_RECISS <> ''
--AND  C5_NOTA IN ('000000359')
--AND  C5_NOTA >=  'EZ0000038' AND C5_NOTA <=  'EZ0000047'
--and  C5_NUM IN ('045053','045055','045057','045058','045051','045039','045040','045041','045042','045043','045044','045045','045046','045047','045048','045049','045050')
--and A1_NATUREZ = '0000000003'

--and  C5_NUM IN ('045125')
--and  C5_NUM IN ('045107','045119','045120','045122','045124','045125','045129','045130','045131','045132','045134','045138')
and C5_NUM IN ('045214','045215','045213','045219','045220','045222','045223','045224','045225','045209','045211','045212','045217')
--AND C5_MDCONTR = '316000507'
--AND C5_CLIENT = '000273'
ORDER BY C5_NUM

SELECT CNB_CONTRA,CNA_CLIENT,CNA_LOJACL,CNB_REVISA,CNB_NUMERO,CNB_PRODUT,CNB_DESCRI,B1_DESC,B1_CODISS,B1_ALIQISS,CNB_TS,B1_TS,CNA_XXCMUN,CNA_XXMUN,CNA_XXTPNF,CNB010.R_E_C_N_O_,CNA010.R_E_C_N_O_ FROM CNB010
--UPDATE CNB010 SET CNB_PRODUT='281004510-001',CNB_DESCRI = SUBSTRING(B1_DESC,1,30),CNB_TS = B1_TS FROM CNB010
--UPDATE CNB010 SET CNB_PRODUT='281043455-001',CNB_DESCRI = SUBSTRING(B1_DESC,1,30),CNB_TS = B1_TS FROM CNB010
--UPDATE CNB010 SET CNB_PRODUT='281044510-001',CNB_DESCRI = SUBSTRING(B1_DESC,1,30),CNB_TS = B1_TS FROM CNB010
--UPDATE CNB010 SET CNB_DESCRI = SUBSTRING(B1_DESC,1,30),CNB_TS = B1_TS FROM CNB010
--UPDATE CNB010 SET CNB_DESCRI = SUBSTRING(B1_DESC,1,30),CNB_TS = B1_TS FROM CNB010
LEFT JOIN CNA010 ON CNB_NUMERO = CNA_NUMERO AND CNB_CONTRA = CNA_CONTRA AND CNB_REVISA = CNA_REVISA AND CNA010.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''
LEFT JOIN SB1010 ON CNB_PRODUT = B1_COD AND SB1010.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''
WHERE CNB010.D_E_L_E_T_='' 
--AND  CNB_PRODUT in ('000000000000007')
--AND  CNB_PRODUT in ('281049455-003')
--AND CNB_CONTRA IN ('316000507','317000507','318000507','319000507','320000507','321000507') 
AND CNB_CONTRA IN ('281044510') AND CNB_REVISA = '001' -- AND CNB_NUMERO = '000001' 
--AND CNB_REVISA = '024'
--AND CNA_CLIENT = '000040' -- AND CNA_LOJACL = '49'
--AND B1_CODISS = '170201214' 
--AND CNA_XXCMUN = '02403'
ORDER BY CNA_CONTRA,CNA_REVISA,CNB_NUMERO

--05309 - Vitoria ES

SELECT CNA_CONTRA,CNA_REVISA,CNA_CLIENT,CNA_LOJACL,CNA_NOMCLI,A1_NOME,CNA_XXRISS,CNA_XXCMUN,CNA_XXMUN,CNA_XXTPNF,CNA_XXNAT FROM CNA010
--UPDATE CNA010 SET CNA_XXRISS='1',CNA_XXTPNF='B' FROM CNA010 --,CNA_NOMCLI = A1_NOME FROM CNA010 
--UPDATE CNA010 SET CNA_XXRISS='2',CNA_XXTPNF='N' FROM CNA010 --,CNA_NOMCLI = A1_NOME FROM CNA010 
--UPDATE CNA010 SET CNA_XXTPNF='B',CNA_XXRISS='2' FROM CNA010 --,CNA_NOMCLI = A1_NOME FROM CNA010 
--UPDATE CNA010 SET CNA_XXTPNF='B',CNA_XXRISS='2',CNA_LOJACL = '44', CNA_NOMCLI = A1_NOME FROM CNA010 
LEFT JOIN SA1010 ON CNA_CLIENT = A1_COD AND CNA_LOJACL = A1_LOJA AND SA1010.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''
WHERE CNA010.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''
AND CNA_CONTRA IN ('281044510') AND CNA_REVISA = '001'
--AND CNA_CLIENT IN ( '000316', '000317', '000318', '000319', '000320', '000321')-- AND CNA_LOJACL = '01'
--AND CNA_NOMCLI <> A1_NOME


SELECT B1_COD,B1_DESC,B1_ALIQISS,B1_CODISS,B1_TS,B1_TE,B1_CONTA,B1_INSS,B1_IRRF,B1_PIS,B1_COFINS,B1_CSLL,B1_MEPLES  FROM SB1010
--UPDATE SB1150 SET B1_CONTA = '34202009' FROM SB1150
--UPDATE SB1010 SET B1_ALIQISS = 5, B1_DESC = 'ENGENHARIA 5% S/INSS VITORIA' FROM SB1010
WHERE D_E_L_E_T_ = '' 
--AND B1_DESC LIKE '%ENGENH%'
---AND (SUBSTRING(B1_CODISS,1,4) = '1102' 
--AND (SUBSTRING(B1_CODISS,1,4) = '0701' AND B1_ALIQISS = 2)
--AND (B1_CODISS = '170101217') --AND B1_ALIQISS = 3)
--AND B1_IRRF  <> ' '
--AND B1_COD IN ('281014510-001','281015510-001')
AND B1_COD IN ('281015510-001') --,'000000000000227','000000000000228')


SELECT F2_DOC,F2_EMISSAO,F2_CLIENTE,F2_LOJA,F2_BASEISS,F2_BASEIRR,F2_VALISS,F2_VALBRUT,F2_RECISS,F2_ESTPRES,F2_MUNPRES,F2_VLCPM,F2_XXVRETC,F2_XXCVINC FROM SF2010 
--UPDATE SF2010 SET F2_RECISS = '2' FROM SF2010
WHERE D_E_L_E_T_='' 
AND  F2_DOC IN ('000000364','000000365')
--AND F2_CLIENT = '000273'
ORDER BY F2_DOC


select D1_COD,D1_CONTA,* from SD1150 
--UPDATE SD1150 SET D1_CONTA = '34202009'
WHERE D_E_L_E_T_='' 
AND D1_COD IN ('000000000000226','000000000000227','000000000000228')
        

SELECT CND_PEDIDO,* FROM CND010 
WHERE D_E_L_E_T_ = ''
AND CND_NUMMED = '044428'

SELECT CND_NUMERO,CNA_NUMERO,CND_CONTRA,CNA_CONTRA,CND_REVISA,CNA_REVISA,CND_CLIENT,CNA_CLIENT,CND_LOJACL,CNA_LOJACL,CND_XXTPNF,CNA_XXTPNF 
--UPDATE CNA010 SET CNA_XXTPNF = CND_XXTPNF 
FROM CNA010
INNER JOIN CND010 ON CND_NUMERO = CNA_NUMERO AND CND_CONTRA = CNA_CONTRA AND CND_REVISA = CNA_REVISA AND CND010.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''
WHERE CNA010.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''
AND CND_XXTPNF <> ' ' AND CND_XXTPNF <> CNA_XXTPNF


SELECT * FROM SED010 WHERE D_E_L_E_T_=''
ORDER BY ED_CODIGO

-- Alterar especie
SELECT * FROM SF1010 WHERE F1_ESPECIE = 'NF3E' AND F1_DTDIGIT >= '20200901'
UPDATE SF1010 SET F1_ESPECIE = 'NFCEE' WHERE F1_ESPECIE = 'NF3E' AND F1_DTDIGIT >= '20200901'

SELECT * FROM SF3010 WHERE F3_ESPECIE = 'NF3E' AND F3_ENTRADA >= '20200901'
UPDATE SF3010 SET F3_ESPECIE = 'NFCEE' WHERE F3_ESPECIE = 'NF3E' AND F3_ENTRADA >= '20200901'

SELECT * FROM SFT010 WHERE FT_ESPECIE = 'NF3E' AND FT_ENTRADA >= '20200901'
UPDATE SFT010 SET FT_ESPECIE = 'NFCEE' WHERE FT_ESPECIE = 'NF3E' AND FT_ENTRADA >= '20200901'

23/10/20===============================================
--SELECT CNB_CONTRA,CNA_CLIENT,CNA_LOJACL,CNB_REVISA,CNB_NUMERO,CNB_PRODUT,CNB_DESCRI,B1_DESC,B1_CODISS,B1_ALIQISS,CNB_TS,B1_TS,CNA_XXCMUN,CNA_XXMUN,CNA_XXTPNF,CNB010.R_E_C_N_O_,CNA010.R_E_C_N_O_ FROM CNB010
UPDATE CNB010 SET CNB_DESCRI = SUBSTRING(B1_DESC,1,30) FROM CNB010
LEFT JOIN CNA010 ON CNB_NUMERO = CNA_NUMERO AND CNB_CONTRA = CNA_CONTRA AND CNB_REVISA = CNA_REVISA AND CNA010.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''
LEFT JOIN SB1010 ON CNB_PRODUT = B1_COD AND SB1010.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''
WHERE CNB010.D_E_L_E_T_='' 
AND SUBSTRING(B1_DESC,1,30) <> CNB_DESCRI  
ORDER BY CNA_CONTRA,CNA_REVISA,CNB_NUMERO

15/10/20===============================================
Correo da reteno contratual conforme planilha fornecida pela Fbia

25/09/20===============================================

DECLARE @plan VARCHAR(6) = '000018' 
DECLARE @revisa VARCHAR(3) = '004'
SELECT @plan, @revisa

select SUM(CNA_VLTOT) AS TOTAL,SUM(CNA_VLTOT) AS TOTAL,SUM(CNA_SALDO) AS SALDOPLANILHA --,CNA_CRONOG
 from CNA140 WHERE D_E_L_E_T_='' AND CNA_CONTRA='302000508' AND CNA_REVISA= @revisa AND CNA_NUMERO=@plan


select SUM(CNB_VLTOT) AS TOTALCNB,SUM(CNB_QUANT*CNB_VLUNIT) AS VALUNIT, SUM(CNB_SLDMED*CNB_VLUNIT) AS SALDOITEMPLANILHA
	 from CNB140 WHERE D_E_L_E_T_='' AND CNB_CONTRA='302000508' AND CNB_REVISA= @revisa AND CNB_NUMERO=@plan
group by CNB_NUMERO


select SUM(CNF_VLPREV) AS VALPREVCRON,SUM(CNF_VLPREV),SUM(CNF_SALDO) AS SALDOCRON --,CNF_NUMERO
 from CNF140 CNF1
 WHERE D_E_L_E_T_='' AND CNF_CONTRA='302000508' AND CNF_REVISA= @revisa AND CNF_NUMPLA=@plan


 select * from CNF140 
 WHERE D_E_L_E_T_='' AND CNF_CONTRA='302000508' AND CNF_REVISA= @revisa AND CNF_NUMPLA=@plan


SELECT * INTO CNBXXX FROM CNB140
SELECT * INTO CNAXXX FROM CNA140
SELECT * INTO CNFXXX FROM CNF140

USE dataP12Tst
GO
SELECT DB_NAME() AS DbName,
name AS FileName,
size/128.0 AS CurrentSizeMB,
size/128.0 - CAST(FILEPROPERTY(name, 'SpaceUsed') AS INT)/128.0 AS FreeSpaceMB
FROM sys.database_files
WHERE type_desc = 'ROWS'
GO

select 28946.500000 - 5926.375000

GO

17/08/20=============================================== 

MP - FIS - ISS, Configurao para Reduo de Base por EDSON SOARES FLORENCIO
Dvida
Qual a configurao para a correta reduo da Base de ISS ?

Ambiente
Microsiga Protheus Livros Fiscais A partir da verso 11.80

Soluo
Configurar o parmetro abaixo:

MV_DBRDIF = .F.
Indica se o valor do ICMS/ISS a ser deduzido, quando o campo F4_AGREG = D ou R , dever ser sobre o
valor da base reduzida ou valor de reduo da base.

Preencher os campos abaixo no Cadastro de Produtos:
Aliq. ISS (B1_ALIQISS) = preencher com a alquota do imposto.
Cod. Serv. ISS (B1_CODISS) = preencher com o cdigo de Servio.

Preencher os campos no Cadastro do Fornecedor
Recolhe ISS (A2_RECISS) = N - No

Preencher os campos abaixo no Cadastro do TES
Calculo ISS (F4_ISS) = S - Sim
L. Fiscal ISS (F4_LFISS) = T - Tributado
Agrega Valor (F4_AGREG) = D - Ded IC V.Ct
%Red. do ISS (F4_BASEISS) = Define o percentual da base de ISS para o caso de existir base reduzida.

Configurar Natureza para reter ISS 
Calcula ISS (ED_CALCISS) = Sim

Informaes Adicionais:
https://tdn.totvs.com/pages/releaseview.action?pageId=6076798
https://tdn.totvs.com/pages/releaseview.action?pageId=235571086



14/08/20=============================================== 
Alterado o Parmetro MV_ESPECIE da Seguradora para: UNI=NF;1=RPS;2=RPS;
Reprocessado todo o livro da Seguradora

DELETE FROM SFT120
DELETE FROM SF3120


SELECT B1_MEPLES,* FROM SB1120 WHERE SUBSTRING(B1_COD,1,5) = '00000'

Nas aquisies: 

Se o servio for configurado como EP (B1_MEPLES = 1 ou Branco), ou seja, ISS devido no estabelecimento do prestador, o ISS ser considerado devido no municpio do fornecedor do documento (A2_COD_MUN).
Se o servio for configurado como LES (B1_MEPLES = 2), ou seja, ISS devido no local de execuo do servio, primeiramente sero avaliados os campos F1_ESTPRES e F1_INCISS, que podem ser informados no momento da digitao do documento de entrada. Se estes campos estiverem preenchidos, o ISS ser considerado devido no municpio ali definido.
Caso contrrio, o ISS ser considerado devido no municpio do SIGAMAT (M0_CODMUN).

Nas prestaes: 
Se o servio for configurado como EP (B1_MEPLES = 1 ou Branco), ou seja, ISS devido no estabelecimento do prestador, o ISS ser considerado devido no municpio do SIGAMAT (M0_CODMUN).
Se o servio for configurado como LES (B1_MEPLES = 2), ou seja, ISS devido no local de execuo do servio, primeiramente sero avaliados os campos F2_ESTPRES e F2_MUNPRES, preenchidos atravs dos campos C5_ESTPRES e C5_MUNPRES no pedido de venda. Se estes campos estiverem prenchidos o ISS ser considerado devido no municpio ali definido.

Caso contrrio o ISS ser considerado devido no municpio do cliente de faturamento (A1_COD_MUN).
No sistema, EP significa Estabelecimento do Prestador, LES significa Local de Execuo do Servio.
Esta configurao  feita no cadastro de produto, por meio do campo Exec. Servio(B1_MEPLES), a opo 1 indica EP e opo 2 indica LES, e caso este campo esteja vazio, ser adotada EP como padro.

Informaes adicionais:

https://tdn.totvs.com/pages/viewpage.action?pageId=500292737

UPDATE SB1120 SET B1_MEPLES = '1' FROM SB1120 WHERE SUBSTRING(B1_COD,1,5) = '00000'

UPDATE SC9010 SET C9_XXORPED = 'N' FROM SC9010
UPDATE SC5010 SET C5_XXTPNF  = 'N' FROM SC5010
UPDATE SC9010 SET C9_XXORPED = 'A' FROM SC9010 SC9, SC5010 SC5 
WHERE SC5.C5_NUM = SC9.C9_PEDIDO AND SC5.C5_CLIENTE = SC9.C9_CLIENTE AND SC5.D_E_L_E_T_ = '' AND SC9.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''
  AND (SUBSTRING(C5_NOTA,1,1) = 'E' OR SUBSTRING(C5_NOTA,1,1) = 'F')
UPDATE SC5010 SET C5_XXTPNF = 'A' FROM SC5010 SC5
WHERE SUBSTRING(C5_NOTA,1,1) = 'E' OR SUBSTRING(C5_NOTA,1,1) = 'F'

UPDATE SC9020 SET C9_XXORPED = 'N' FROM SC9020
UPDATE SC5020 SET C5_XXTPNF  = 'N' FROM SC5020
UPDATE SC9020 SET C9_XXORPED = 'A' FROM SC9020 SC9, SC5020 SC5 
WHERE SC5.C5_NUM = SC9.C9_PEDIDO AND SC5.C5_CLIENTE = SC9.C9_CLIENTE AND SC5.D_E_L_E_T_ = '' AND SC9.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''
  AND (SUBSTRING(C5_NOTA,1,1) = 'E' OR SUBSTRING(C5_NOTA,1,1) = 'F')
UPDATE SC5020 SET C5_XXTPNF = 'A' FROM SC5020 SC5
WHERE SUBSTRING(C5_NOTA,1,1) = 'E' OR SUBSTRING(C5_NOTA,1,1) = 'F'

UPDATE SC9120 SET C9_XXORPED = 'N' FROM SC9120
UPDATE SC5120 SET C5_XXTPNF  = 'N' FROM SC5120
UPDATE SC9120 SET C9_XXORPED = 'A' FROM SC9120 SC9, SC5120 SC5 
WHERE SC5.C5_NUM = SC9.C9_PEDIDO AND SC5.C5_CLIENTE = SC9.C9_CLIENTE AND SC5.D_E_L_E_T_ = '' AND SC9.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''
  AND (SUBSTRING(C5_NOTA,1,1) = 'E' OR SUBSTRING(C5_NOTA,1,1) = 'F')
UPDATE SC5120 SET C5_XXTPNF = 'A' FROM SC5120 SC5
WHERE SUBSTRING(C5_NOTA,1,1) = 'E' OR SUBSTRING(C5_NOTA,1,1) = 'F'

UPDATE SC9140 SET C9_XXORPED = 'N' FROM SC9140
UPDATE SC5140 SET C5_XXTPNF  = 'N' FROM SC5140
UPDATE SC9140 SET C9_XXORPED = 'A' FROM SC9140 SC9, SC5140 SC5 
WHERE SC5.C5_NUM = SC9.C9_PEDIDO AND SC5.C5_CLIENTE = SC9.C9_CLIENTE AND SC5.D_E_L_E_T_ = '' AND SC9.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''
  AND (SUBSTRING(C5_NOTA,1,1) = 'E' OR SUBSTRING(C5_NOTA,1,1) = 'F')

SELECT CT2_DATA,CT2_LOTE,CT2_DOC,CT2_LINHA,CT2_DEBITO,CT2_CREDIT,CT2_VALOR,CT2_HIST,CT2_ORIGEM FROM CT2010 
WHERE CT2_ORIGEM = '650001-CTBANFE-ADREA BRITO DE -20/07/2020' OR CT2_ORIGEM = '650001-CTBANFE-PAMELA CASTRO D-20/07/2020' OR CT2_ORIGEM = '650001-CTBANFE-ADALBERTO XAVIE-18/07/2020'
ORDER BY CT2_DATA

20/07/20 =============================================== 

SELECT CNB_PRODUT,CNB_DESCRI,CTT_CUSTO,CTT_DESC01 FROM CNB010 CNB 
LEFT JOIN CTT010 CTT ON CTT_CUSTO = CNB_CONTRA AND CTT.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''
WHERE CNB_PRODUT = '000000000000213' AND CNB.D_E_L_E_T_ = '' 
GROUP BY CTT_CUSTO,CTT_DESC01,CNB_PRODUT,CNB_DESCRI
ORDER BY CTT_CUSTO,CTT_DESC01,CNB_PRODUT,CNB_DESCRI

17/07/20 =============================================== 


SELECT D1_DOC,D1_ITEM,D1_FILIAL,D1_COD,B1_DESC,B1_GRUPO,D1_CC,(D1_TOTAL+D1_VALFRE+D1_SEGURO+D1_DESPESA-D1_VALDESC) AS D1_TOTAL,E2_DESCONT,E2_VALOR,E2_PARCELA
 FROM SD1010 SD1
 LEFT JOIN SB1010 SB1 ON D1_COD = B1_COD  AND SB1.D_E_L_E_T_ = ' ' 
 LEFT JOIN SE2010 SE2 ON E2_NUM = D1_DOC AND D1_SERIE = E2_PREFIXO AND D1_FORNECE = E2_FORNECE AND D1_LOJA = E2_LOJA AND E2_TIPO = 'NF' AND SE2.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''
 WHERE SUBSTRING(D1_DTDIGIT,1,6) = '202006' AND SD1.D_E_L_E_T_ = ' ' 
 AND D1_CC = '346000530'
 AND (SUBSTRING(D1_CONTA,1,1) = '3' OR D1_CONTA in ('29104004') OR SUBSTRING(D1_CONTA,1,5) = '12201')
 --GROUP BY  D1_FILIAL,D1_COD,B1_DESC,B1_GRUPO,D1_CC

15/07/20 =============================================== 


UPDATE SC9010 SET C9_XXORPED = 'C' FROM SC9010 SC9, SC5010 SC5 
WHERE SC5.C5_NUM = SC9.C9_PEDIDO AND SC5.C5_CLIENTE = SC9.C9_CLIENTE AND SC5.D_E_L_E_T_ = '' AND SC9.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''
AND C5_MDCONTR <> ' '
UPDATE SC9010 SET C9_XXORPED = 'A' FROM SC9010 SC9, SC5010 SC5 
WHERE SC5.C5_NUM = SC9.C9_PEDIDO AND SC5.C5_CLIENTE = SC9.C9_CLIENTE AND SC5.D_E_L_E_T_ = '' AND SC9.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''
AND C5_MDCONTR = ' '

09/06/20 =============================================== 

Use dataP10


SELECT F4_CODIGO,F4_CODBCC,F4_CSTPIS FROM SF4010 WHERE D_E_L_E_T_ <> '*' ORDER BY F4_CODIGO

SELECT F4_CODIGO,F4_CODBCC,F4_CSTPIS,F4_TPREG FROM SF4120 WHERE D_E_L_E_T_ <> '*' ORDER BY F4_CODIGO
SELECT F4_CODIGO,F4_CODBCC,F4_CSTPIS,F4_TPREG FROM SF4020 WHERE D_E_L_E_T_ <> '*' ORDER BY F4_CODIGO


SELECT F4_CODIGO,F4_CODBCC FROM SF4020 WHERE F4_CODBCC <> ' ' ORDER BY F4_CODIGO

UPDATE SF4020 SET SF4020.F4_CODBCC = SF4010.F4_CODBCC FROM SF4010 WHERE SF4020.F4_CODIGO = SF4010.F4_CODIGO
UPDATE SF4120 SET SF4120.F4_CODBCC = SF4010.F4_CODBCC FROM SF4010 WHERE SF4120.F4_CODIGO = SF4010.F4_CODIGO

UPDATE SF4020 SET SF4020.F4_CF = SF4120.F4_CF FROM SF4120 WHERE SF4120.F4_CODIGO = SF4020.F4_CODIGO

UPDATE SF4020 SET F4_TPREG = '2', F4_SITTRIB = '40'
UPDATE SF4120 SET F4_TPREG = '2', F4_SITTRIB = '40'

UPDATE SF4020 SET F4_PISCRED='3',F4_CSTPIS = '70', F4_CSTCOF = '70' WHERE SUBSTRING(F4_CODIGO,1,1) = '1'
UPDATE SF4120 SET F4_PISCRED='3',F4_CSTPIS = '70', F4_CSTCOF = '70' WHERE SUBSTRING(F4_CODIGO,1,1) = '1'

UPDATE SF4020 SET F4_CSTPIS = '01', F4_CSTCOF = '01' WHERE SUBSTRING(F4_CODIGO,1,1) = '5'
UPDATE SF4120 SET F4_CSTPIS = '01', F4_CSTCOF = '01' WHERE SUBSTRING(F4_CODIGO,1,1) = '5'


UPDATE SD1020 SET D1_CF = '2'+SUBSTRING(F4_CF,2,3) FROM SD1020
INNER JOIN SF4020 ON D1_TES = F4_CODIGO AND. SF4020.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''
INNER JOIN SA2020 ON D1_FORNECE = A2_COD AND D1_LOJA = A2_LOJA AND SA2020.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''
WHERE A2_EST <> 'SP' AND D1_TES <> ''

UPDATE SD1120 SET D1_CF = '2'+SUBSTRING(F4_CF,2,3) FROM SD1120
INNER JOIN SF4120 ON D1_TES = F4_CODIGO AND. SF4120.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''
INNER JOIN SA2120 ON D1_FORNECE = A2_COD AND D1_LOJA = A2_LOJA AND SA2120.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''
WHERE A2_EST <> 'SP' AND D1_TES <> ''



UPDATE SD1020 SET D1_CF = F4_CF FROM SD1020
INNER JOIN SF4020 ON D1_TES = F4_CODIGO AND. SF4020.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''
INNER JOIN SA2020 ON D1_FORNECE = A2_COD AND D1_LOJA = A2_LOJA AND SA2020.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''
WHERE A2_EST = 'SP' AND D1_TES <> ''

UPDATE SD1120 SET D1_CF = F4_CF FROM SD1120
INNER JOIN SF4120 ON D1_TES = F4_CODIGO AND. SF4120.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''
INNER JOIN SA2120 ON D1_FORNECE = A2_COD AND D1_LOJA = A2_LOJA AND SA2120.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''
WHERE A2_EST = 'SP' AND D1_TES <> ''


UPDATE SD2020 SET D2_CF = '6'+SUBSTRING(F4_CF,2,3) FROM SD2020
INNER JOIN SF4020 ON D2_TES = F4_CODIGO AND. SF4020.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''
WHERE D2_EST <> 'SP'

UPDATE SD2120 SET D2_CF = '6'+SUBSTRING(F4_CF,2,3) FROM SD2120
INNER JOIN SF4120 ON D2_TES = F4_CODIGO AND. SF4120.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''
WHERE D2_EST <> 'SP'



UPDATE SD2020 SET D2_CF = F4_CF FROM SD2020
INNER JOIN SF4020 ON D2_TES = F4_CODIGO AND. SF4020.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''
WHERE D2_EST = 'SP'

UPDATE SD2120 SET D2_CF = F4_CF FROM SD2120
INNER JOIN SF4120 ON D2_TES = F4_CODIGO AND. SF4120.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''
WHERE D2_EST = 'SP'

DELETE FROM SF3020 WHERE Substring(F3_ENTRADA,1,6) >= '201901'

DELETE FROM SFT120 WHERE Substring(FT_ENTRADA,1,6) >= '201901'

SELECT ED_CODIGO,ED_DESCRIC, ED_APURCOF,ED_APURPIS,ED_TPREG,ED_COND,ED_PCAPPIS,ED_PCAPCOF,ED_INDRET,ED_INDCMLT FROM SED010 WHERE D_E_L_E_T_='' ORDER BY ED_CODIGO
SELECT ED_CODIGO,ED_DESCRIC, ED_APURCOF,ED_APURPIS,ED_TPREG,ED_COND,ED_PCAPPIS,ED_PCAPCOF,ED_INDRET,ED_INDCMLT,ED_CSTPIS,ED_CSTCOF FROM SED020 WHERE D_E_L_E_T_='' ORDER BY ED_CODIGO
SELECT ED_CODIGO,ED_DESCRIC, ED_APURCOF,ED_APURPIS,ED_TPREG,ED_COND,ED_PCAPPIS,ED_PCAPCOF,ED_INDRET,ED_INDCMLT,ED_CSTPIS,ED_CSTCOF FROM SED120 WHERE D_E_L_E_T_='' ORDER BY ED_CODIGO

UPDATE SED020 SET ED_APURPIS = 'D',ED_APURCOF='D',ED_COND='R',ED_PCAPPIS = 1.65,ED_PCAPCOF=3,ED_INDRET='03',ED_INDCMLT='1',ED_CSTPIS='01',ED_CSTCOF='01'  WHERE SUBSTRING(ED_DESCRIC,1,5)='CLIEN'
UPDATE SED020 SET ED_APURPIS = 'C',ED_APURCOF='C',ED_COND='D',ED_INDCMLT='1' WHERE SUBSTRING(ED_CODIGO,1,1)='0' AND ED_COND <> 'R'

UPDATE SED120 SET ED_APURPIS = 'D',ED_APURCOF='D',ED_COND='R',ED_PCAPPIS = 1.65,ED_PCAPCOF=3,ED_INDRET='03',ED_INDCMLT='1',ED_CSTPIS='01',ED_CSTCOF='01'  WHERE SUBSTRING(ED_DESCRIC,1,5)='CLIEN'
UPDATE SED120 SET ED_APURPIS = 'C',ED_APURCOF='C',ED_COND='D',ED_INDCMLT='1' WHERE SUBSTRING(ED_CODIGO,1,1)='0' AND ED_COND <> 'R'

UPDATE SED020 SET ED_TPREG = '2'
UPDATE SED120 SET ED_TPREG = '2'

select B1_TPREG from SB1010 WHERE B1_TPREG <> ' '

select A1_COD,A1_TPREG from SA1020 WHERE A1_TPREG <> ' '
select A2_COD,A2_TPREG from SA2010 WHERE A2_TPREG <> ' '
select A2_COD,A2_TPREG from SA2020 WHERE A2_TPREG <> ' '

select * from SF1020 WHERE F1_DTDIGIT >= '202001'

02/06/20 =============================================== 

select CN9_VLATU,CN9_SALDO,CN9_REVISA from CN9010 WHERE D_E_L_E_T_='' AND CN9_NUMERO='129000351' AND CN9_REVISA='019'

select SUM(CNF_VLPREV) AS VALPREVCRON,SUM(CNF_SALDO) AS SALDOCRON--,CNF_NUMERO
--select (CNF_VLPREV) AS VALPREVCRON,(CNF_SALDO) AS SALDOCRON,* --,CNF_NUMERO
 from CNF010 CNF1
 WHERE D_E_L_E_T_='' AND CNF_CONTRA='129000351' AND CNF_REVISA='019' --AND CNF_NUMERO='001917'
 --group by CNF_NUMERO

select CNF_NUMERO,R_E_C_N_O_,CNF_VLPREV, CNF_VLPREV * 1000 - CAST(CNF_VLPREV * 1000 AS INT) AS VALPREVCRON,CNF_SALDO, CNF_SALDO * 100 - CAST(CNF_SALDO * 100 AS INT) AS SALDOCRON
 from CNF010 CNF1
 WHERE D_E_L_E_T_='' AND CNF_CONTRA='129000351' AND CNF_REVISA='019' --AND CNF_NUMERO='001917'

select
SUM(CNA_VLTOT) AS TOTAL,SUM(CNA_SALDO) AS SALDOPLAINILHA--,CNA_CRONOG
 from CNA010 WHERE D_E_L_E_T_='' AND CNA_CONTRA='129000351' AND CNA_REVISA='019' --AND CNA_NUMERO='000009'
--group by CNA_CRONOG

SELECT SUM(CNB_SLDMED) FROM CNB010 AS QTDAMEDIR WHERE CNB_CONTRA='129000351' AND CNB_REVISA='019'

-- Dividir SALDOCRON POR CNF_VLPREV = Deveria ser igual ao QTDAMEDIR (CNB_SLDMED)

select * from SZ2010 WHERE Z2_DATAPGT > '20200519' AND Z2_DATAPGT <= '20200521' AND Z2_STATUS = 'S'
order by Z2_E2NUM
UPDATE SZ2010 SET Z2_DATAPGT = '20200519' WHERE Z2_DATAPGT > '20200519' AND Z2_DATAPGT <= '20200521' AND Z2_STATUS = 'S'

select * from SZ2010 WHERE SUBSTRING(Z2_E2NUM,1,6) =  '321426'

01/05/20 =============================================== 

-- Cronogramas com diferena de dzimas
select CNF_SALDO,CNF_SALDO - ROUND(CNF_SALDO,2),R_E_C_N_O_ from CNF010 WHERE (CNF_SALDO - ROUND(CNF_SALDO,2)) <> 0 AND D_E_L_E_T_ = '' ORDER BY R_E_C_N_O_

-- Cronogramas com saldos inferiores a 10
select R_E_C_N_O_,* from CNF010 WHERE CNF_SALDO <= 10 AND CNF_SALDO <> 0  AND D_E_L_E_T_ = '' ORDER BY CNF_CONTRA

SET @emp = '980'
set @tab = 'SD1'

dataP12Tst

UPDATE SE1010 SET E1_VENCTO = E1_EMISSAO, E1_VENCREA = E1_EMISSAO, E1_MOVIMEN = E1_EMISSAO, E1_VENCORI = E1_EMISSAO  WHERE SUBSTRING(E1_EMISSAO,1,6) >= '201901' AND SE1010.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''

UPDATE SE1010 SET E1_BAIXA = E1_EMISSAO WHERE SUBSTRING(E1_EMISSAO,1,6) >= '201901' AND SE1010.D_E_L_E_T_ = '' AND E1_BAIXA <> ''

USE [master]
RESTORE DATABASE [dataP12Tst] FROM  DISK = N'\\vmpandora\Backup Protheus 12\2020-04-23-dataP10.bak' WITH  FILE = 1,  MOVE N'DATA' TO N'D:\Arquivos\Dados\dataP12Tst.mdf',  MOVE N'DATA_log' TO N'D:\Arquivos\Logs\dataP12Tst.ldf',  NOUNLOAD,  REPLACE,  STATS = 5

GO

31/03/20 ================================================ Contrato com problema no CNB

select CN9_VLATU,CN9_SALDO,CN9_REVISA from CN9010 WHERE D_E_L_E_T_='' AND CN9_NUMERO='198000293' AND CN9_REVISA='012'

select SUM(CNF_VLPREV) AS VALPREVCRON,SUM(CNF_SALDO) AS SALDOCRON--,CNF_NUMERO
--select (CNF_VLPREV) AS VALPREVCRON,(CNF_SALDO) AS SALDOCRON,* --,CNF_NUMERO
 from CNF010 CNF1
 WHERE D_E_L_E_T_='' AND CNF_CONTRA='198000293' AND CNF_REVISA='012' --AND CNF_NUMERO='001917'
 --group by CNF_NUMERO
/*
SELECT CAST(25.65 AS int);

select CNF_NUMERO,R_E_C_N_O_,CNF_VLPREV, CNF_VLPREV * 1000 - CAST(CNF_VLPREV * 1000 AS INT) AS VALPREVCRON,CNF_SALDO, CNF_SALDO * 100 - CAST(CNF_SALDO * 100 AS INT) AS SALDOCRON
 from CNF010 CNF1
 WHERE D_E_L_E_T_='' AND CNF_CONTRA='198000293' AND CNF_REVISA='012' --AND CNF_NUMERO='001917'
*/

select
SUM(CNA_VLTOT) AS TOTAL,SUM(CNA_SALDO) AS SALDOPLAINILHA--,CNA_CRONOG
 from CNA010 WHERE D_E_L_E_T_='' AND CNA_CONTRA='198000293' AND CNA_REVISA='012' --AND CNA_NUMERO='000009'
--group by CNA_CRONOG



select SUM(CNB_VLTOT) AS TOTAL,SUM(CNB_QUANT*CNB_VLUNIT) AS VALUNIT, SUM(CNB_SLDMED*CNB_VLUNIT) AS SALDOITEMPLANILHA
--	select CNB_VLTOT AS TOTAL,(CNB_QUANT*CNB_VLUNIT) AS VALUNIT, (CNB_SLDMED*CNB_VLUNIT) AS SALDOITEMPLANILHA,*
	 from CNB010 WHERE D_E_L_E_T_='' AND CNB_CONTRA='198000293' AND CNB_REVISA='012' --AND CNB_NUMERO='000009'
--group by CNB_NUMERO




31/03/20 ================================================ Otimizao
/*
Detalhes de ndice Ausentes de SQLQuery1.sql - VMPANDORA\SQLPANDORA.dataP12 (sa (109))
O Processador de Consultas estima que a implementao do ndice a seguir pode melhorar o custo da consulta em 81.6276%.
*/

USE [dataP12]
GO
CREATE NONCLUSTERED INDEX [SA2010_DEL]
ON [dbo].[SA2010] ([D_E_L_E_T_])
INCLUDE ([A2_COD],[A2_LOJA],[A2_NOME])
GO

31/03/20 ================================================ NFS classificadas

Notas fiscais classificadas pelo Adilson Marinho 

SELECT F1_XXUSER,F1_XXUSERS,F1_SERIE,F1_DOC,F1_VALBRUT,
(SELECT TOP 1 Cast(Cast(D1_XXHIST As varbinary(max)) As varchar(max)) FROM SD1010 WHERE F1_FILIAL = D1_FILIAL AND F1_DOC = D1_DOC AND F1_SERIE = D1_SERIE AND F1_FORNECE = D1_FORNECE AND F1_LOJA = D1_LOJA AND F1_TIPO = D1_TIPO ) AS HIST
FROM SF1010 WHERE F1_XXUSERS = '000007' AND F1_DTDIGIT >= '20200101'
ORDER BY F1_DTDIGIT DESC

19/03/20 ================================================ EFD 12/19

UPDATE SE1010 SET E1_VENCTO = E1_EMISSAO, E1_VENCREA = E1_EMISSAO, E1_MOVIMEN = E1_EMISSAO, E1_VENCORI = E1_EMISSAO  WHERE SUBSTRING(E1_EMISSAO,1,6) >= '201908' AND SE1010.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''
UPDATE SE1010 SET E1_BAIXA = E1_EMISSAO WHERE SUBSTRING(E1_EMISSAO,1,6) >= '201901' AND SE1010.D_E_L_E_T_ = '' AND E1_BAIXA <> ''

UPDATE SE1140 SET E1_VENCTO = E1_EMISSAO, E1_VENCREA = E1_EMISSAO, E1_MOVIMEN = E1_EMISSAO, E1_VENCORI = E1_EMISSAO  WHERE SUBSTRING(E1_EMISSAO,1,6) >= '201908' AND SE1140.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''
UPDATE SE1140 SET E1_BAIXA = E1_EMISSAO WHERE SUBSTRING(E1_EMISSAO,1,6) >= '201901' AND SE1140.D_E_L_E_T_ = '' AND E1_BAIXA <> ''

SELECT E5_FILIAL+E5_PREFIXO+E5_NUMERO+E5_PARCELA+E5_TIPO+E5_CLIFOR+E5_LOJA,E1_FILIAL+E1_PREFIXO+E1_NUM+E1_PARCELA+E1_TIPO+E1_CLIENTE+E1_LOJA,
E1_VALOR,E5_VALOR,E1_EMISSAO,E1_BAIXA,E5_DATA,E5_VENCTO,E5_DTDIGIT,E5_DTDISPO
 FROM SE5010 LEFT JOIN SE1010 ON E5_FILIAL+E5_PREFIXO+E5_NUMERO+E5_PARCELA+E5_CLIFOR+E5_LOJA = E1_FILIAL+E1_PREFIXO+E1_NUM+E1_PARCELA+E1_CLIENTE+E1_LOJA 
WHERE SUBSTRING(E1_EMISSAO,1,6) >= '201901'  AND E1_BAIXA <> '' AND SE1010.D_E_L_E_T_ = '' AND SE5010.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''


UPDATE SE5010 SET E5_DATA=E1_EMISSAO,E5_VENCTO=E1_EMISSAO,E5_DTDIGIT=E1_EMISSAO,E5_DTDISPO=E1_EMISSAO
 FROM SE5010 INNER JOIN SE1010 ON E5_FILIAL+E5_PREFIXO+E5_NUMERO+E5_PARCELA+E5_CLIFOR+E5_LOJA = E1_FILIAL+E1_PREFIXO+E1_NUM+E1_PARCELA+E1_CLIENTE+E1_LOJA 
WHERE SUBSTRING(E1_EMISSAO,1,6) >= '201901'  AND E1_BAIXA <> '' AND SE1010.D_E_L_E_T_ = '' AND SE5010.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''

UPDATE FK1010 SET FK1_DATA = E5_DATA FROM FK1010 INNER JOIN SE5010 ON FK1_IDFK1 = E5_IDORIG
WHERE SUBSTRING(E5_DATA,1,6) >= '201901' 

-- Baixar os titulos em aberto no periodo (Baixa automatica)
SELECT * FROM SE1010 WHERE E1_BAIXA = '' AND SUBSTRING(E1_EMISSAO,1,6) = '201912' AND E1_TIPO = 'NF' AND SE1010.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''
SELECT * FROM SE1140 WHERE E1_BAIXA = '' AND SUBSTRING(E1_EMISSAO,1,6) = '201912' AND E1_TIPO = 'NF' AND SE1140.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''

use master
BACKUP LOG dataP10 TO DISK='Nul:'
ALTER DATABASE dataP10 SET RECOVERY SIMPLE
use dataP10
DBCC SHRINKFILE(N'DATA_log')
ALTER DATABASE dataP10 SET RECOVERY FULL

07/03/20 ===========================================================


UPDATE SC5010 SET C5_XXCOMPM = SUBSTRING(C5_XXCOMPT,1,2)+'/'+SUBSTRING(C5_XXCOMPT,3,4) FROM SC5010 WHERE C5_XXCOMPM = '' AND C5_XXCOMPT <> ''
UPDATE SC5020 SET C5_XXCOMPM = SUBSTRING(C5_XXCOMPT,1,2)+'/'+SUBSTRING(C5_XXCOMPT,3,4) FROM SC5020 WHERE C5_XXCOMPM = '' AND C5_XXCOMPT <> ''
UPDATE SC5040 SET C5_XXCOMPM = SUBSTRING(C5_XXCOMPT,1,2)+'/'+SUBSTRING(C5_XXCOMPT,3,4) FROM SC5040 WHERE C5_XXCOMPM = '' AND C5_XXCOMPT <> ''
UPDATE SC5140 SET C5_XXCOMPM = SUBSTRING(C5_XXCOMPT,1,2)+'/'+SUBSTRING(C5_XXCOMPT,3,4) FROM SC5140 WHERE C5_XXCOMPM = '' AND C5_XXCOMPT <> ''


select C5_XXCOMPM,C5_MDNUMED,CND_NUMMED FROM SC5010 INNER JOIN CND010 ON C5_MDNUMED = CND_NUMMED

UPDATE SC5010 SET C5_XXCOMPM = CND_COMPET FROM SC5010 INNER JOIN CND010 ON C5_MDNUMED = CND_NUMMED
UPDATE SC5020 SET C5_XXCOMPM = CND_COMPET FROM SC5020 INNER JOIN CND020 ON C5_MDNUMED = CND_NUMMED
UPDATE SC5040 SET C5_XXCOMPM = CND_COMPET FROM SC5040 INNER JOIN CND040 ON C5_MDNUMED = CND_NUMMED
UPDATE SC5140 SET C5_XXCOMPM = CND_COMPET FROM SC5140 INNER JOIN CND140 ON C5_MDNUMED = CND_NUMMED

29/02/20 ===========================================================


Acerto datas impostos retidos para EFD

Use dataP12
Select E1_EMISSAO,E1_VENCTO,E1_VENCREA,E1_BAIXA from SE1010 WHERE SUBSTRING(E1_EMISSAO,1,6) >= '201908' AND SE1010.D_E_L_E_T_ = '' AND E1_BAIXA <> ''
ORDER BY E1_EMISSAO

UPDATE SE1010 SET E1_VENCTO = E1_EMISSAO, E1_VENCREA = E1_EMISSAO, E1_MOVIMEN = E1_EMISSAO, E1_VENCORI = E1_EMISSAO  WHERE SUBSTRING(E1_EMISSAO,1,6) >= '201908' AND SE1010.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''

UPDATE SE1010 SET E1_BAIXA = E1_EMISSAO WHERE SUBSTRING(E1_EMISSAO,1,6) >= '201908' AND SE1010.D_E_L_E_T_ = '' AND E1_BAIXA <> ''




27/02/20 ===========================================================

SELECT SUM(E5_VALOR) AS E5VALOR FROM SE5010 WHERE E5_PREFIXO = '1  ' AND E5_NUMERO = '000045535' AND E5_PARCELA = '  ' AND E5_TIPO = 'NF' AND  E5_CLIFOR = '000197' and E5_LOJA = '01' 
AND E5_TIPODOC = 'DC' AND E5_RECPAG = 'R' AND E5_SITUACA <> 'C'


 SELECT CNF_CONTRA,CNF_REVISA,A1_NOME,CTT_DESC01,CN9_SITUAC,CNA_XXMUN,SUM(D2_TOTAL) AS D2_TOTAL,SUM(D2_VALISS) AS D2_VALISS,
 SUM(E5_VALOR) AS E5VALOR 
 FROM CNF010 CNF INNER JOIN CN9010 CN9 ON CN9.CN9_NUMERO = CNF.CNF_CONTRA AND CN9.CN9_REVISA = CNF.CNF_REVISA AND CN9.CN9_FILIAL = '01' AND  CN9.D_E_L_E_T_ = '' 
 LEFT JOIN CTT010 CTT ON CTT_CUSTO = CNF_CONTRA AND  CTT_FILIAL = '01' AND  CTT.D_E_L_E_T_ = '' 
 LEFT JOIN CNA010 CNA ON CNA_CRONOG = CNF_NUMERO AND CNA_REVISA = CNF_REVISA      AND  CNA_FILIAL = '01' AND  CNA.D_E_L_E_T_ = ' ' 
 LEFT JOIN CND010 CND ON CND_CONTRA = CNF_CONTRA AND CND_COMPET = CNF_COMPET AND CND_PARCEL = CNF_PARCEL AND CNA_NUMERO = CND_NUMERO AND CND_REVISA = CNF_REVISA      AND  CND_FILIAL = '01' AND  CND.D_E_L_E_T_ = ' ' 
 LEFT JOIN SC6010 SC6 ON CND_PEDIDO = C6_NUM      AND  C6_FILIAL = '01'  AND  SC6.D_E_L_E_T_ = ' '	
 LEFT JOIN SD2010 SD2 ON SC6.C6_NUM = SD2.D2_PEDIDO AND C6_ITEM = D2_ITEM        AND  D2_FILIAL = '01'  AND  SD2.D_E_L_E_T_ = ' '  
 LEFT JOIN SE5010 SE5 ON E5_PREFIXO = D2_SERIE AND E5_NUMERO = D2_DOC  AND E5_TIPO = 'NF' AND  E5_CLIFOR = D2_CLIENTE and E5_LOJA = D2_LOJA AND E5_TIPODOC = 'DC' AND E5_RECPAG = 'R' AND E5_SITUACA <> 'C' --AND E5_PARCELA = '  '
 INNER JOIN SA1010 SA1 ON CN9.CN9_CLIENT = SA1.A1_COD  AND CN9.CN9_LOJACL = SA1.A1_LOJA  AND  SA1.A1_FILIAL = '  ' AND  SA1.D_E_L_E_T_ = ' ' 
  
  WHERE CNF.D_E_L_E_T_='' AND CNF.CNF_COMPET='01/2020'  AND CNF_CONTRA ='281000473' AND CN9.CN9_SITUAC <> '10' 
  GROUP BY CNF_CONTRA,CNF_REVISA,A1_NOME,CTT_DESC01,CN9_SITUAC,CNA_XXMUN 
  ORDER BY CNF_CONTRA





select CN9_VLATU,CN9_SALDO,CN9_REVISA from CN9140 WHERE D_E_L_E_T_='' AND CN9_NUMERO='302000508' AND CN9_REVISA='003'

select SUM(CNF_VLPREV) AS VALPREVCRON,SUM(CNF_SALDO) AS SALDOCRON--,CNF_NUMERO
 from CNF140 CNF1
 WHERE D_E_L_E_T_='' AND CNF_CONTRA='302000508' AND CNF_REVISA='003' AND CNF_NUMERO='000007'
 
 select *
 from CNF140 CNF1
 WHERE D_E_L_E_T_='' AND CNF_CONTRA='302000508' AND CNF_REVISA='003' AND CNF_NUMERO='000007'
 
 

 --group by CNF_NUMERO
/*
SELECT CAST(25.65 AS int);

select CNF_NUMERO,R_E_C_N_O_,CNF_VLPREV, CNF_VLPREV * 1000 - CAST(CNF_VLPREV * 1000 AS INT) AS VALPREVCRON,CNF_SALDO, CNF_SALDO * 100 - CAST(CNF_SALDO * 100 AS INT) AS SALDOCRON
 from CNF140 CNF1
 WHERE D_E_L_E_T_='' AND CNF_CONTRA='142000415' AND CNF_REVISA='009' --AND CNF_NUMERO='000007'
*/

select CNA_CRONOG,
SUM(CNA_VLTOT) AS TOTAL,SUM(CNA_SALDO) AS SALDOPLAINILHA
 from CNA140 WHERE D_E_L_E_T_='' AND CNA_CONTRA='302000508' AND CNA_REVISA='003' AND CNA_NUMERO='000001'
group by CNA_CRONOG

select * from CNA140
 WHERE D_E_L_E_T_='' AND CNA_CONTRA='302000508' AND CNA_REVISA='003' AND CNA_NUMERO='000001'


select CNB_NUMERO,SUM(CNB_VLTOT) AS TOTAL,SUM(CNB_QUANT*CNB_VLUNIT) AS VALUNIT, SUM(CNB_SLDMED*CNB_VLUNIT) AS SALDOITEMPLANILHA

 from CNB140 WHERE D_E_L_E_T_='' AND CNB_CONTRA='302000508' AND CNB_REVISA='003' AND CNB_NUMERO='000001' --AND CNB_ITEM = '001'
group by CNB_NUMERO


SELECT (CNB_SLDMED*CNB_VLUNIT) AS SALDOITEMPLANILHA,* from CNB010 WHERE D_E_L_E_T_='' AND CNB_CONTRA='302000508' AND CNB_REVISA='003' AND CNB_NUMERO='000001'

SELECT * FROM CND010 WHERE CND_CONTRA = '302000508'

Use dataP10
SELECT D_E_L_E_T_,'INSERT INTO SE1_X01 (E1_FILIAL,E1_PREFIXO,E1_NUM,E1_PARCELA,E1_TIPO,E1_NATUREZ,E1_CLIENTE,E1_LOJA,E1_NOMCLI,E1_EMISSAO,E1_VENCTO,E1_VENCREA,E1_VALOR,E1_EMIS1,E1_LA,E1_SITUACA,E1_SALDO,E1_VENCORI,E1_MOEDA,E1_OCORREN,E1_VLCRUZ,E1_STATUS,E1_ORIGEM,E1_FILORIG,E1_MSFIL,E1_MSEMP,E1_TITPAI,R_E_C_N_O_) VALUES'+
'('''+E1_FILIAL+''','+
''''+E1_PREFIXO+''','+
''''+E1_NUM+''','+
''''+E1_PARCELA+''','+
''''+'IR-'+''','+
''''+'IRF'+''','+
''''+E1_CLIENTE+''','+
''''+E1_LOJA+''','+
''''+E1_NOMCLI+''','+
''''+E1_EMISSAO+''','+
''''+E1_VENCTO+''','+
''''+E1_VENCREA+''','+
STR(E1_IRRF,17,2)+','+
''''+E1_EMIS1+''','+
''''+' '+''','+
''''+E1_SITUACA+''','+
STR(E1_IRRF,17,2)+','+
''''+E1_VENCORI+''','+
''''+'1'+''','+
''''+'04'+''','+
STR(E1_IRRF,17,2)+','+
''''+E1_STATUS+''','+
''''+E1_ORIGEM+''','+
''''+E1_FILORIG+''','+
''''+E1_MSFIL+''','+
''''+E1_MSEMP+''','+
''''+E1_PREFIXO+E1_NUM+E1_PARCELA+E1_TIPO+E1_CLIENTE+E1_LOJA+''')'
FROM SE1020
WHERE E1_NUM IN ('000002216')

23/01/2020 - Marcos ====================================================

Select E5_DATA,E5_DTDIGIT,E5_DTDISPO,E5_VENCTO,E5_DATA,E5_NUMERO,E1_NUM,* from SE5010 SE5 

UPDATE SE5010 SET E5_DATA=E1_EMISSAO,E5_DTDIGIT=E1_EMISSAO,E5_DTDISPO=E1_EMISSAO,E5_VENCTO=E1_EMISSAO
from SE5010 SE5
LEFT JOIN SE1010 SE1 ON (SE5.E5_FILIAL=SE1.E1_FILIAL AND SE5.E5_TIPODOC NOT IN ('DC','JR','MT') AND SE5.E5_PREFIXO=SE1.E1_PREFIXO AND SE5.E5_NUMERO=SE1.E1_NUM AND SE5.E5_PARCELA=SE1.E1_PARCELA AND SE5.E5_TIPO=SE1.E1_TIPO AND 
SE5.E5_CLIFOR=SE1.E1_CLIENTE AND SE5.E5_LOJA=SE1.E1_LOJA AND 
SE5.E5_TIPODOC	<> 'ES' AND
SE5.E5_MOTBX NOT IN ('LIQ','CEC') AND 
SE5.E5_SITUACA <> 'C' AND 
SE5.D_E_L_E_T_ =  ' ') 
WHERE SUBSTRING(E1_EMISSAO,1,6) >= '201910' AND SE1.D_E_L_E_T_ = '' AND E1_TITPAI = '' 
AND E1_TIPO = 'NF '


22/01/2020 - Marcos ====================================================

Base teste
UPDATE SE1010 SET E1_VENCTO = E1_EMISSAO, E1_VENCREA = E1_EMISSAO, E1_MOVIMEN = E1_EMISSAO, E1_VENCORI = E1_EMISSAO  WHERE SUBSTRING(E1_EMISSAO,1,6) >= '201911' AND SE1010.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''
UPDATE SE1010 SET E1_BAIXA = E1_EMISSAO WHERE SUBSTRING(E1_EMISSAO,1,6) >= '201911' AND SE1010.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''

10/01/20
SELECT D1_TES,D1_DTDIGIT,D1_CF,D1_FORNECE,D1_TOTAL,D1_COD FROM SD1010
UPDATE SD1010 SET D1_TES = '107',D1_CF = '1933'
SELECT D1_TES,D1_DTDIGIT,D1_CF,D1_FORNECE,D1_TOTAL,D1_COD FROM SD1010
WHERE D1_FORNECE = '001570' AND D1_COD = '11301007' AND SD1010.D_E_L_E_T_<>'*' AND Substring(D1_DTDIGIT,1,6) > '201910'
UPDATE SFT010 SET FT_TES = '107',FT_CFOP = '1933'
SELECT FT_TES,FT_ENTRADA,FT_CFOP,FT_CLIEFOR,FT_TOTAL,FT_PRODUTO FROM SFT010
WHERE FT_TIPOMOV = 'E' AND FT_CLIEFOR = '001570' AND FT_PRODUTO = '11301007' AND SFT010.D_E_L_E_T_<>'*' AND Substring(FT_ENTRADA,1,6) > '201910'
UPDATE SD1010 SET D1_TES = '107',D1_CF = '1933'
WHERE D1_FORNECE = '001570' AND D1_COD = '29104004' AND SD1010.D_E_L_E_T_<>'*' AND Substring(D1_DTDIGIT,1,6) > '201910'
SELECT D1_TES,D1_DTDIGIT,D1_CF,D1_FORNECE,D1_TOTAL,D1_COD FROM SD1010
WHERe D1_COD = '29104004' AND SD1010.D_E_L_E_T_<>'*' AND Substring(D1_DTDIGIT,1,6) > '201910'
UPDATE SFT010 SET FT_TES = '107',FT_CFOP = '1933'
SELECT FT_TES,FT_ENTRADA,FT_CFOP,FT_CLIEFOR,FT_TOTAL,FT_PRODUTO FROM SFT010
WHERE FT_TIPOMOV = 'E' AND FT_CLIEFOR = '001570' AND FT_PRODUTO = '29104004' AND SFT010.D_E_L_E_T_<>'*' AND Substring(FT_ENTRADA,1,6) > '201910'
DELETE FROM SFT010 WHERE Substring(FT_ENTRADA,1,6) = '201912'
DELETE FROM SF3010 WHERE Substring(F3_ENTRADA,1,6) = '201912'

03/01/2020
Configurao EFD Balsa Nova

use dataP10
UPDATE SD1140 SET D1_CF = '2'+SUBSTRING(F4_CF,2,3) FROM SD1140
INNER JOIN SF4140 ON D1_TES = F4_CODIGO AND. SF4140.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''
INNER JOIN SA2140 ON D1_FORNECE = A2_COD AND D1_LOJA = A2_LOJA AND SA2140.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''
WHERE A2_EST <> 'SP' AND D1_TES <> ''

UPDATE SD1140 SET D1_CF = F4_CF FROM SD1140
INNER JOIN SF4140 ON D1_TES = F4_CODIGO AND. SF4140.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''
INNER JOIN SA2140 ON D1_FORNECE = A2_COD AND D1_LOJA = A2_LOJA AND SA2140.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''
WHERE A2_EST = 'SP' AND D1_TES <> ''

UPDATE SD2140 SET D2_CF = '6'+SUBSTRING(F4_CF,2,3) FROM SD2140
INNER JOIN SF4140 ON D2_TES = F4_CODIGO AND. SF4140.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''
WHERE D2_EST <> 'SP'

UPDATE SD2140 SET D2_CF = F4_CF FROM SD2140
INNER JOIN SF4140 ON D2_TES = F4_CODIGO AND. SF4140.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''
WHERE D2_EST = 'SP'

DELETE FROM SFT140 --WHERE Substring(FT_ENTRADA,1,6) = '201910'
DELETE FROM SF3140 --WHERE Substring(F3_ENTRADA,1,6) = '201910'

MV_CFAREC = 5933,6933

03/01/2020
Reviso de Contrato
select CN9_VLATU,CN9_SALDO,CN9_REVISA from CN9010 WHERE D_E_L_E_T_='' AND CN9_NUMERO='281000473' AND CN9_REVISA='   '
select SUM(CNF_VLPREV) AS VALPREVCRON,SUM(CNF_SALDO) AS SALDOCRON--,CNF_NUMERO
 from CNF010 CNF1
 WHERE D_E_L_E_T_='' AND CNF_CONTRA='281000473' AND CNF_REVISA='   ' --AND CNF_NUMERO='001917'
 --group by CNF_NUMERO
/*
SELECT CAST(25.65 AS int);
select CNF_NUMERO,R_E_C_N_O_,CNF_VLPREV, CNF_VLPREV * 1000 - CAST(CNF_VLPREV * 1000 AS INT) AS VALPREVCRON,CNF_SALDO, CNF_SALDO * 100 - CAST(CNF_SALDO * 100 AS INT) AS SALDOCRON
 from CNF010 CNF1
 WHERE D_E_L_E_T_='' AND CNF_CONTRA='142000415' AND CNF_REVISA='009' --AND CNF_NUMERO='001917'
*/
select
SUM(CNA_VLTOT) AS TOTAL,SUM(CNA_SALDO) AS SALDOPLAINILHA--,CNA_CRONOG
 from CNA010 WHERE D_E_L_E_T_='' AND CNA_CONTRA='281000473' AND CNA_REVISA='   ' --AND CNA_NUMERO='000009'
--group by CNA_CRONOG
select SUM(CNB_VLTOT) AS TOTAL,SUM(CNB_QUANT*CNB_VLUNIT) AS VALUNIT, SUM(CNB_SLDMED*CNB_VLUNIT) AS SALDOITEMPLANILHA
 from CNB010 WHERE D_E_L_E_T_='' AND CNB_CONTRA='281000473' AND CNB_REVISA='   ' --AND CNB_NUMERO='000009'
--group by CNB_NUMERO

02/01/2020

Acerto datas impostos retidos para EFD

Use dataP12
Select E1_EMISSAO,E1_VENCTO,E1_VENCREA,E1_BAIXA from SE1010 WHERE SUBSTRING(E1_EMISSAO,1,6) >= '201908' AND SE1010.D_E_L_E_T_ = '' AND E1_BAIXA <> ''
ORDER BY E1_EMISSAO

UPDATE SE1010 SET E1_VENCTO = E1_EMISSAO, E1_VENCREA = E1_EMISSAO, E1_MOVIMEN = E1_EMISSAO, E1_VENCORI = E1_EMISSAO  WHERE SUBSTRING(E1_EMISSAO,1,6) >= '201908' AND SE1010.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''

UPDATE SE1010 SET E1_BAIXA = E1_EMISSAO WHERE SUBSTRING(E1_EMISSAO,1,6) >= '201908' AND SE1010.D_E_L_E_T_ = '' AND E1_BAIXA <> ''


SELECT * from SE1010 WHERE SUBSTRING(E1_EMISSAO,1,6) >= '201908' AND SE1010.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''  and E1_NUM = '000045008'
ORDER BY E1_EMISSAO
SELECT E1_NUM,E1_EMISSAO,* FROM SE5010 INNER JOIN SE1010 ON E5_PREFIXO = E1_PREFIXO AND E5_NUMERO = E1_NUM AND E5_PARCELA = E1_PARCELA AND E5_TIPO = E1_TIPO AND SE1010.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''
WHERE  SUBSTRING(E1_EMISSAO,1,6) >= '201908' AND SE5010.D_E_L_E_T_ = '' AND E5_RECPAG = 'R' and E5_NUMERO = '000044817'
UPDATE SE5010 SET E5_DATA = E1_EMISSAO,E5_DTDIGIT = E1_EMISSAO,E5_DTDISPO = E1_EMISSAO FROM SE5010 INNER JOIN SE1010 ON E5_PREFIXO = E1_PREFIXO AND E5_NUMERO = E1_NUM AND E5_PARCELA = E1_PARCELA AND E5_TIPO = E1_TIPO AND SE1010.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''
WHERE SUBSTRING(E1_EMISSAO,1,6) >= '201908' AND SE5010.D_E_L_E_T_ = '' AND E5_RECPAG = 'R'

20/12/19

NF 000062949 alterado o D1_DTDIGIT de 18/12/19 para 18/10/19 de 200,40

Query com todos itens de entrada para conferncia de Pis/Cofin - EFD
SELECT D1_TES,D1_DOC,D1_ITEM,D1_COD,B1_DESC,D1_VUNIT,D1_TOTAL,D1_BASIMP5,D1_VALIMP5,D1_VALIMP6,SD1010.R_E_C_N_O_ FROM SD1010
INNER JOIN SB1010 ON B1_COD = D1_COD AND SB1010.D_E_L_E_T_ <> '*'
WHERE SUBSTRING(D1_DTDIGIT,1,6) = '201910' AND SD1010.D_E_L_E_T_ <> '*'
ORDER BY D1_DOC,D1_ITEM
