13/12/19

MP - FIS - EFD CONTRIBUIES - Como gerar o registro F600, 1300 e 1700 do Sped Contribuies
https://centraldeatendimento.totvs.com/hc/pt-br/articles/360016177611-MP-FIS-EFD-CONTRIBUI%C3%87%C3%95ES-Como-gerar-o-registro-F600-1300-e-1700-do-Sped-Contribui%C3%A7%C3%B5es


USE dataP10
select D1_SERIE,D1_DOC,D1_DTDIGIT,F1_ESPECIE,'="'+D1_COD+'"' AS D1_COD,B1_DESC,D1_TES,F4_TEXTO,'="'+D1_CC+'"' AS D1_CC,D1_FORNECE,D1_LOJA,A2_NOME,B1_CONTA,D1_TOTAL,D1_VALCOF,D1_VALPIS,D1_BASIMP5,D1_BASIMP6 from SD1010
INNER JOIN SB1010 ON B1_COD = D1_COD AND SB1010.D_E_L_E_T_ <> '*'
INNER JOIN SF4010 ON D1_TES = F4_CODIGO AND SF4010.D_E_L_E_T_ <> '*'
INNER JOIN SF1010 ON F1_DOC = D1_DOC AND F1_SERIE = D1_SERIE AND F1_FORNECE = D1_FORNECE AND F1_LOJA = D1_LOJA AND SF1010.D_E_L_E_T_<>'*'
INNER JOIN SA2010 ON D1_FORNECE = A2_COD AND D1_LOJA = A2_LOJA AND SA2010.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''
 WHERE SD1010.D_E_L_E_T_<>'*' AND Substring(D1_DTDIGIT,1,6) = '201910'
 ORDER BY D1_COD


UPDATE SD1010 SET D1_TES = '101' WHERE D1_TES <> '101' AND D1_SERIE = 'DNF' AND SD1010.D_E_L_E_T_<>'*' AND Substring(D1_DTDIGIT,1,6) = '201910' AND D1_TES <> ''
UPDATE SD1010 SET D1_TES = '105'  FROM SD1010 WHERE  D1_SERIE = 'DNF' AND SD1010.D_E_L_E_T_<>'*' AND Substring(D1_DTDIGIT,1,6) = '201910' AND D1_TES <> '' AND D1_COD ='320200301'
UPDATE SD1010 SET D1_TES = '104'  FROM SD1010 WHERE SD1010.D_E_L_E_T_<>'*' AND Substring(D1_DTDIGIT,1,6) = '201910' AND D1_TES <> '' AND D1_COD ='000000000000141' AND D1_CC <> '000000001' AND D1_SERIE <> 'DNF'

12/12/19

use dataP10
UPDATE SD1010 SET D1_CF = '2'+SUBSTRING(F4_CF,2,3) FROM SD1010
INNER JOIN SF4010 ON D1_TES = F4_CODIGO AND. SF4010.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''
INNER JOIN SA2010 ON D1_FORNECE = A2_COD AND D1_LOJA = A2_LOJA AND SA2010.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''
WHERE Substring(D1_DTDIGIT,1,6) >= '201910' AND A2_EST <> 'SP'

UPDATE SD1010 SET D1_CF = F4_CF FROM SD1010
INNER JOIN SF4010 ON D1_TES = F4_CODIGO AND. SF4010.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''
INNER JOIN SA2010 ON D1_FORNECE = A2_COD AND D1_LOJA = A2_LOJA AND SA2010.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''
WHERE Substring(D1_DTDIGIT,1,6) >= '201910' AND A2_EST = 'SP'

UPDATE SD2010 SET D2_CF = '6'+SUBSTRING(F4_CF,2,3) FROM SD2010
INNER JOIN SF4010 ON D2_TES = F4_CODIGO AND. SF4010.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''
WHERE Substring(D2_EMISSAO,1,6) >= '201910' AND D2_EST <> 'SP'

UPDATE SD2010 SET D2_CF = F4_CF FROM SD2010
INNER JOIN SF4010 ON D2_TES = F4_CODIGO AND. SF4010.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''
WHERE Substring(D2_EMISSAO,1,6) >= '201910' AND D2_EST = 'SP'

SELECT A2_NOME,A2_CGC,* FROM SF1010
INNER JOIN SA2010 ON F1_FORNECE = A2_COD AND F1_LOJA = A2_LOJA AND SA2010.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''
WHERE SF1010.D_E_L_E_T_ = '' AND Substring(F1_DTDIGIT,1,6) = '201910'

DELETE FROM SFT010 WHERE Substring(FT_ENTRADA,1,6) = '201910'
DELETE FROM SF3010 WHERE Substring(F3_ENTRADA,1,6) = '201910'

==================================================================

use dataP10
select A1_COD,A1_LOJA,A1_NOME,A1_RECIRRF FROM SA1140 WHERE A1_RECIRRF = ' '
UPDATE SA1010 SET A1_RECIRRF = '2' WHERE A1_COD = '000045'


06/12/2019

Acerto titulos de IRRF no gerados:

Criar uma tabela a parte com a estrutura do E1: (trocar NOT NULL por NULL) COPIAR O IDENTIFY DO R_E_C_N_O_)

Use dataP10
SELECT E1_IRRF,E1_FILIAL,E1_PREFIXO,E1_NUM,E1_PARCELA,E1_TIPO,E1_NATUREZ,E1_CLIENTE,E1_LOJA,E1_NOMCLI,E1_EMISSAO,E1_VENCTO,E1_VENCREA,E1_VALOR,E1_EMIS1,E1_LA,E1_SITUACA,E1_SALDO,E1_VENCORI,E1_MOEDA,E1_OCORREN,E1_VLCRUZ,E1_STATUS,E1_ORIGEM,E1_FILORIG,E1_MSFIL,E1_MSEMP,E1_TITPAI
FROM SE1010
WHERE E1_IRRF > 0 AND E1_SALDO = E1_VALOR AND E1_VRETIRF > 0 AND SE1010.D_E_L_E_T_ = '' AND E1_TIPO = 'NF' AND SUBSTRING(E1_EMISSAO,1,6) >= '201911'
SELECT 'INSERT INTO SE1_X01 (E1_FILIAL,E1_PREFIXO,E1_NUM,E1_PARCELA,E1_TIPO,E1_NATUREZ,E1_CLIENTE,E1_LOJA,E1_NOMCLI,E1_EMISSAO,E1_VENCTO,E1_VENCREA,E1_VALOR,E1_EMIS1,E1_LA,E1_SITUACA,E1_SALDO,E1_VENCORI,E1_MOEDA,E1_OCORREN,E1_VLCRUZ,E1_STATUS,E1_ORIGEM,E1_FILORIG,E1_MSFIL,E1_MSEMP,E1_TITPAI) VALUES'+
'('''+E1_FILIAL+''','+
''''+E1_PREFIXO+''','+
''''+E1_NUM+''','+
''''+E1_PARCELA+''','+
''''+'IR-'+''','+
''''+'IRF'+''','+
''''+E1_CLIENTE+''','+
''''+E1_LOJA+''','+
''''+E1_NOMCLI+''','+
''''+E1_EMISSAO+''','+
''''+E1_VENCTO+''','+
''''+E1_VENCREA+''','+
STR(E1_IRRF,17,2)+','+
''''+E1_EMIS1+''','+
''''+' '+''','+
''''+E1_SITUACA+''','+
STR(E1_IRRF,17,2)+','+
''''+E1_VENCORI+''','+
''''+'1'+''','+
''''+'04'+''','+
STR(E1_IRRF,17,2)+','+
''''+E1_STATUS+''','+
''''+E1_ORIGEM+''','+
''''+E1_FILORIG+''','+
''''+E1_MSFIL+''','+
''''+E1_MSEMP+''','+
''''+E1_PREFIXO+E1_NUM+E1_PARCELA+E1_TIPO+E1_CLIENTE+E1_LOJA+''')'
SELECT ''''+E1_NUM+''',',E1_NUM
FROM SE1010
WHERE E1_NUM IN ('000045191',

25/11/19

UPDATE SF1010 SET F1_ESPECIE='NFE'
WHERE F1_ESPECIE = 'SPED' AND SUBSTRING(F1_DTDIGIT,1,6) >= '201909'
UPDATE SF3010 SET F3_ESPECIE='NFE'
WHERE F3_ESPECIE = 'SPED' AND SUBSTRING(F3_ENTRADA,1,6) >= '201909'

UPDATE SD1010 SET D1_CF = '2'+SUBSTRING(F4_CF,2,3) FROM SD1010
INNER JOIN SF4010 ON D1_TES = F4_CODIGO AND. SF4010.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''
INNER JOIN SA2010 ON D1_FORNECE = A2_COD AND D1_LOJA = A2_LOJA AND SA2010.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''
WHERE Substring(D1_DTDIGIT,1,6) >= '201909' AND A2_EST <> 'SP'
UPDATE SD1010 SET D1_CF = F4_CF FROM SD1010
INNER JOIN SF4010 ON D1_TES = F4_CODIGO AND. SF4010.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''
INNER JOIN SA2010 ON D1_FORNECE = A2_COD AND D1_LOJA = A2_LOJA AND SA2010.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''
WHERE Substring(D1_DTDIGIT,1,6) >= '201909' AND A2_EST = 'SP'

UPDATE SD1010 SET D1_TES = '104' WHERE
SUBSTRING(D1_COD,1,3) = 'UNI' AND
D_E_L_E_T_='' AND

SUBSTRING(D1_DTDIGIT,1,6) >= '201909'
UPDATE SD1010 SET D1_TES = '104' WHERE
SUBSTRING(D1_COD,1,3) = 'EPI' AND
D_E_L_E_T_='' AND
SUBSTRING(D1_DTDIGIT,1,6) >= '201909'

--UPDATE SF1010 SET F1_ESPECIE='NFS'
 from SF1010 SF1
INNER JOIN SD1010 SD1 ON SD1.D_E_L_E_T_='' AND D1_DOC=F1_DOC
AND D1_SERIE=F1_SERIE
AND D1_FORNECE=F1_FORNECE
AND D1_LOJA=F1_LOJA
AND D1_COD='31103001'
AND D1_DTDIGIT>='20190901'
AND D1_SERIE<>'DNF'

UPDATE SD2010 SET D2_CF = '6'+SUBSTRING(F4_CF,2,3) FROM SD2010
INNER JOIN SF4010 ON D2_TES = F4_CODIGO AND. SF4010.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''
WHERE Substring(D2_EMISSAO,1,6) = '201909' AND D2_EST <> 'SP'

INNER JOIN SF4010 ON D2_TES = F4_CODIGO AND. SF4010.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''
WHERE Substring(D2_EMISSAO,1,6) = '201909' AND D2_EST = 'SP'

INNER JOIN SF4010 ON D1_TES = F4_CODIGO AND. SF4010.D_E_L_E_T_ = ''

WHERE Substring(D1_DTDIGIT,1,6) = '201909' AND A2_EST <> 'SP'

use dataP10
select C1_CC,C8_ITEM,C8_PRODUTO,B1_DESC,C8_UM,C8_NUMSC,C8_QUANT,C8_PRECO,C1_XXLCVAL,C8_VLDESC,C8_VALFRE,C8_DESPESA,C8_SEGURO FROM SC8010
INNER JOIN SB1010 SB1 ON C8_PRODUTO = SB1.B1_COD AND SB1.D_E_L_E_T_=''
INNER JOIN SC1010 SC1 ON C8_NUMSC = C1_NUM AND C8_ITEMSC = C1_ITEM AND SC1.D_E_L_E_T_=''
WHERE C8_NUMPED <> 'XXXXXX' AND C8_EMISSAO >= '20190301' AND C8_EMISSAO <= '201903311'
      aForn[nPosForn,nPSubTot]   += (SC8->C8_QUANT*SC8->C8_PRECO)  // Sub-Total
      aForn[nPosForn,nPDesconto] += (SC8->C8_VLDESC)  // Desconto
      aForn[nPosForn,nPFrete]    += (SC8->C8_VALFRE)  // Frete
      aForn[nPosForn,nPOutros]   += (SC8->C8_DESPESA+SC8->C8_SEGURO)  // Outros
      aForn[nPosForn,nPTotal]    += ((SC8->C8_QUANT*SC8->C8_PRECO) - SC8->C8_VLDESC + SC8->C8_VALFRE + SC8->C8_DESPESA+SC8->C8_SEGURO)
 
SELECT C8_ITEM,C8_PRODUTO,C8_EMISSAO,C8_FORNECE,C8_LOJA,C8_UM,C8_NUMSC,C8_QUANT,C8_PRECO,C1_XXLCVAL,C8_VLDESC,C8_VALFRE,C8_DESPESA,C8_SEGURO,B1_DESC,C1_CC,CTT_DESC01,A2_NOME
FROM SC8010 SC8
INNER JOIN SB1010 SB1 ON SB1.B1_FILIAL='01' AND SC8.C8_PRODUTO = SB1.B1_COD AND SB1.D_E_L_E_T_=''
INNER JOIN SC1010 SC1 ON SC1.C1_FILIAL='01' AND SC8.C8_NUMSC = SC1.C1_NUM AND SC8.C8_ITEMSC = SC1.C1_ITEM AND SC1.D_E_L_E_T_=''
INNER JOIN CTT010 CTT ON CTT.CTT_FILIAL='01' AND SC1.C1_CC = CTT.CTT_CUSTO AND CTT.D_E_L_E_T_=''
INNER JOIN SA2010 SA2 ON SA2.A2_FILIAL='  ' AND SC8.C8_FORNECE=SA2.A2_COD AND SC8.C8_LOJA=SA2.A2_LOJA AND SA2.D_E_L_E_T_=''
WHERE SC8.C8_FILIAL='01' AND SC8.D_E_L_E_T_=''
AND SC8.C8_EMISSAO >= '20190101' AND SC8.C8_EMISSAO <='20190331'
AND SC1.C1_CC = '258000429'

SELECT * FROM SZI010

'000004051' ,
'000004059' ,
'000004060'

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

WITH GER AS (
SELECT 
	FG.EMPRESA AS EMPRESA,
	FG.NOMEEMP AS NOMEEMP,
GETDATE() AS DATAPRC,
	FG.CONTRATO AS CONTRATO,
FG.DESCRICAO,
G.CN9_XXNRBK,
FG.COMPETAM,
FG.COMPET,
FG.COMPETD,
FG.EMPRESA + FG.CONTRATO + FG.COMPET AS CHAVE,
SUM(FG.VALFAT) AS VALFAT,
SUM(FG.PREVFAT) AS PREVFAT,
SUM(FG.DESPESA) AS TOTDESP,
CHAVEZG
FROM 
	(SELECT 
	EMPRESA,
	NOMEEMP,
	CONTRATO,
	DESCRICAO,
	COMPETAM,
	COMPET,
	COMPETD,
	SUM(F2_VALFAT) AS VALFAT,
	SUM(CXN_VLPREV) AS PREVFAT,
	SUM(0) AS DESPESA,
	(SELECT TOP 1 ZGCHAVE FROM 
		(SELECT MAX(COMPETAM+ZG_SEQ) AS ZGCHAVE
		FROM PREVDESP1 
		WHERE PREVDESP1.EMPRESA = FATURAMENTO.EMPRESA AND PREVDESP1.CONTRATO = FATURAMENTO.CONTRATO AND PREVDESP1.COMPETAM <= FATURAMENTO.COMPETAM
		GROUP BY PREVDESP1.CONTRATO,PREVDESP1.ZG_DATA
		) AS X
		ORDER BY ZGCHAVE DESC) AS CHAVEZG
	 FROM PowerBk.dbo.FATURAMENTO
	   GROUP BY EMPRESA,NOMEEMP,CONTRATO,DESCRICAO,COMPETAM,COMPET,COMPETD
	 UNION ALL
	 SELECT EMPRESA,
 	NOMEEMP,
	CONTRATO,
	DESCRICAO,
	COMPETAM,
	COMPET,
	COMPETD,
	SUM(0) AS VALFAT,
	SUM(0) AS PREVFAT,
	SUM(DESPESA) AS DESPESA,
	(SELECT TOP 1 ZGCHAVE FROM 
		(SELECT MAX(COMPETAM+ZG_SEQ) AS ZGCHAVE
		FROM PREVDESP1 
		WHERE PREVDESP1.EMPRESA = GASTOSGERAIS.EMPRESA AND PREVDESP1.CONTRATO = GASTOSGERAIS.CONTRATO AND PREVDESP1.COMPETAM <= GASTOSGERAIS.COMPETAM
		GROUP BY PREVDESP1.CONTRATO,PREVDESP1.ZG_DATA
		) AS X
		ORDER BY ZGCHAVE DESC) AS CHAVEZG

	   FROM PowerBk.dbo.GASTOSGERAIS
       GROUP BY EMPRESA,NOMEEMP,CONTRATO,DESCRICAO,COMPETAM,COMPET,COMPETD
	 ) AS FG
LEFT JOIN PowerBk.dbo.GESTORES G
   ON	G.EMPRESA  = FG.EMPRESA 
AND G.CONTRATO = FG.CONTRATO 
GROUP BY FG.EMPRESA,FG.NOMEEMP,FG.CONTRATO,FG.DESCRICAO,FG.COMPETAM,FG.COMPET,FG.COMPETD,G.CN9_XXNRBK,CHAVEZG)
--SELECT * FROM GER
	--WHERE GER.CONTRATO = '346000530'


SELECT 
	GER.* ,
   	PDP1.ZG_DATA,
   	PDP1.ZG_SEQ,
   	PDP1.ZG_CLT,
   	PDP1.ZG_ENCSOC,
   	PDP1.ZG_VLENCSO,
   	PDP1.ZG_AJCUSTO,
   	PDP1.ZG_ENCAC,
   	PDP1.ZG_VLENAC,
   	PDP1.ZG_INSUMOS,
   	PDP1.ZG_BENEFIC,
   	PDP1.ZG_EQUIPAM,
   	PDP1.ZG_UNIFORM,
   	PDP1.ZG_DESPDIV,
   	PDP1.ZG_TRIBUTO,
   	PDP1.ZG_VLTRIBU,
   	PDP1.ZG_RENTABI,
   	PDP1.ZG_VLRENTA,
   	PDP1.ZG_TOTAL

FROM GER
LEFT JOIN PREVDESP1 PDP1 ON 
	GER.EMPRESA  = PDP1.EMPRESA AND 
	GER.CONTRATO = PDP1.CONTRATO AND 
	GER.CHAVEZG  = PDP1.COMPETAM+PDP1.ZG_SEQ

	--WHERE GER.CONTRATO = '346000530'

ORDER BY GER.EMPRESA,GER.CONTRATO,GER.COMPETAM

SELECT EMPRESA,CONTRATO,COMPETAM,ZG_SEQ,'SELECT * FROM dataP10.dbo.SZL010 WHERE D_E_L_E_T_ = '''' AND ZL_CONTRAT = '''+CONTRATO+''' UNION ALL' FROM PREVDESP1
GROUP BY EMPRESA,CONTRATO,COMPETAM,ZG_SEQ
HAVING COUNT(*) > 1


SELECT * FROM dataP10.dbo.SZL010 WHERE D_E_L_E_T_ = '' AND ZL_CONTRAT = '008000363' UNION ALL
SELECT * FROM dataP10.dbo.SZL010 WHERE D_E_L_E_T_ = '' AND ZL_CONTRAT = '008047034' UNION ALL
SELECT * FROM dataP10.dbo.SZL010 WHERE D_E_L_E_T_ = '' AND ZL_CONTRAT = '008049034' UNION ALL
SELECT * FROM dataP10.dbo.SZL010 WHERE D_E_L_E_T_ = '' AND ZL_CONTRAT = '008051034' UNION ALL
SELECT * FROM dataP10.dbo.SZL010 WHERE D_E_L_E_T_ = '' AND ZL_CONTRAT = '008058034' UNION ALL
SELECT * FROM dataP10.dbo.SZL010 WHERE D_E_L_E_T_ = '' AND ZL_CONTRAT = '008095034' UNION ALL
SELECT * FROM dataP10.dbo.SZL010 WHERE D_E_L_E_T_ = '' AND ZL_CONTRAT = '008097034' UNION ALL
SELECT * FROM dataP10.dbo.SZL010 WHERE D_E_L_E_T_ = '' AND ZL_CONTRAT = '008130034' UNION ALL

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------


SELECT 
(SELECT TOP 1 * FROM 
	(SELECT MAX(COMPETAM+ZG_SEQ) AS ZGCHAVE
	FROM PREVDESP1 
	WHERE PREVDESP1.EMPRESA = GERAL.EMPRESA AND PREVDESP1.CONTRATO = GERAL.CONTRATO AND PREVDESP1.COMPETAM <= GERAL.COMPETAM
	GROUP BY CONTRATO,ZG_DATA
	) AS X
ORDER BY ZGCHAVE DESC)
,
*
FROM GERAL 
WHERE CONTRATO = '346000530'
ORDER BY EMPRESA,CONTRATO,COMPETAM

SELECT EMPRESA,CONTRATO,COMPETAM,ZG_DATA,* FROM PREVDESP1
WHERE CONTRATO = '346000530'
AND ZG_DATA = '20200128'
AND ZG_SEQ = '02'

SELECT SUM(ZL_VALOR) FROM SZL 
WHERE ZL_CONTRAT = '346000530'
AND ZL_DATA = '20200128'
AND ZL_SEQ = '02'
AND ZL_TIPO = '02'

SELECT * FROM SZL 
WHERE ZL_CONTRAT = '346000530'
AND ZL_DATA = '20200128'
AND ZL_SEQ = '02'
AND ZL_TIPO = '02'
